T12TD4298E:33b-31: pa thin la sogs pa'i tha yig la rnam dbye thog ma lnga pha rol la nuta\ a'a ga ma 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:33b-37: pa thin la sogs pa'i ti ni rnam dbye si pha rol la a'a ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:33b-40: ` (lam) ...panth'a:...(si) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:33b-43: panth'a noo/...(aoo) panth'a na:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:33b-44: panth'a nam/...(aama\) panth'a noo/...(aoo) mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:33b-45: ba th'am te: pa thina\ rnams kyi ti'o //
T12TD4298E:33b-46: pa thina\ la sogs pa rnams kyi ti ni shasa\ sogs rnam dbye dbyangs dang po can rnams pha rol la dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:34a-5: mthina\/....(srub pa/) ri bhu kshina\ ...(brgya byin/) sogs kyang de kho na dang 'dra'o /
T12TD4298E:34a-6: ` / nra yig mtha' can dandina\ zhes pa la sogs pa'i sgra la ni mi 'dra ba yod de /
T12TD4298E:34a-9: ai na\ rnams kyi shi dang si la'o //
T12TD4298E:34a-12: ....(rgyas pa/) aar++ya ....(nyi ma) mana\ zhes pa rnams kyi au pa dh'a ni dzasa\ shasa\ bsgyur ba'i shi dang dhi ma yin pa'i si pha rol la ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:34a-16: si) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34a-17: dandi noo/...(aoo) dandi na:...(dzasa\) bod tshig gsum la /
T12TD4298E:34a-18: he dandi na/...(si) he dandi noo:...(aoo) he dandi na:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:34a-19: dandi nam/...(aama\) dandi noo/...(aoo) dandi na:...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:34a-23: ka lina\/....(cha shas can/) ka p'a li na\/...(thod pa can/) mu sha lina\/...(gtun shing can/) danti na\/....(mche ba can te glang po/) m'a lina\/....('phreng ba can/) dha nina\/....(nor can/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:34a-24: ` / na\ yig mtha' can brahma hana\ zhes pa'i sgra la ni rnam dbye thog ma lnga de dang 'dra zhing shas sogs la khyad par yod de /
T12TD4298E:34a-25: ` brahya h'a/...(si tshangs 'joms/) brahma ha noo/...(aoo) brahma ha na:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34a-26: brahma ha nam/...(aama\) brahma ha noo/...(aoo) mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34a-27: shas la sogs pa dbyangs lam pa sogs kyis aa phyis /
T12TD4298E:34a-30: han gyi ha ni aa phyis pa lta bu'i bar na yi ge gzhan med pa'i nra yig dang rkyen nyu na kra dra rnams 'gro ba pha rol la'ang gha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:34a-32: brahma ghna: ...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:34a-35: ` / de bzhin du pu shana\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang rnam dbye bdun pa'i gcig tshig ma gtogs sngon ma rnams dang 'dra ste /
T12TD4298E:34a-36: ` (rgyas pa/) ...push'a/...(si) pu sha noo/...(aoo) pu sha na:...(dzasa\) pu sha nam/...(aama\) pu sha noo/...(aoo) pu sha na:...(shasa\) pu sha n'a/...(t'a) pu sha bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:34a-37: pu sha bhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34a-38: skabs la lar di la du shan\ gyi ti dbyi bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:34b-2: mi dbyi ba gsum 'dam kha can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:34b-3: pu shi/...(ngi) pu shni/...(ngi) pu sha ni/...(ngi) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:34b-4: ` / aar++ya ....(mchod pa byed/) man zhes pa'i sgra la'ang gzhan thams cad de dang 'dra ba la ngi la ti mi dbyi /
T12TD4298E:34b-5: aa dbyi ba dang mi dbyi ba yang na par byas pas /
T12TD4298E:34b-7: (si) aar++ya ma noo/...(aoo) aar++ya ma na:...(dzasa\) aar++ya ma nam /
T12TD4298E:34b-8: ...(aama\) aar++ya ma noo/...(aoo) aar++ya mna:...(shasa\) aar++ya mh'a/...(t'a) aar++ya ma bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:34b-10: aar++ya mni/...(ngi) aar++ya ma ni/...(ngi) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:34b-11: ` / na\ yig mtha' can panytsana\ la grangs kyi don brjod pa la mang tshig kho na las mi 'jug cing rkyen la mi ltos par rang bzhin gyi rtags gsum pa zhes zer te /
T12TD4298E:34b-14: panytshana\/ dzasa\ zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:34b-16: dzasa\ shasa\ dag ni 'jig go / grangs kyi sgra sha\ yig dang na\ yig gi mtha' las pha rol gyi dzasa\ shasa\ dag 'jig ste /
T12TD4298E:34b-18: rkyen phyis pa la rkyen gyi bya ba yod la /
T12TD4298E:34b-19: 'jig pa la ni bya ba med do zhes bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:34b-21: ` (lnga) ....banytsa/...(dzasa\) de bzhin du shas la yang /
T12TD4298E:34b-22: pa nytsa/...(shasa\) gsum pa bzhi pa lnga pa rnams la /
T12TD4298E:34b-23: panytsa bhi: panytsa bhya: panytsa bhya: drug pa'i a'a ma\ la /
T12TD4298E:34b-25: grangs kyi sgra sha yig dang nra yig gi mtha' las pha rol gyi a'a ma\ la nu ta a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:34b-33: saptana\/....(bdun/) na ba na\/....(dgu/) da shana\ ....(bcu/) sogs so ;
T12TD4298E:34b-34: ` yang na\ yig mtha' can aashtana\ zhes pa'i sgra la bya ba mi 'dra ba yod de /
T12TD4298E:34b-35: de yang grangs kyi dbang du byas te dang po'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34b-38: aashtan las pha rol gyi dzasra shasra gnyis ni yang na doo zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:34b-40: ` (brgyad) ....aashtoo/...(dzasa\) aashta/...(dzasa\) de bzhin du shas la /
T12TD4298E:34b-41: aashtoo/...(shasa\) aashta/...(shasa\) gsum ba'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:34b-44: aashtnra gyi au pa dh'a'i aa ni 'di rnams te rnam dbye rnams pha rol la ring por yang na 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35a-1: bhi: bzhi pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35a-2: aasht'a bhya: aashta bhya: lnga pa la'ang /
T12TD4298E:35a-3: aasht'a bhya: aashta bhya: drug pa'i mang tshig la cho ga yang na bar byed kyang gzugs gcig pas /
T12TD4298E:35a-8: ` ma yig mtha' can ai dama\ gyi sgra la /
T12TD4298E:35a-10: ai da monya yam pum si /
T12TD4298E:35a-11: ai dama\ gyi skyes pa la aa yam mo //
T12TD4298E:35a-12: ai dama\ gyi sgra ni skyes pa'i rtags kyi skabs su si dang lhan cig par aa yam zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35a-14: tyad sogs kyi si sogs la ti aa 'os /
T12TD4298E:35a-18: tyada\ la sogs pa'i da yig ni rnam dbye si la sogs pa pha rol la ma yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35a-23: ai me/...(dzasa\) tyada sogs la bod tshig ni mi 'jug la /
T12TD4298E:35a-25: ai mam/...(aama\) ai moo/...(aoo) ai m'ana\/
T12TD4298E:35a-27: aa na too soo: ta aos dag la aa na'o //
T12TD4298E:35a-28: ai dama\ gyi sgra ni rnam dbye t'a dang ao sra dag pha rol la aa na zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35a-29: aa ne na/...(t'a) gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35a-31: ai dam gyi sgra ni sa yig dang bha yig pha rol la aa yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35a-32: ai ma aa bha la a'a 'os /
T12TD4298E:35a-37: ai dama\ dang aa dasa\ kyi sgra las pha rol gyi rnam dbye bhis ni bhi sa ru 'gyur la de yang bha yang 'gyur ba 'gog pa'i don te /
T12TD4298E:35a-38: bha sa mang po nyid la ae 'os aa aer bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:35a-39: ae bhi: bzhi pa'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35a-40: sarba sogs la smata\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:35a-41: aasmee/...(nge) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35a-42: a'a bhy'am: ae bhya: de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:35a-45: ae bhya: drug pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:35a-46: aa sya/...(ngasa\) aa na yo:...(aosa\) ae sh'am/...(a'ama\) bdun pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:35a-47: aa smin\/...(ngi) aa na yo:...(aosa\) ae shu/...(supa\) ` ma yig mtha' can kimra gyi sgra las /
T12TD4298E:35a-48: tyada\ sogs kyi si sogs la ti aa 'os /
T12TD4298E:35a-49: ka zhes bsgyur ba la chog thams cad sarba'i skabs ltar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:35b-3: ` / dha yig mtha' can ta tva budhra zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:35b-4: rnam dbye dbyangs thog ma can la 'dren pa dang /
T12TD4298E:35b-5: ra sa'i yi ge thog ma can rnams la dzha bha'i mtha' las zhes pa dang /
T12TD4298E:35b-6: gnas med pa sogs kyi cho gas bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:35b-7: ` ta tva bhu ta\/...(si de kho na nyid rtogs pa/) ta tva bhuda\/...(si) ta tva budhoo/...(aoo) ta tva bu dha:...(dzasa\) he ta tva bhuta\/...(si) he ta tva bhu da\/...(si) ta tva bu dham/...(aama\) ta tva bu dhoo /
T12TD4298E:35b-8: ...(aoo) ta tva budha:...(shasa\) ta tva budh'a/...(t'a) ta tva bhudbhi: ta to bhut+su ...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:35b-9: ` / dza\ yig mtha' can samr'a dza\ zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:35b-11: tsha sha sha r'a dz'a de: sha: tsha sha sha r'a dza\ la sogs pa'i sha'o //
T12TD4298E:35b-12: tsha\ yig dang sha\ yig dang sha\ yig rnams kyi mtha' can dang r'a dza\ ....(gsal ba/) ya dza\ ....(lha mchod ba/) mri dza\ ....(gtong ba/) bhra dza\ ....(brtan pa/) la sogs pa'i mtha' ni byings yin na dzha sa'i yi ge dang ming yin na ra sa'i yi ge pha rol tu byung ba dang tshig mtha' las kyang sha nyid du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35b-15: mtha'i sha\ yig ni byings yin na dzha sa'i yi ge dang ming la ra sa'i yi ge pha rol na yod pa dang tshig mtha' las kyang da yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35b-17: gnas med pa la yang na 'os /
T12TD4298E:35b-18: ` samr'ata\/...(si yang dag pa gsal ba/) samr'a da\/...(si) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35b-19: samr'a dzoo/...(aoo) samr'a dza:...(dzasa\) bod tshig gsum la /
T12TD4298E:35b-20: he samr'ata\/...(si) he samr'ada\/...(si) he samr'a dzoo/...(aoo) he samr'a dza:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:35b-21: samr'a dzam/...(aama\) samr'a dzoo/...(aoo) samr'a dza:...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:35b-23: samr'adbhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:35b-26: bi r'a dza\ ....(rnam par gsal ba/) la sogs pa yang 'di dang 'dra'o /
T12TD4298E:35b-27: ` / da yig mtha' can tyada\ tada\ yada\ ae tad rnams kyi sgra las /
T12TD4298E:35b-29: tyada\ sogs kyi si sogs la ti aa 'os /
T12TD4298E:35b-32: tyada\ la sogs pa'i ta yig ni si pha rol las yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:35b-34: ti aar bsgyur ba las rba sogs kyi cho gas bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:36a-2: tyoo/...(aoo) tye/...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36a-3: tyam/...(aama\) tyoo/...(aoo) ty'ana/...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36a-7: tye bhya: lnga pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36a-9: tye bhya: drug pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36a-10: tya sya/...(ngasa\) tya yo:...(aosa\) tya sh'am/...(a'ama\) bdun pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36a-17: ...(dzasa\) ` ae sha/....('di si) ae too/...(aoo) aee te ...(dzasa\) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:36a-18: yang ae tada\ kyi sga las slar yang lnga bas te brjod pa'i don la rnam dbye gnyis pa rnams dang t'a aos dag pha rol la ae tadra ni ae na zhes par bsgyur ba dang mi bsgyur ba 'dam kha can du bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:36a-21: ...(aama\) ae noo/...(aoo) ae n'a na\/...(shasa\) ae ne na/...(t'a) ae na yo: ...(aosa\) ae na yo:...(aosa\) zhes pa'o /
T12TD4298E:36a-22: ` / tsha yig mtha' can ta tva pr'a tsha\ zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:36a-23: tsha sha sha sogs kyis tshva sha\/
T12TD4298E:36a-25: gnas med pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:36a-26: ` ta tva pr'ata\/...(si de kho na nyid la dri ba/) tatva pr'a da\/
T12TD4298E:36a-27: ...(si) ta tva br'a tshoo/...(aoo) ta tva pr'a tsha:...(dzasa/) he ta tva br'ata\/...(si) he ta tva pr'ada\/...(si) ta tva pr'a tsham/...(aama\) ta tva pr'a tshoo/...(aoo) ta tva pr'a tsha:...(shasa\) ta tva pr'a tsh'a/...(t'a) ta tva pr'adbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:36a-28: ta tva pr'adbhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:36a-30: ` tha yig mtha' can aagni mtha\ zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:36a-31: gnas med pa la yang na'o dang /
T12TD4298E:36a-32: dzha bha la dza ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:36a-33: ` (si) ...aagni ma tra/....(me srubs pa/) aagni mada\/...(si) aagni ma thoo/...(aoo) aagni ma tha:...(dzasa\) he aagni mata\/...(si) he aagni mada\/...(si) aagni mtham/...(aama\) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:36a-37: ` / tsa yig mtha' can pra tyatsra zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:36a-38: de yang aatsa\'i sgral rnam dbye thog ma lnga po pha rol la num\a a'a ga ma ster bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:36a-41: tsa\ si zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:36a-42: sa tu'i sha tsu rnams la sha tsu 'os /
T12TD4298E:36a-44: yang dag par sbyor ba'i mtha' dbyi 'os /
T12TD4298E:36b-0: mtha'i tsa sde ni byings yin na dzha sa'i yi ge dang ming la ra sa'i yi ge pha rol na yod pa dang tshig mtha' las @36b kyang grangs mtshungs ba'i ka sde rnams su 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:36b-2: ` (nub) ....pra tyanga/...(si) de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:36b-3: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:36b-4: pra tyanytsoo/...(aoo) bra tyanytsa:...(dzasa\) bod pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:36b-5: he pra tyanga\/...(si) he pra tyanytsoo/...(aoo) he pra tyanytsa: ...(dzasa\) gnyis pa'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:36b-6: pra tyanytsam/...(aama\) pra tyanytsoo/...(aoo) mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:36b-7: aa tse ra lo po d'irghra shtsa: aa tsa\'i dbyi zhing ring po'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:36b-8: aa tsa\ zhes pa'i sgra'i aa yig ni shasra sogs rnam dbye dbyangs thog ma rnams dang /
T12TD4298E:36b-10: mo rkyen pa'i pra dang pa'i yig rnams pha rol la dbyi zhing dbyangs snga ma de yang ring por 'gyur te aa phyis /
T12TD4298E:36b-11: rgyu mtshan med na rgyu mtshan can yang med pas ya\ yang ai la log / de ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:36b-17: zhes pa la'ang rnam dbye thog ma lnga pra tyatsa\ dang 'dra zhing shas sogs dbyangs thog ma can rnams la cho ga mi 'dra ba yod de /
T12TD4298E:36b-18: ` tir++ya nga\/...(si dud 'gro rgyags po) tir++yanytsoo/...(aoo) tiryanytsa:...(dzasa\) he tir++yanga\/...(si) tir++yanytsam/...(aama\) tir++yanytsoo/...(aoo) zhes dang /
T12TD4298E:36b-20: ti rashts'a da ya: ti rashtsa\ la sogs pa'o //
T12TD4298E:36b-21: tir++yatsa\ la sogs pa rnams ni shas sogs rnam dbye dbyangs thog ma can rnams dang /
T12TD4298E:36b-24: a'i yig rnams pha rol la ti rashtsa la sogs pa rnams su 'gyur la de yang tshig phrad kyis sgrub pa ste /
T12TD4298E:36b-25: tir++yatsa\ ti rashtsa ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:36b-26: ti rashtsa: ...(shasa\) lhag ma rnams la /
T12TD4298E:36b-28: tir++yagbhi: ti rashtse/...(nge) tir++ya kshu ...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:36b-29: ` / de bzhin du au datsa\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang thog ma lnga de rnams dang 'dra la shas sogs la ti rashtsa\ la sogs pa'os au datsa\/
T12TD4298E:36b-30: au d'itsa\ ru bsgyur nas sgrub pa sogs byas pas /
T12TD4298E:36b-31: ` au danga\/...(si) au danytshoo/...(aoo) au danytsa:...(dzasa\) he au dang/...(si) au danytsam/...(aama\) audanytsoo/...(aoo) au d'itsa:...(shasa\) au d'its'a/...(t'a) au dagbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:36b-32: au dgbhi: au d'i tse/...(nge) au da kshu ...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:36b-33: ` / de bzhin du sa mya tsra la yang shas sogs dbyangs thog ma can la sa m'i tsa ru sgyur ba sogs byas pas /
T12TD4298E:37a-1: sa myanytsoo/...(aoo) sa myanytsa:...(dzasa\) he sa myanga\/
T12TD4298E:37a-2: ...(si) sa myanytsam/...(aama\) sa myanytsoo/...(aoo) sa m'i tsa: ...(shasa\) sa m'i ts'a/...(t'a) sa myagbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37a-3: sa m'i tse/...(nge) sa myakshu/...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37a-4: ` / ta yig mtha' can ma ruta\ ces pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:37a-5: gnas med pa la yang na'o dang /
T12TD4298E:37a-7: dzha bha la dza ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:37a-8: ` ma ruta\/...(si) ma ruda\/...(si) ma ru too/...(aoo) ma ru ta:...(dzasa\) ma ru tam /
T12TD4298E:37a-9: ...(aama\) ma ru too/...(aoo) ma ru ta:...(shasa\) ma ru t'a/...(t'a) ma rudbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37a-10: ma rudbhi: ma rut+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37a-11: ` / de bzhin du aagni tsitra ....(me gsog pa/) sogs mang po dag des 'gre'o /
T12TD4298E:37a-12: ` / ta mtha' au yig rjes 'brel can las ma ha tu zhes pa la au phyis /
T12TD4298E:37a-14: ces gnas pa la rnam dbye rnams byin pas /
T12TD4298E:37a-17: au rita\ dag las nu ma\'o //
T12TD4298E:37a-18: rtags au yig dang rita\ rjes 'brel can rnams las /
T12TD4298E:37a-19: skyes pa'i rtags kyi skabs su rnam dbye thog ma lnga po dang dhi rnams dang /
T12TD4298E:37a-20: shi pha rol la yang numa\ a'a ga ma 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:37a-22: nsamma ha to dhoo d'irgha: shoo tsa /
T12TD4298E:37a-23: na\ sa\ aapa\ ma ha ta\ kyi dhi ma yin pa la ring po ste shi la'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:37a-24: na\ yig dang sa\ yig gi mtha' dang aapa\ dang ma hat\ kyi sgra rnams phyis au pa dh'a'i dbyangs rnams ni dhi por ba'i rnam dbye thog ma lnga dang shi pha rol la la'ang ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:37a-26: yang dag par sbyor ba'i mtha' phyis /
T12TD4298E:37a-27: ` (si) ...ma hana\/....(chen po/) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37a-28: ma h'antoo/...(aoo) ma h'anta:...(dzasa\) bod tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37a-29: he ma hana\/...(si) gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:37a-30: ma h'antam/...(aama\) ma h'a ntoo/...(aoo) ma ha ta:...(shasa\) gsum pa'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37a-31: ma ha t'a/...(t'a) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37a-37: ma hadbhya: ma ha ta:...(ngasi) ma hat+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37a-38: ` / ta mtha' au rjes 'brel can bha ba ta\ ces pa'i sgra las /
T12TD4298E:37a-41: aa tu dang sa'i si la'o //
T12TD4298E:37a-42: rkyen aa tu'i mtha' dang sa yig mtha' can gyi au pa dh'a ni dhi ma yin pa'i si pa rol la ring bor 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:37a-43: ` (dngos po/) ....bha b'ana\/...(si) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37a-44: bha bantoo/...(aoo) bha banta:...(dzasa\) de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:37b-0: @37b bha bantam/...(aama\) bha bantoo/...(aoo) bha ba ta:...(shasa\) bha ba t'a/...(t'a) bha badbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37b-1: bha badbhi: bha bat+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37b-2: ` / ta yig mtha' rita rjes 'brel can bha ba tri zhes pa'i sgra la'ang ri phyis /
T12TD4298E:37b-3: si la ring por mi 'gyur gzhan thams cad sngon ma dang 'dra ste /
T12TD4298E:37b-4: ` bha bana\/...(si dngos po byed/) bha bantoo /
T12TD4298E:37b-5: ...(aoo) bha banta:...(dzasa\) he bha bana\/...(si) bha bantam/...(aama\) bha bantoo/...(aoo) bha ba ta:...(shasa\) bha ba t'a/...(t'a) bha badbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37b-6: bha badbhi: bha bat+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37b-7: ` / de bzhin du ta mtha' ri yig rjes 'brel can pa tsa tri zhes pa'i sgra la'ang cho ga thams cad bha ba tri dang 'dra bas /
T12TD4298E:37b-8: ` pa tsana\/...(si 'tshed pa/) pa tsantoo/...(aoo) pa tsanta:...(dzasa\) he pa tsana\/...(si) pa tsantam/...(aama\) pa tsantoo/...(aoo) pa tsa ta:...(shasa\) pa tsa t'a/...(t'a) pa tsadbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37b-9: pa tsadbhi: pa tsat+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:37b-10: ` / sha yig mtha' can bi shra zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:37b-11: tsha sha sha sogs kyis sha sha /
T12TD4298E:37b-13: sha\ da\ ru bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:37b-15: ` bita\/....(gyog / si) bida\/...(si) bi shoo/...(aoo) bi sha:...(dzasa\) he bita\/...(si) he bida\/...(si) bi sham/...(aama\) bi shoo/...(aoo) bi sha:...(shasa\) bi sh'a/...(t'a) bidbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:37b-17: ` /sha yig mtha' can sha sha\ zhes pa'i sgra las grangs kyi don la mang tshig kho na las mi 'jug cing /
T12TD4298E:37b-18: de yang rang bzhin gyi rtags gsum pa zhes zer te /
T12TD4298E:37b-19: dang po'i mang tshig la dzasa\ shasa\ dag 'jig gos dzasa\ phyis /
T12TD4298E:37b-22: ` sha ...(drug/) da\/...(dzasa\) shata\/...(dzasa\) de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:37b-23: he shata\/...(dzasa\) he shada\/...(dzasa\) shata\/...(shasa\) shada\/...(shasa\) shadbhi: shadbhya: shadbhya: zhes dang drug ba'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37b-25: n'am la'os ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:37b-26: sh'ada\ na\ a'ama\ zhes gnas pa la dna: da'i na'o //
T12TD4298E:37b-27: grangs dang 'brel ba'i da yig ni n'amra pha rol la na yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:37b-30: sh'annram/...(a'ama\) bdun ba'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:37b-31: shatshu/...(supa\) skabs la lar tshig mtha' ma yin pa la'ang tshig mtha'i cho ga rnams bya bar bshad do /
T12TD4298E:37b-32: ` /sha yig mtha' can do sha zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:37b-34: do sh'am ra: dosha rnams kyi ra'o //
T12TD4298E:38a-0: ....(g-yog nang zan lta bu/) a'a shisha\/....(snying nye ba/) ha bi sha\ ....(sreg rdzas/) la sogs pa rnams kyi @38a * //
T12TD4298E:38a-1: mtha'i sha yig ni ra sa'i yi ge pha rol tu byung ba dang tshig mtha' las kyang ra\ yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:38a-2: ` do:...(si lag pa/) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-3: do shoo/...(aoo) do sha\:...(dzasa\) bod tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-4: he do:...(si) gnyis pa'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-5: do sham/...(aama\) do shoo/...(aoo) mang tshig la ;
T12TD4298E:38a-6: shasa\ sogs rnam dbye dbyangs thog ma can rnams pha rol la na\ yig mtha' can du sgyur ba dang mi sgyur ba sha\ mtha' nyid kyi cho ga 'dam kha can du bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:38a-7: doshna:...(shasa\) do sha:...(shasa\) de bzhin du gsum pa sogs la /
T12TD4298E:38a-9: dorbhi: doshne/...(nge) do she/...(nge) dorshu sogs so //
T12TD4298E:38a-10: de bzhin du sa dzusha\ zhes pa'i sgra la yang gzhan cho ga thams cad de dang 'dra ba la /
T12TD4298E:38a-11: sa dzusha\ dang a'a shisha\'i au pa dh'a'i dbyangs ni ra sa'i yi ge pha rol dang tshig mtha' las kyang ring por 'gyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:38a-12: ` sadzu:...(si gyog nang zan lta bu rgyun du nye bar gnas pa'i don/) sadzushoo/...(aoo) sa dzu sha:...(dzasa\) he sa dz'u:...(si) sadzu sham/...(aama\) sadzu shoo/...(aoo) sa dzusha:...(shasa\) sa dzu sh'a /
T12TD4298E:38a-14: sadz'urbhi: sa dzu she/...(nge) sadz'urshu sogs so /
T12TD4298E:38a-15: ` / sa yig mtha' can pum sa'i sgra las dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-18: pum sa\'i mtha' ni rnam dbye thog ma lnga po pha rol la aa sung du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:38a-20: da\ yig mtha' kho na 'gyur ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:38a-21: au yig au ri ta\ dag la numa\ 'os don /
T12TD4298E:38a-22: sva re ma: dbyangs la ma'o //
T12TD4298E:38a-23: rjes su nga ro ni dbyangs pha rol la ma yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:38a-24: pu ma sa\ si zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:38a-25: au rita\ ces pa'i num\ byin /

T12TD4298E:38a-27: yang dag par sbyor ba'i mtha' phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:38a-28: ` pu m'ana\/...(si skyes bu/) de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:38a-29: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-30: pu m'am soo/...(aoo) pu m'am sa:...(dzasa\) bod tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-31: he bu mana\/...(si) he bu m'am soo/...(aoo) he pu m'am ...(dzasa\) sa: gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:38a-32: pu m'am sam/...(aama\) pu m'am soo/...(aoo) pums: ...(shasa\) gsum pa'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-33: pum s'a/...(t'a) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38a-34: yang dag pa'i mtha' phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:38a-37: pum se/...(nge) pum bhy'am: pum bhya: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38b-0: aa sam bha @38b be pum sa: kaksoo /
T12TD4298E:38b-1: mi 'byung ba la pum sra'i su la ka ka\'o //
T12TD4298E:38b-2: mi 'byung ba zhes pa skyes bu ni rang nyid gcig po yin pas bdun ba'i mang tshig supa\ mi thob la de la rigs dang brtson pa skyed pa'i don du supa\ pha rol la kaka\ a'a ga ma ster bar rig byed kyi lugs tshig phrad du bsgrub pa ste /
T12TD4298E:38b-4: pumsa\ ka\ su zhes gnas pa la /

T12TD4298E:38b-7: yang dag par sbyor ba sa\ yig dang ka\ yig gnyis 'dzom pa la ni gang sngon na yod pa de dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:38b-9: ku ai la sogs kyis sa\ sha\/
T12TD4298E:38b-10: ka\ sha\ yang dag par sbyor baksha /
T12TD4298E:38b-12: yang na ka kra ma byin pas /
T12TD4298E:38b-14: pum ssu ste gzugs gsum mo /
T12TD4298E:38b-15: ` / sa\ yig mtha' can bi dvasa\ zhes pa'i sgra la rnam dbye thog ma lnga bod tshig dang bcas pa gong ma rnams dang 'dra bas /
T12TD4298E:38b-16: ` bi dv'ana\/...(si mkhas pa/) bidv'am soo/...(aoo) bi dv'am sa:...(dzasa\) he bi dva na\/...(si) bi dv'am sam/...(aama\) bi dv'am soo/...(aoo) shasa\ la ;
T12TD4298E:38b-17: ba sorba au: basa\ kyi ba au'o //
T12TD4298E:38b-18: basa\ kyi ba yig ni shas sogs rnam dbye dbyangs dang po can rnams dang /
T12TD4298E:38b-20: mo rkyen a'ipa\ dang a'i yig rnams pha rol la au ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:38b-21: bi du sha: ...(shasa\) gsum pa'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:38b-23: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la ;
T12TD4298E:38b-24: bsa\ rnams kyi ra sa la'os /
T12TD4298E:38b-27: bi dvadbhi: de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:38b-30: bi dvadbhya: bi dvat+su sogs so /
T12TD4298E:38b-31: ` / sa\ yig mtha' can su ba tsa sa\ zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:38b-32: aa tu dang sa'i si la'os /
T12TD4298E:38b-34: bha yig thog ma can rnams la /
T12TD4298E:38b-37: de aur bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:38b-38: ` (si) ...su bats'a:....(legs pa'i ngag/) su ba tsa soo/...(aoo) su ba tsa sa:...(dzasa\) he su ba tsa: ...(si) su btsa sam/...(aama\) su ba tsa soo/...(aoo) su ba tsa sa: ...(shasa\) su ba tsa s'a/...(t'a) su ba tso bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:38b-39: su ba tso bhi: su ba tsassu ...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:38b-41: tsandra ....(zla ba) ma sa\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang cho ga thams cad de dang 'dra'o /
T12TD4298E:38b-42: ` / sa yig mtha' can au sha nas zhes pa'i sgral khyad par yod de /
T12TD4298E:39a-2: aa ne hasa\ rnams las pha rol gyi dhi ma yin pa'i si ni d'a zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:39a-5: ` au shan'a/...(si pa sangs/) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:39a-7: (aoo) au sha na sa: (dzasa\) bod tshig la au sha nas kyi na mtha' dang aa mtha' dang sa mtha' gsum du bshad pa ltar /
T12TD4298E:39a-9: ...(si) he au sha na/...(si) he au sha na:...(si) he au sha na soo /
T12TD4298E:39a-10: ...(aoo) he au sha na sa:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa sogs la /
T12TD4298E:39a-11: au sha na sam/...(aama\) au sha na soo/...(aoo) au sha na sa:...(shasa\) au sha na s'a/...(t'a) au sha no bhy'am /

T12TD4298E:39a-13: ` / sa yig mtha' can aa dasa\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang mi 'dra ba yod de /

T12TD4298E:39a-22: aa das las pha rol gyi si ni aoo zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:39a-25: ` / aa soo/...('di si) gnyis tshig la /

T12TD4298E:39a-46: sngon la bha la a'a 'os a'ara\ bsgyur /
T12TD4298E:39a-52: bhas mang po nyid la ae ru bsgyur /
T12TD4298E:39a-53: mang po nyid la ae'i a'i 'os /

T12TD4298E:39b-0: @39b aa m'i bhya: lnga pa gsum la /

T12TD4298E:39b-9: aa mu yo:...(aosa\) mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:39b-10: aa m'i sh'am/...(a'ama\) bdun pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:39b-11: aa mushmina\/...(ngi) aa mu yo:...(aosa\) aa m'i shu /
T12TD4298E:39b-12: ...(supa\) ` aa dasa\ kyi lus 'gyur gzhan ni /
T12TD4298E:39b-13: aa da sa: ka: sy'a di batstsa /

T12TD4298E:39b-15: aa dasa\ kyi sgra las mtshungs pa'am spyi'i sgra la 'jug pa la /
T12TD4298E:39b-16: ka rkyen du 'gyur la de la yang si sogs kyi cho ga rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:39b-20: aa mu ka zhes 'grub pa la sarba sogs kyi bya ba rnams byas pas /
T12TD4298E:39b-21: ` aa mu ka:...(si che ge mo/) aa mu koo/...(aoo) aa mu ke /
T12TD4298E:39b-22: ...(dzasa\) aa mu kam/...(aama\) aa mu koo/...(aoo) aa mu k'a na\/...(shasa\) aa mu ke na/...(t'a) aa mu k'a bhy'am /

T12TD4298E:39b-28: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'addha sant'a:pullim g'a:sa m'agt'a: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las ha sa'i mtha' las skyes pa'i rtags rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:39b-29: ` // de nas ha sa'i mtha' las bud med kyi rtags rnams bshad par bya ste /

T12TD4298E:40a-0: @40a * // au pa nadbhyam: drug pa gsum la /

T12TD4298E:40a-8: ` dyoo: ...(si 'od gsal/) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /

T12TD4298E:40a-17: di b'a/...(t'a) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /

T12TD4298E:40a-32: ti sri dang tsa ta sri zhes par 'gyur zhing mtha'i ri yig de yang r'i yig bzhin du ste aar du mi bsgyur ba ra\ yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:40a-33: ` tsa ta sra:...(dzasa bzhi/) de bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:40a-34: gnyis pa gsum pa bzhi pa lnga pa rnams kyi mang tshig la /

T12TD4298E:40a-36: sdeb sbyor las n'am la ring por sgyur ba dang mi sgyur ba 'dam kha can du bshad pas /

T12TD4298E:40a-43: ra ba dag la ai au dag gi ha sa la'o //
T12TD4298E:40a-44: ra\ yig dang ba\ yig dag gi au ba dh'a'i dbyings kyi ai yig dang au yig dag ni ha sa'i yi ge pha rol la ring bor 'gyur te /

T12TD4298E:40b-11: ` / dha yig mtha' can sa midhra zhes pa'i sgra la /

T12TD4298E:40b-14: ` sa mita\/...(si yam shing/) sa mida\/...(si) sa mi dhoo/...(aoo) sa mi dha:...(dzasa\) he sa mi ta\/...(si) he sa mida\/...(si) sa mi dham ...(aama\) sa mi dhoo/...(aoo) sa mi dha:...(shasa\) sa mi dh'a/...(t'a) sa midbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:40b-17: ` / bha\ yig mtha' can ka ku bha\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang gnas med pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:40b-18: ` ka kupa\/...(si yul phyog) ka kupa\/...(si) ka ku bhoo/...(aoo) ka ku bha:...(dzasa\) he ka kupa\/...(si) he ka kupa\/...(si) ka ku bham/...(aama\) ka ku bhoo/...(aoo) ka ku bha: ...(shasa\) ka ku bh'a/...(t'a) ka ku bbhy'am /

T12TD4298E:40b-20: ` / da yig mtha' can tyad la sogs pa la tyad sogs kyi si sogs la ti aa /

T12TD4298E:40b-36: ` / ma\ yig mtha' can ki ma\ zhes pa'i sgra la yang de rnams dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:40b-37: ` k'a/...(ci si) ke/...(aoo) k'a:...(dzasa\) k'am/...(aama\) ke/...(aoo) k'a:...(shasa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:40b-38: ` ma\ yig mtha' can ai dma\ gyi sgra la dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-2: / ai dama\ zhes pa'i sgra ni bud med du brjod pa la si dang lhan cig par ai yam zhes bar 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:41a-3: ` ai yam/...(si) gnyis tshig sogs la tyad sogs kyis ti aa dang /

T12TD4298E:41a-9: a'a bhya: aa sya: ...(ngasi) a'a bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:41a-10: a'a bhya: aa sy'a:...(ngasa\) aa na yo:...(aosa\) a'a s'am/...(a'ama\) aa sy'am/...(ngi) aa na yo:...(aosa\) a'a su /
T12TD4298E:41a-11: ...(supa\) ` tsa yig mtha' can tva tsa\ zhes pa'i sgra la /

T12TD4298E:41a-14: ` (si) ...tvaka\/...(pags pa/) tvaga\/...(si) tva tsoo/...(aoo) tva tsa:...(dzasa\) he tvaka\/...(si) he tvaga\/...(si) tva tsa/...(aama\) tva tsoo/...(aoo) tva tsa:...(shasa\) tva ts'a/...(t'a) tvagbhy'am tvagbhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-16: ` de bzhin du ritsa\ ....(rig byed kyi tshig rkang /
T12TD4298E:41a-17: nga\g) dang b'atsa\ sogs kyang 'di kho na dang 'dra ba nyid do /
T12TD4298E:41a-18: ` / pa yig mtha' can aapa\ ces pa'i sgra la mang tshig kho na las mi 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:41a-20: sa\ na\ aapa\ sogs kyis ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:41a-21: ` a'a pa:....(chu dzasa\) bod tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-22: he a'a pa:...(dzasa\) gnyis pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-23: aa pa:...(shasa\) gsum pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-25: aa pa\ rnams kyi bha la da\'o //

T12TD4298E:41a-27: aadbhi: de bzhin du bzhi pa lnga pa drug pa bdun pa rnams kyi mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41a-29: ` sha yig mtha' can di sha\ zhes pa'i sgra las /
T12TD4298E:41a-31: di sh'am ka: disha\ rnams kyi ka'o //

T12TD4298E:41a-35: dzhra bhra la dza ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:41a-36: ` (phyogs) ....dika\/...(si) diga\/...(si) di shoo/...(aoo) di sha:...(dzasa\) he dika\/...(si) he diga\/...(si) di sham/...(aama\) di shoo/...(aoo) di sha:...(shasa\) di sh'a/...(t'a) digbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:41b-0: digbhi: @41b sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41b-1: dikshu/...(supa\) ` sha yig mtha' can tvisha zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:41b-2: sha'i da'o dang gnas med pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /

T12TD4298E:41b-4: tvidbhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41b-6: ...(supa\) ` sha yig mtha' can a'a shi sha\ zhes pa'i sgra las /
T12TD4298E:41b-7: si la ra nyid dang lhag ma ra sa'i yi ge rnams la /
T12TD4298E:41b-8: dosha\ rnams kyi ra'os ra\ dang /

T12TD4298E:41b-12: ` a'a sh'i: ...(si mdza' ba'am snying nye ba/) a'a shi shoo/...(aoo) a'a shi sha: ...(dzasa\) he a'a sh'i:...(si) a'a shi sham/...(aama\) a'a shi shoo /

T12TD4298E:41b-15: a'a sh'irbhi: a'a shidbhi: sogs dang bdun pa'i mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:41b-18: ` sa yig mtha' can aa dasa\ zhes pa'i sgra las /
T12TD4298E:41b-21: lhag ma rnams la tyada\ sogs kyis ti aa /
T12TD4298E:41b-22: bud med la aa la a'apa\/
T12TD4298E:41b-25: mo rtags sarba sogs kyi cho gas bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:41b-27: ` aa soo/....('di si) aa m'u/...(aoo) aa m'u: ...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:41b-28: aa m'um/...(aama\) aa m'u/...(aoo) aa m'u:...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /

T12TD4298E:41b-31: aa mu shyee/...(nge) aa m'u bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:41b-32: aa m'ubhya: lnga pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:41b-33: aa mu shy'a:...(ngasi) aa m'u bhy'am /
T12TD4298E:41b-34: aa m'u bhya: drug pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:41b-35: aa mu shy'a:...(ngasa\) aa mu yo:...(aosa\) aa m'u sh'am /
T12TD4298E:41b-37: aa mu shy'am/...(ngi) aa mu yo:...(aosa\) aa m'u shu/...(supa\) ai ti sva ra svasti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tvaddha s'anta str'e lingg'atsha m'apt'a: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las ha sa'i mtha' las bud med kyi rtags rnams rdzogs so /
T12TD4298E:41b-39: // / de nas ha sa'i mtha' can ma ning gi rtags rnams rab tu bstan par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:41b-40: de la ra yig mtha' can b'ara\ zhes pa'i sgra las /
T12TD4298E:41b-41: ma ning la si aama\ 'jig pa dang /
T12TD4298E:42a-0: @42a * // yama\ min pa zhes numa\ mi ster /
T12TD4298E:42a-1: dbyangs kyi dman pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:42a-3: ...(dzasa\) he b'a:...(si) b'a:...(aama\) b'a r'i/...(aoo) b'a ri/...(shasa\) b'a r'a/...(t'a) b'arbhy'am b'arbhi: b'arshu /
T12TD4298E:42a-5: ` / ra yig mtha' can tsa tura\ gyi sgra las /
T12TD4298E:42a-6: de yang grangs kyi don la mang tshig kho na las mi 'jug cing /
T12TD4298E:42a-7: tsa tur gyi shi la a'ama\ a'a ga ma ster ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:42a-8: ` tsa tv'a ri/...(dzasa\ bzhi/) he tsa tv'a ri/...(dzasa\) tsa tv'a ri/...(shasa\) tsa turbhi: tsa turbhya: tsa turbhya: tsa turn'am /
T12TD4298E:42a-10: (supa\) ` na yig mtha' can aa hana\ zhes pa'i sgra la /
T12TD4298E:42a-12: aahna: sa: aa han gyi sa'o //
T12TD4298E:42a-13: aa han gyi na yig ni ra sa'i yi ge pha rol tu byung ba dang /
T12TD4298E:42a-14: tshig mtha' las kyang sa\ yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:42a-16: ` aa ha:...(si nyi ma) gnyis tshig la /

T12TD4298E:42a-20: aa hni/...(aa) aa ha n'i/...(aoo) mang tshig la /

T12TD4298E:42a-28: aahna/...(t'a) gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:42a-31: sa\ ra\ dag gi rnam bcad /
T12TD4298E:42a-32: aa las ha ba la au /

T12TD4298E:42a-37: aa ho bhya: lnga pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:42a-39: ao ho bhya: drug pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:42a-40: aa hna:...(ngasa\) aa hna:...(aosa\) aa hn'am /

T12TD4298E:42a-45: brahmana\ la sogs pa'i na\ yig ni ra sa'i yi ge pha rol dang tshig mtha' las kyang dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:42b-0: ` (tshangs pa/) ....pra hma/...(si) gnyis tshig dang mang @42b tshig la /
T12TD4298E:42b-1: brahma n'i/...(aoo) brahm'a ni/...(dzasa\) slar yang /
T12TD4298E:42b-2: brahma/...(aama\) brahma n'i/...(aoo) brahm'a ni/...(shasa\) bod tshig la na mi dbyi bas /

T12TD4298E:42b-16: tsharmna\/...(pags pa/) karmana\/ ...(las/) barmanda\/...(go cha'am gso ba/) sharmana\ ....(ngo mtshar ram skyid pa/) la sogs pa yang cho ga thams cad 'di dang 'dra'o /
T12TD4298E:42b-17: ` / n'anta da dant'a tshanda si ngi shyorb'a lo pa /

T12TD4298E:42b-33: ...(dzasa\ thams cad rnams/) sarb'a ni/...(dzasa\) bh'u t'a/...(shasa\ 'byung po rnams la/) bh'u t'a ni/...(shasa\) lta bu'o /
T12TD4298E:42b-34: ` / da yig mtha' can tyad ces pa'i sgra la /

T12TD4298E:42b-37: ` tya ...(nge) da\/...(si) tyata\/...(si) tye/...(aoo) ty'a ni /

T12TD4298E:43a-0: @43a * // ae tada\/...(si) ae tata\/...(si) ae te/...(aoo) ae t'a ni /
T12TD4298E:43a-3: ` yada\/....(gang / si) yata\/...(si) ye/...(aoo) y'a ni/...(dzasa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:43a-4: ` / de ltar du ma yig mtha' can kima\ gyi sgra la yang /

T12TD4298E:43a-7: ` ai dam/...(si 'di/) ai me/...(aoo) ai m'a ni /

T12TD4298E:43a-14: gnas med pa la yang na'o dang /

T12TD4298E:43a-19: ` pra tyaka\/...(si nub/) pra tyga\/...(si) pa\ t'its'i/...(aoo) pratyanytsi/...(dzasa\) pra tyaka\/...(aama\) pra tyaga\/...(aama\) pra t'its'i/...(aoo) pra tyanytsi/...(shasa\) pra t'i ts'a/...(t'a) pra tyagbhy'am /
T12TD4298E:43a-20: pra tyagbhi: pra t'i tse/...(nge) pra tyakshu/...(supa\) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:43a-21: ` / tra yig mtha' can dza gata\ cas pa'i sgra la'ang gnas med pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:43a-22: ` dza gatra/...(si 'gro ba/) dza gada\/...(si) dza ga t'i /
T12TD4298E:43a-23: ...(aoo) dza ganti/...(dzasa\) gnyis pa'ang de dang 'dra /
T12TD4298E:43a-28: ` / de bzhin du ta yig mtha' can ma hata\ kyi sgra la'ang /
T12TD4298E:43a-29: ` ma hada\/...(si chen po/) ma ha ta/...(si chen po/) ma ha t'i/...(aoo) ma hanti/...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum yang de dang 'dra /
T12TD4298E:43a-32: ma hadbhi: ma ha te sogs so /
T12TD4298E:43a-33: ` / sa yig mtha' can pa yasa\ zhes pa'i sgra la'ang /
T12TD4298E:43a-34: pa ya:...(si chu'am 'o ma/) pa ya s'i/...(aoo) pa y'am si/...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum yang de dang 'dra /
T12TD4298E:43a-38: pa yo bhi: pa ya se/...(nge) pa yassu sogs so /

T12TD4298E:43a-41: ` /sha yig mtha' can ha bisha\ zhes pa'i sgra la yang /

T12TD4298E:43a-43: dosha\ rnams kyi ra 'osa\ sha\ ra\ ru bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:43b-0: ` (sreg rdzas/) ....ha bi:...(si) @43b ha bi sh'i/...(aoo) he b'im shi/...(dzasa\) gnyis pa gsum la yang /
T12TD4298E:43b-6: ha birbhi: ha bi she/...(nge) ha ba rashu sogs so /
T12TD4298E:43b-7: ` / sa yig mtha' can aa dasa\ kyi sgra la /

T12TD4298E:43b-15: ...(dzasa\) slar yang gnyis pa gsum la /
T12TD4298E:43b-17: ...(aoo/) aa m'u ni/...(shasa\) gsum pa gsum la /

T12TD4298E:43b-22: aa m'i bhya: lnga ba gsum la /
T12TD4298E:43b-25: aa m'i bhya: drug pa gsum la /

T12TD4298E:43b-29: ai ti svar sva sti by'a kar na sya s'u tr'a ddha s'anta na pum sa ka lingga sa m'a pt'a: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las ha sa'i mtha' las ma ning gi rtags rnams rdzogs so /
T12TD4298E:43b-31: // / de nas brjod pa'i rtags yushmad aasmad gnyis kyi cho ga rnams bshad bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:43b-32: de yang rtags 'di gnyis ni yul pho mo ma ning gsum ka la 'jug cing /

T12TD4298E:43b-38: tvam/...(si khyod/) aa ham/...(si nga'am bdag/) gnyis tshig la /

T12TD4298E:43b-40: gnyis tshig la yu ba a'a ba dag go / yushmad dang aasmad dag ni gnyis tshig pha rol la rim pa bzhin yu ba a'a ba zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:43b-47: yushmad dang aa smad dag las pha rol gyi rnam dbye aoo gnyis ni a'ama\ zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:43b-48: ...(aoo) yu b'am/....(khyod dag/) a'a b'am/...(aoo bdag dag/) mang tshig la /

T12TD4298E:54b-11: de ltar tshig sdud drug las dang po mi zad par gyur pa'i bsdu ba ni /

T12TD4298E:54b-13: de'i rjes su aa dhi kri tya bha ba ti zhes pa bris pas /
T12TD4298E:54b-14: stri ya ma dhi kri tya bha ba ti/....(bud med bya ba lhag por yod pa'o/) zhes pa 'di la tshig sbyor ram ngag ste /
T12TD4298E:54b-16: bi gra ha: zer la tshig sdud byed pa'i gzhi yin no /
T12TD4298E:54b-20: mi zad pa snga ma ni mi zad par gyur pa'o //
T12TD4298E:54b-21: mi zad pa'i rtags gcig sngon na yod pa de la mi zad pa'i bsdu ba zhes bya zhing tshig sbyor gyi skabs mi zad pa'i rtags de dbus mthar yod kyang bsdu ba byed tshe sngon du 'jog pa ni tshig phrad nges tshig gi sgrub pa zhes bya ba ste /

T12TD4298E:54b-23: ` / sa m'a sa pra tya ya yo: bsdu ba dang rkyen dag la'o //

T12TD4298E:54b-25: rnam dbye rjes 'brel dang bcas pa phyis pas /

T12TD4298E:54b-27: de la yang tshig tu bsgrub pa'i phyir si la sogs pa'i rnam dbye rnams ster dgos te mtshon byed du si byin /
T12TD4298E:55a-0: mi zad pa sngon na yod cing mi zad pa'i bsdu ba byas pa de ni @55a * //

T12TD4298E:55a-10: r'a....(re/) ya ma....(aama\) ti kr'antam/....(ches cher 'byor ba dang ldan pa/) zhes pa'i don la /

T12TD4298E:64b-21: ` / aoonna tye dant'a du ra: danta las ring ba la au ra'o //

T12TD4298E:64b-23: aunn'a:...(dzasa) dant'a:...(dzasa) aa sya/....(so ring po yod pa'am so sbom po yod ba'am so mthon po yod pa can/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:64b-24: dantu ...(aura) ra:/...(si so ring po yod pa'am so sbom po yod ba'am so mthon po yod pa can/) ` shraddh'a de rlu: shraddha la sogs pa la lu'o //

T12TD4298E:64b-27: ` / aasa\ kyi mtha' can dang m'a y'a dang me dh'a dang sra kra rnams las yod pa'i don la rkyen bin 'gyur bar bshad de /

T12TD4298E:65a-0: smad pa brjod pa la a'a la a'a ta dag go / b'a tsa las smad pa'i tshig brjod pa'i don la rkyen a'a la dang a'a ta @65a * //
T12TD4298E:65a-2: b'a ts'a la:....(smra ba ngan pa can te rdzun chen po/) ....b'a ts'a ta:/
T12TD4298E:65a-3: ` a'i sha da pa ri sa m'a ptoo ka lpa de shya de sh'i ya: cung zad yongs su ma rdzogs pa la /

T12TD4298E:65a-18: (rdzus ma'i brda sprod mkhan po/) ....be y'a ka ra na r'u pa:/

T12TD4298E:65a-22: (brda sprod mkhan po rdzun du smra ba'am ngan par smra ba/) ....bee y'a ka ra na p'a sha: de bzhin du /

T12TD4298E:65a-25: sngon dus shes pa la tsa ra ta'o //

T12TD4298E:65a-28: ` pr'atsur+ya bi k'a ra pra dh'a n+y'a di shu ma yata\/
T12TD4298E:65a-29: spyi bungs dang rnam 'gyur dang gtso bo rnams lam ya ta'o //

T12TD4298E:65a-34: (mchod sbyin gyi zas sbyi sbungs 'di/) ....aanna ma yo ...(ma yata\) yadznya/...(si) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:65a-35: mri to ...(ngas\) ba ki ra gha ta:....(sa'i rnam 'gyur bum pa byed/) ....mrinma (ma yata si) ...aom gha ta: str'i pra dh'a n+ya ma sya st'i ti/....(khyis gyi gtso bo bud med 'di yod pa'o/) ..../ str'i ma yo ...(mayat\ si) dz'a lma: p'u rne na aa mri ta tsandra:....(nya gang ba'i zla bas bdud rtsi sbre/) ....aa mri ta ma ya shtsandra:/
T12TD4298E:65b-0: ` brda sprod shes nas rig byed kyang klog pa @65b lta bu'i don la rkyen aan 'gyur bar bshad de /

T12TD4298E:65b-5: mtshams sbyor gyi ya\ ba\ dag la ma yin te aita\ auta\ dag go / rkyen 'phel ba'i rgyu mtshan can pha rol las 'phel ba byed rgyu'i yi ge dang po de mtshams sbyar ba'i ya\ yig dang ba\ yig yin na thog mar 'phel ba mi byed par /

T12TD4298E:65b-17: ` / ta ra ta me ya svishth'a: pra karshe /

T12TD4298E:66b-13: (khyed dag las gang zhig rtog ge mkhan po de ni smra ba mchog tu 'dzin pa'o/) ....bha ba to ...(aosa\) r++ya ta ...(yata) ra st'arki ...(da tar) ka sta ...(tuta) ta ra ...(da tar) au nggri n'a tu sogs so /
T12TD4298E:66b-14: ` / sam khy'a ya bi she sh'a ya ba dh'a ra ne rdvi tri bhy'am t'i ya: grangs kyi bye brag logs su bkol ba la dvi dang tri dag las t'i ya'o //

T12TD4298E:66b-18: grangs kyi bye brag gis logs su bkar ba'i don la sha sha\ dang tsa tur\ dag la rkyen tha 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:66b-19: shshtha:....(drug po'am drug pa/) tsa turtha:/....(bzhi po'am bzhi po/) ` ka ti ka ti p'a y'a bhy'am tha: ka ti dang ka ti p'a ya dag las kyang tha'o //
T12TD4298E:66b-20: grangs dngos ma yin kyang grangs kyi don can yin pas ka ti dang ka ti p'a ya dag las kyang logs su bkar ba'i don la rkyen tha 'gyur te /

T12TD4298E:80a-13: lhag ma 'chad 'gyur rnam dbye sde tshan drug po rnams la byings phyed pa'i rnam dbye zhes bya ste /

T12TD4298E:80a-16: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las byed pa po'i rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so /
T12TD4298E:80a-18: // / de nas dngos po dang las kyi rab tu byed pa rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:80a-20: dngos po dang las la a'atra'o //
T12TD4298E:80a-21: byings las dang bcas pa rnams la las kyi don dang las med pa rnams la dngos po'i don du rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug cing dngos po'i don la de rnams kyi gcig tshig kho na 'jug la /
T12TD4298E:80a-22: nyer bsgyur gyi stobs kyis bsgyur ba la ni der ma nges so //
T12TD4298E:80a-23: de yang byings las bcas dang las med kyi dbye ba ni /
T12TD4298E:80a-24: byings des byed pa'i tshig gi don kho na brjod pa ni las med pa dang /
T12TD4298E:80a-25: las dang byed tshig gnyis ka'i don brjod pa de las dang bcas pa'i byings zhes grags pa las /
T12TD4298E:80a-26: byings las med pa ni bh'u dang /
T12TD4298E:80a-31: ladzdz'a satt'a sthi ti dz'a ga ra nam briddhid ksha ya bha ya dz'i bi ta ma ram /
T12TD4298E:80a-32: sha yan kri d'a ru tsi d'i ptya rtham dh'a tu ga nam ta ma karma ka m'a hu:/
T12TD4298E:80a-33: ngo tsha yod pa gnas pa mel tshe dang //
T12TD4298E:80a-34: 'phel ba zad pa 'jig pa 'tsho ba dang //
T12TD4298E:80a-35: nyal dang rtsed mo 'od dang 'bar ba'i don //
T12TD4298E:80b-0: byings kyi tshogs rnams @80b pas med par bshad do //
T12TD4298E:80b-1: zhes pa ste ngo tsha sogs don bcu gnyis po de rnams kyi don can gyi byings rnams la ni las med pa zhes bya zhing /
T12TD4298E:80b-2: de rnams las gzhan pa rnams las dang bcas pa'o //
T12TD4298E:80b-5: sanm'a tram bh'a ba linggam sy'a da sprishtam yatstsha k'a ra kee: //
T12TD4298E:80b-6: dha tv'a rtha:ke ba lam shuddhe bha ba ai tya bhi dh'i ya te /
T12TD4298E:80b-7: yod tsam dngos po'i rtags su 'gyur //
T12TD4298E:80b-8: gang yang byed can rnams ma reg / byings don rkyang pa dag pa ni //
T12TD4298E:80b-9: de la dngos por mngon par brjod //
T12TD4298E:80b-10: ces te byed can drug pa gang dang yang ma sbyar pa /
T12TD4298E:80b-11: dngos po yod pa tsam ston pa ni dngos po'i don zhes bya'o /
T12TD4298E:80b-14: byings las rnam dbye ba rta ma na sogs sde tshan dang po bzhi po pha rol la dngos po dang las kyi don la yaka\ rkyen du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:80b-15: ka yig byings la yon tan 'gog pa'i don yin pas dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:80b-16: bh'u ya te bha ba t'a/....(khyod yin/) ae dhya te dh'armi ka:....(chos dang ldan pa 'phel/) a'a sya te au p'a sa ne/....(nye ba'i gdan la gnas/) sh'ing gi yaka\ pha rol la a'i aa yada\ du bsgyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:80b-18: nga\ dang ya'i aa rjes 'brel yin pas phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:80b-19: shayya te shru dre na/....(nyal bar byed do dmangs rigs/) yang skabs la lar byings las med pa la'ang las can ltar bsgrub pa yang yod la /
T12TD4298E:80b-20: de yang nyer bsgyur sngon du byung na ni nyer bsgyur gyi dbang gis las med las can dang las can las med du bsgyur ba dang /
T12TD4298E:80b-21: gcig tshig kho na 'jug pa la gnyis tshig mang tshig thams cad sbyor ba sogs sna tshogs yod de /
T12TD4298E:80b-22: byings las nyer bsgyur stobs che bas nyer bsgyur gyis bsgyur 'gro bas dper na /
T12TD4298E:80b-23: h'a ra 'phrog pa la 'jug kyang nyer bsgyur gyis bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:80b-24: bi h'a ra/....(gnas pa/) a'a h'a ra/....(zas/) sam h'a ra/....(khongs su sdud pa/) pra ti h'a ra ....('joms pa/) sogs byings kyi don gzhan du 'gyur 'gro ba lta bu ste /
T12TD4298E:80b-26: su kha ma nu bh'u ya te sv'a mi n'a/....(rje bos bde ba rjes su myong bar byed/) zhes pa lta bu'o //
T12TD4298E:80b-27: las bcas la las kyi don du yakra sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:81a-0: ka ta: kri ya te k'a ru ke na/....(rtsva'i lha sa ma'i mal byed/) @81a * //
T12TD4298E:81a-1: tvam du kh'i kri ya se/....(khyed dka' bas byed do/) r'a goo be r'a gee:....(/ chags pa dag las chags pa bral bas nged bde bar byed do/) su khya ham kri ye /
T12TD4298E:81a-4: byings mtha'i ri tra ni rkyen aa dang yaka\ pha rol la ring\ du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81a-5: nga\ yig par mtshams gcod pa'i don te 'og nas 'byung ba'i ya la'o zhes pa sogs 'gog pa'i don yin pas dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs / pas /
T12TD4298E:81a-6: mringa\ srog gtong ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-8: ` dri 'gro ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-9: br'aham ne na d'a na m'a dri ya te/....(bram ze sbyin pa long/) hri nya\ 'phrog pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-10: hri yate dha na ta ska re na/....('phrog par byed do nor chom rkun gyis/) ` r'i ta aira\/
T12TD4298E:81a-12: rkyen ya yig pha rol la byings mtha'i r'ita\ ni aira\ du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81a-13: tr'i mchod pa dang rgyal ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la yaka\/
T12TD4298E:81a-15: tira\ ya te zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:81a-18: rkyen ya pha rol la dbyangs sngon ma de ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81a-22: tsinya\ gsog pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-23: (so phag rnams gsog par byed/) ....aishti k'a shts'i ya te /
T12TD4298E:81a-24: hu sbyin pa dang za ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-25: h'u ya te aagnim bahnoo/....(mel zas sbyin sreg phyed/) ` d'a de ri: d'a sogs kyi ai'o //
T12TD4298E:81a-26: byings du d'a nya\ la sogs pa'i a'a yig ni rkyen ka\ dang nga\ 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la ai ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81a-27: du d'anya\ sbyin pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la yaka\/
T12TD4298E:81a-29: ya la 'os ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:81a-30: d'i ya te/....(sbyin par byed/) be da bi de a'a do d'i ya t'am dha nam/....(rig byed rig pa la nor byin cig/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:81a-31: du dh'a nya\ 'dzin pa dang gsol ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-32: nidh'i ya tedh'a n+y'am bh'u moo/....(gter du sbos shig 'bru rnams/) m'ada\ tshad 'jal ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81a-33: m'i ya te/....(tshad 'jal bar byed/) ` sandhya ksha r'a n'a m'a /
T12TD4298E:81a-34: mtshams sbyor gyi yi ge rnams kyi a'a'o //
T12TD4298E:81a-35: byings mtha'i mtshams sbyor gyi yig rnams ni dngos po dang las kyi don gyi a'atma ne pa da rnams pha rol la a'a yi ge tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81a-36: kee gee ree sgra la'o zhes pa'i byings gsum la yakra /
T12TD4298E:81b-0: aee a'a ru bsgyur de nas d'a sogs kyis a'a de slar @81b yang ai /
T12TD4298E:81b-1: ya la 'os ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:81b-2: k'i ya te/....(smra bar byed) ....g'i ya te /
T12TD4298E:81b-3: r'i ya te/....(smra bar byed) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:81b-4: sho phra mor byed pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-5: sh'i ya te/....(phra mor byed/) ao h'aka\ gtong ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-6: h'i ya te/....(gtong bar byed dam 'dor bar byed/) p'a btung ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-7: p'i ya te/....('thung bar byed/) shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-9: yaka\/ dang po'i sha na ni sa na 'os sha sa /
T12TD4298E:81b-10: rgyu mtshan med na rgyu mtshan can yang med do zhes pas tha thar bsgyur ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:81b-11: sth'i ya te/....(gnas so/) ` ta no te rn'a b'a /
T12TD4298E:81b-12: tana\ gyi na'i a'a yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:81b-13: byings ta nu'i na yig ni rkyen ka 'gro ba pha rol la a'a yig tu yang na 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81b-14: ta nu yang ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-15: ta n+ya te/....(yang bar byed dam phra mor byed/) ....t'a ya te /
T12TD4298E:81b-16: ` gu no rta sim yo g'a dyo: ri'i yang dag par sbyor / ba sogs la yon tan no //
T12TD4298E:81b-17: byings ri 'gro ba la sogs pa ni yaka\ sogs dngos po dang las kyi don yang dag par sbyor ba sogs la yon tan du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:81b-18: ri 'gro ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la yaka\/
T12TD4298E:81b-20: aar++ya te/....('gro bar byed/) de bzhin du smri sems pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:81b-21: (sems par byed dam dran par byed/) .. ..smar++ya te /
T12TD4298E:81b-22: las kyi don la yang byed pa dang bcas pa'i las dang las dngos rkyang gi dbye ba yang yod de /
T12TD4298E:81b-24: yatkarma gu na sam yo g'atka rtri tve na sam yo g'atkartri tve na bi bakshya te sa karma kart'a /
T12TD4298E:81b-25: kri ya m'a nam tu yatkarma sva ya me ba pra siddhya ti /
T12TD4298E:81b-26: su ka ree:svee rgu nee r++ya sm'atkarma karte ti ta dvi du:/
T12TD4298E:81b-27: yon tan yang dag par ni ldan pa yi //
T12TD4298E:81b-28: ji ltar las nyid byed pa po yang ste //
T12TD4298E:81b-29: byed por bcas pa'i las su rnam par 'dod //
T12TD4298E:81b-30: las gang byed pas 'jug par ldan pa ste //
T12TD4298E:81b-31: rang gi stobs shugs kyi ni gang la yang //
T12TD4298E:81b-32: de nyid rab tu grub par byed pa ni //
T12TD4298E:81b-33: bde blag byed pa rang gi yon tan rnams //
T12TD4298E:81b-34: las de byed po nyid dang lhan cig rig //
T12TD4298E:81b-35: ces pa ste gang bya ba'i las kyi dngos po de byed pa pos rtsol ba chen po mi dgos par bde blag tu 'grub pa de ni byed pa po dang bcas pa'i las zhes zer te /
T12TD4298E:81b-37: ('bras chan tshos te rang shugs kyi/) ....ao da na: pa tsya te sva ya me ba /
T12TD4298E:82a-0: (dum bur byed do shing rang shugs kyi/) ....bhi dya te @82a * //
T12TD4298E:82a-2: (rnga bar byed do zhing rang shugs kyi/) l'u ya te ke d'a ra: sva ya me pa /
T12TD4298E:82a-3: zhes pa lta bu ste byings patsra 'tshed pa /
T12TD4298E:82a-4: bhi dira\ gnyis su byed pa /
T12TD4298E:82a-5: l'u nya\ gcod pa rnams la yaka\ sbyar nas bsgrubs pa'o //
T12TD4298E:82a-6: yang don gcig la las kyi tshig gnyis sbyor dgos pa yang yod la /
T12TD4298E:82a-14: tsinya\ sogs la las kyi tshig gnyis sbyor ba ste /
T12TD4298E:82a-15: n'inya\ thob pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la rkyen yaka\ sbyar /
T12TD4298E:82a-16: de la las kyi tshig gnyis sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:82a-17: na ga ram n'i ya te n'a ga ri kee rba ne tsa ra:....(grong khyer du thob bo grong khyer bas nags spyod/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:82a-18: bru y'a tsvi slong ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:82a-19: bho dza nam y'a tsya te ya dza ma no y'a tsa ke na/....(lto zas slong bar byed do slong ston gyi sar slong mo pas/) pratstsha shes par 'dod pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:82a-20: (graha\ sogs kyi slar yang dag par bsgyur ba'o/) ....pritstshya te panth'a nam pa thi ke na/....(/'dri bar byed dol ma rnams lam zhugs kyis 'grul ba la/) shishye n'a tsarya sta tvam pritstshya te/....(slob mas slob dpon la de kho na nyid 'dri bar byed do/) de ltar las kyi tshig gnyis sbyor ba la byed pa dang 'brel pa de las gtso phal gnyis las gtso bo yin no //
T12TD4298E:82a-21: ai ti sva ra svasti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'addha ba karma / pra kri ya sa m'a pt'a:/
T12TD4298E:82a-22: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las dngos po dang las kyi rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:82a-23: ` // de nas pa ro& ksha la sogs pa rnam dbye sde tshan gyi phyi ma drug gi cho ga rnams rab tu brjod par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:82a-24: de la dang po pa ro& ksha ni /
T12TD4298E:82a-25: pa ro& ksha na pa tu su stha ba thu sa na bba m'a y'a ta yi re sa y'a the dhva ye ba he ma he /
T12TD4298E:82a-45: byings las lkog tu gyur pa'i dus brjod pa'i byed pa'i don la na pra la sogs pa rnam dbye bco brgyad po 'di rnams 'gyur zhing /
T12TD4298E:82a-46: lkog tu gyur pa'i dus de la'ang 'das ma 'ongs gnyis su yod pa las 'das pa la 'jug pa 'das pa de yang 'das nas yun ring lon pa'i dus la 'jug pa shas che'o //
T12TD4298E:82a-47: rnam dbye 'di rnams la p'a ni pa'i lugs la /
T12TD4298E:82b-0: napa\ la @82b sogs pa rnam dbye bco brgyad po pha rol la de rnams sbyor gzhi'i byings de gnyis su'ang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:82b-2: lkog gyur lita'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig na pra sbyar gnyis brjod pas /
T12TD4298E:82b-6: napa\ sogs la bh'u aa dag gi a'a'o //
T12TD4298E:82b-7: rnam dbye napa\ la sogs pa pha rol la byings gnyis brjod pa'i dang po de bh'u'i a'u dang aa yin na a'a yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:82b-10: de thung ngur bsgyur dzha pa sogs kyis bha ba /
T12TD4298E:82b-13: napa\ la sogs pa'i rnam dbye rnams pha rol las byings bh'u la buka\ a'a ga ma 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:82b-14: puka\ byin ka\ gnas don au brjod don yin pas dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:82b-16: de bzhin du bsgrubs pas gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:82b-17: ba bh'u ba tu: ba bh'u bu: skyes bu dbus ma'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:82b-18: ba bh'u pa thapa\ zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:82b-19: ` kr'a derna de: kri sogs las na sogs la'o //
T12TD4298E:82b-27: sru rnams ma yin pa'i byings rnams las pha rol gyi napa\ sogs rnam dbye ba so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge dang po can rnams la aita\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:82b-30: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:82b-31: ba bh'u ba thu: ba bh'u ba /
T12TD4298E:82b-32: de rnams dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas skyes bu phyi ma gsum la /
T12TD4298E:82b-36: de bzhin du du pa tsa sha 'tshed pa la'o zhes pa'i byings la bdag don dang gzhan don gnyis ka 'jug pa las /
T12TD4298E:82b-37: dang po pa rasmee pa da'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:82b-41: gnyis kyang ngos byings gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:82b-42: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po'i sa tsa\ gong ma phyis /
T12TD4298E:82b-43: ` aa ta au pa dh'a y'a: au pa dh'a'i aatra'o [?] //
T12TD4298E:82b-44: byings kyi au pa dh'a'i aa yig ni nya\ yig dang na yig 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la 'phel bar 'gyur te ;
T12TD4298E:82b-52: na la sogs pa ka 'gro ba'o //
T12TD4298E:82b-53: rnam dbye napa\ la sogs pa pa\ 'gro ba rnams ma yin pa rnams la ni ka 'gro ba'i ming can zhes zer ro /
T12TD4298E:83a-0: ` / @83a * // lo pa:pats'i ki tye ts'a sya /
T12TD4298E:83a-1: patsa\ rnams kyi ka 'gro ba la dbyi ste aa'i yang ae'o //
T12TD4298E:83a-2: byings patsa\ la sogs pa rnams kyi gnyis brjod pa'i dang po bsgyur ba ma yin pa'i gdod ma'i aa yig yin na yi ge dang po de dbyi zhing aa yig phyi ma de yang aae yi tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:83a-3: pa gong ma phyis phyi ma'i aa aer bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:83a-4: pe tsa tu: de bzhin du mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83a-5: pe tsu: skyes bu dbus ma'i gcig tshug la /
T12TD4298E:83a-8: byings aita mi 'jug pa rnams kyi pha rol las kyang rnam dbye thapa\ la aita\ yang na 'gyur zhing /
T12TD4298E:83a-9: aita dang bcas pa'i thapa\ de yang ka 'gro ba'i ming can du yang na par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:83a-11: aita\'i phyogs la'ang ka 'gro ba'i cho ga dang mi 'gro ba'i cho ga 'dam kha can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:83a-15: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83a-17: skyes bu phyi ma'i gcig tshig napa\ la na 'gro ba'i cho ga yang na bar bshad pas 'phel ba byed pa dang mi byed pa 'dam kha can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:83a-20: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83a-23: ` a'atma ne pa da rnams la yang cho ga de rnams dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:83a-33: byings du krinya\ byed pa la'ang bdag don dang gzhan don gnyis ka 'jug pa las dang po pa rasmee pa da'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83a-35: byings gnyis brjod pa'i dang po'i dbyangs de ri yig yin na aa yig tu 'gyur te byings gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:83a-37: ku ha sogs kyis ka tsar bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:83a-41: ` dh'a torn'a min: byings kyi n'a mi'i'o //
T12TD4298E:83a-42: byings kyi mtha' n'a mi'i yi ge ni nya yig dang na yig 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la 'phel bar 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:83a-45: gnyis tshig dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83a-47: de bzhin du bsgrubs pas skyes bu dbus ma gsum la /
T12TD4298E:83b-3: cho ga de rnams dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas a'atma ne pa da'i skyes bu dang po gsum dang dbus ma'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:83b-14: tsa turn'am dho dha: bzhi po rnams ma yin pa'i rha'i n'a mi las dha'o //
T12TD4298E:83b-15: byings thams cad pa'i rnam dbye bzhi po ma yin pa las rnam dbye'i dha yig ni byings mtha' n'a mi'i pha rol la dha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:83b-22: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:83b-23: r'a mo r'a dzyam tsa k'a ra/....(dga' bye kyi rgyal srid sngon byas so/) ` de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:83b-24: aa su 'byung ba la'o zhes pa la par smee pa da rnams sbyor ba las byings gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:83b-25: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po 'os sa gong ma phyis /
T12TD4298E:83b-26: 'dra ba'i yi ge 'dus pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas ;
T12TD4298E:83b-35: ` k'a s'a di pra tya y'ant'a d'am krasbh'u pa ra: kri aasa\ bh'u rkyen mtha' can pha rol las k'a sa la sogs pa rnams la a'a ma'o //
T12TD4298E:83b-36: byings kri aasa\ bh'u rnams napa\ sogs kyi rkyen mtha' can dang sbyor ba las k'a sa la sogs pa rnams kyi mthar a'ama\ rkyen du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:83b-37: k'a sri ngan du smra ba la'o zhes pa'i byings la rkyen a'ama\/
T12TD4298E:83b-40: aasa\/ bh'u rnams napa\ sogs kyi mtha' can dang sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:83b-45: ` tsak'a sri snang byed la'o zhes pa'i byings la /
T12TD4298E:83b-48: tsa k'a s'am ba bh'u ba /
T12TD4298E:83b-49: ` dza gri gnyid zad pa la'o zhes pa la /
T12TD4298E:83b-50: a'ama\ byings mtha'i yon tan byas pas /

T12TD4298E:92b-1: ('ongs so grub zin gsar pa dang zas bya bas rdzogs pa/) ....aa bhokshya dbha b'anya dya ga mi shyatra/....(gang khyed ni zas la 'ongs so/) ` du pa tsashra 'tshed pa la /

T12TD4298E:92b-8: pr'a dzva lishyana\ sogs te byings te gnyis nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni //
T12TD4298E:92b-9: aa pakshyadbha b'an++ya dyagni: pr'a dzva li shyatra/....(khyod kyis tshos shig gang du me rab tu 'bar ro/) ` hana\ 'tshe ba la /
T12TD4298E:92b-10: hana\ ri ta las sya ba la'os /
T12TD4298E:92b-14: aa ha ni shyana\ sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:92b-16: aa shkshyatra aa sha kshya t'am /
T12TD4298E:92b-17: aa sha kshna\ sogs te byings de gnyis nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:92b-18: aa ha ni shyadbha b'anya dya shakshyatra/....(khyed rang nus pa ji tsam pa choms shig/) sogs te rnam dbye'i ngo bo dipa\ sogs dang rkyen syapa\ aa yig mtha' can yin pas aapa\ bi k'a ra na sogs kyi rigs 'gre bas cho ga rnams rtogs sla'o //
T12TD4298E:92b-19: ai ti sva ra svasti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'i tkri y'a ti kra ma sya pra ty'a ya pra kri ya sa m'a pt'a:/
T12TD4298E:92b-20: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las bya ba shor ba'i rkyen gyi rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:92b-21: ` // de nas 'das pa'am sngon byung ba'i rkyen gyi rnam dbye rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:92b-24: byings las 'das pa'am byung zin tsam gyi don brjod pa la dipra sogs rnam dbye bco brgyad po 'gyur zhing bar rkyen si yang spyin par bya la 'byung zin de yang 'das nas dus yun ring song ba la 'jug pa shas che ste /
T12TD4298E:92b-25: ` bh'u yod pa la rnam dbye dipa\ bar rkyen si /
T12TD4298E:92b-27: dipra sogs la aata byin pas /
T12TD4298E:92b-28: aa bh'usa\ dra ces gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:92b-30: pa la d'a la sogs pa las so //
T12TD4298E:92b-31: pa ste rnam dbye bar smee pa dang rnams pha rol la byings d'a /
T12TD4298E:92b-36: p'a rnams las pha rol gyi si ni dbyi bar bya ste /

T12TD4298E:93a-0: rnam dbye dbyangs thog ma can pha rol si phyis pa las bh'u la buka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bshad @93a * //
T12TD4298E:93a-5: de rnams dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:93a-11: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:93a-12: aa bh'udbrishtam:....(sngon char bab/) du d'anya\ sbyin pa la'ang de bzhin du bsgrubs pas skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:93a-19: ` sy'a bi da: si la a'a dang bdi las so //
T12TD4298E:93a-20: rkyen si phyis pa la byings a'a ring mtha' can dang byings bdi las pha rol gyi rnam dbye aan ni ausa\ zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:93a-22: ` au sy'a lo pa: aus la a'a dbyi'o //
T12TD4298E:93a-23: aana\ bsgyur ba'i aus pha rol la byings mtha'i a'a ring ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:93a-25: aa du: lhag ma rnams la /
T12TD4298E:93a-31: de bzhin du du dh'anra 'dzin pa la /
T12TD4298E:93a-34: aa dhu: aa dh'a: aa dh'a tam /
T12TD4298E:93a-38: ` de bzhin du shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la /
T12TD4298E:93a-45: si dbyi ba las aina\ ni g'a zhes par 'gyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:93a-50: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:93a-51: (kye 'jig sar ma 'gro khang bzang dbenpar ma 'gro zhig/) ....aa re m'a g'a: s'a dhva sam m'a g'am garbi ta mandi ram /
T12TD4298E:93a-56: ` / gha ta rtsed mo la'o zhes pa'i byings la a'atma ne pa da rnams sbyar /
T12TD4298E:93a-58: aa gha tisa\ tana\ zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:93a-59: dgag pa'i don gyi m'a sngon du gzhag /
T12TD4298E:93a-61: dgag pa'i don gyi m'a sngon ma las dipa\ sogs kyi aata\ ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:93a-63: ku ai la sogs kyis sa\ sha\/
T12TD4298E:93a-65: ta\ ta\ra bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:93b-0: de bzhin du gnyis tshig @93b dang mang tshig la /
T12TD4298E:93b-3: skyes bu dbus ma'i gcig tshig dang gnyis tshig la /
T12TD4298E:93b-4: m'a gha tishth'a: m'a gha ti sh'a th'am /

T12TD4298E:93b-9: rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams pha rol la spyir btang si dbyi ba ma yin kyang de'i dmigs bsal rnam dbye dha yig pha rol la a'atma ne pa da yin na'ang si dbyi bar bya ste /

T12TD4298E:93b-22: aata\/ sma sngon du bzhag de nas aata phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:93b-23: sma bh'u ta/....(byung zin nam 'byung bar 'gyur/) ` byings du kri nyral /
T12TD4298E:93b-25: aa kri sa\ da\ ces gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:93b-28: byings ri yig mtha' can sogs byings mang po zhig las pa ste pa rasmee pa da rnams pha rol la si ni na 'gro ba'i ming can zhes tha snyad byed de dgos pa ni byings la 'phel ba byed pa'i don te /
T12TD4298E:93b-31: rkyen si las pha rol gyi rnam dbye dipa\ dang sipa\ la a'ita\ a'a ga ma 'gyur te /

T12TD4298E:93b-45: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:93b-46: nyer bsgyur nir\ sngon du bzhag pas /
T12TD4298E:93b-47: sva dzny'a nam yo g'i ni ra k'arsh'itra/.... (rang gi ye shes rnal 'byor rnam par grol bsgom mo//) ` de bzhin du nyer bsgyur ba ri sngon ma'i hrinyra 'tsho ba la /

T12TD4298E:94a-1: sa t'a sogs kyis aita\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:94a-3: aisa\ a'ida\ ces gnas pa la /

T12TD4298E:94a-17: ` nyer bsgyur pra sngon ma'i pra dza\ rku ba la'ang de dang 'dra bar bsgrubs pas /

T12TD4298E:94a-40: ` / sha ma dang da ma nye bar zhi ba la /
T12TD4298E:94a-43: aa sha mi shu: sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:94a-47: ` / kra mu rkang pa bskyod pa la /
T12TD4298E:94a-62: aa shva si shu: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:94a-63: ` / dz'a gri gnyid sangs pa la /
T12TD4298E:94a-66: aa dz'a ga ri shu: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:94a-70: aa ha si shta: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:94b-4: ` /du krinyra byed pa la a'atma ne pa da'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig ta si aata\ rnams sbyar bas /

T12TD4298E:94b-8: byings aita mi 'jug pa byings mtha' dbyangs thung ngu yin pa las pha rol gyi si ni rnam dbye dzaha sa so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge dang po can pha rol la dbyi bar bya ste /

T12TD4298E:94b-33: ` / nyer bsgyur aa dhi sngon ma'i aing kha ton byed pa la'ang a'atma ne pa da rnams sbyor ba las /

T12TD4298E:95a-0: byings dzha sa so sor bsdu ba'i mtha' las pha rol gyi si ni rnam dbye dzha sa so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge dang po can pha rol @95a * //

T12TD4298E:95a-52: rkyen gyi nga bar mtshams bzung ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:95a-53: dhra aa la 'dren pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:95a-57: aa ru dha: aa ru dha tam /

T12TD4298E:95b-12: aa sa b'itra: aa se bisht'am /
T12TD4298E:95b-13: aa se bi shu: sogs so /

T12TD4298E:95b-23: byung zin gyi rnam dbye'i skabs 'dir rkyen dang rnam dbye dzha sa'i yi ge dang po pha rol la byings dri sha la sogs pa rnams la yon tan byas pa'i aar ni ra zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:95b-24: byings kyi ri aara\ de ra ru bsgyur /

T12TD4298E:95b-45: ` ; bhi dira\ 'joms pa la aita mi 'jug pa ra smee pa da rnams la /

T12TD4298E:95b-50: a'atma ne pa da rnams la /
T12TD4298E:95b-52: aita\ med pa'i rkyen si dang s'ishta sogs pha rol la byings kyi au pa dh'a la yon tan 'byung ba ma yin te /
T12TD4298E:95b-53: byings la yon tan mi byed rnam dbye dzha sa dang po can rnams la si dbyi ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:95b-62: ` / bri tu 'jug pa la a'atma ne pa da rnams sbyor ba las /
T12TD4298E:95b-63: aita\ ster ba sogs kyis bsgrubs bas /
T12TD4298E:95b-67: aa birtishth'a: aa brti sh'a th'am /
T12TD4298E:96a-0: ` ga mli dang sripli 'gro ba la'ang par smee pa da rnams sbyor ba @96a * //

T12TD4298E:96a-54: dhraka\/ sa shar bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /

T12TD4298E:96a-67: ` krisha\ 'grugs pa'am gshor gtod pa la /
T12TD4298E:96a-71: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'adbh'u ta pra ty'a ya pra kri ya sa m'apt'a:/
T12TD4298E:96a-72: zhes ba brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las byung zin gyi rkyen gyi rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:96a-73: ` // de nas dngos po dang las kyi don sogs kyi rnam dbye 'jug tshul rnams rab tu brjod par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:96b-0: sngar bshad zin gyi dngos po @96b dang las kyi don gyi 'jug tshul dang cho ga rnams ni byings thams cad pa rnams kyi cho ga yin la /

T12TD4298E:96b-6: napa\ sogs la bh'u aa dag gi a'a 'os /
T12TD4298E:96b-13: kri sogs las napa\ sogs la'os /

T12TD4298E:96b-16: aa nu ba bh'u b'a te /
T12TD4298E:96b-17: aa nu ba bh'u bi re /
T12TD4298E:96b-18: aa nu ba bh'u bi she /
T12TD4298E:96b-19: aa nu ba bh'u b'a the /
T12TD4298E:96b-20: aa nu ba bh'u bi dhve /

T12TD4298E:96b-24: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /

T12TD4298E:96b-53: tshig grogs dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /

T12TD4298E:96b-58: gtsang byed gang dang gang yin ba //

T12TD4298E:96b-61: gnyis brjod thung ngu'os thung du dang /

T12TD4298E:97a-1: byings dbyangs kyi mtha' can rnams dang han dang grahra dang dri sha la sogs pa rnams la dngos po dang las kyi don la /

T12TD4298E:97a-8: aa nu bh'a bish'i ranra sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:97a-10: aa nu bha bi sh'i y'ast'am /

T12TD4298E:97a-14: sh'a yi sh'ishta sogs dang sha yi sh'ishta sogs so /
