T12TD4298E:97a-28: aa nu bha bi t'a ra: aa nu bha bi t'a se sogs so /
T12TD4298E:97a-29: ` /'byung 'gyur gyi rnam dbye rnams la'ang yang na bar byas pas /
T12TD4298E:97a-30: aa nu bh'a bi shya te sogs sam /
T12TD4298E:97a-31: aa nu bha bishya te sogs so //
T12TD4298E:97a-32: de bzhin du bya ba shor ba'i don gyi rnam dbye syapa\ dang bcas pa'i dipa\ sogs la'ang 'phel ba dang yon tan yang na bar byas pas /
T12TD4298E:97a-33: aa nva bh'a bi shya ta /
T12TD4298E:97a-34: aa nva bh'a bi shye t'am /
T12TD4298E:97a-35: aa nva bh'a bi shya ta sogs sam /
T12TD4298E:97a-36: aa nva bha bi shya ta /
T12TD4298E:97a-38: aa nva bha bi shya ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:97a-39: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:97a-40: (rjes su zhugs shig gang du khyod de kho na nyid nyan pa la/) ....aa nva bh'a bi shya ta tva ya ta tvam ya dya shro shyatra /
T12TD4298E:97a-41: ` byung zin gyi don gyi a'atma ne pa da'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:97a-43: byed pa po ma yin pa las tana\ la aina\'o //
T12TD4298E:97a-44: byings las byed pa po'i don ma yin pa'i dngos po dang las kyi don las rnam dbye tanra la byung zin gyi rnam dbye'i bar rkyen si'i yul la aina\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:97b-3: ai tan zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:97b-5: rkyen aina\ las pha rol gyi rnam dbye tan ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:97b-10: 'phel ba dang yon tan 'dam kha can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-11: aa nva bh'a bi sh'a t'am /
T12TD4298E:97b-13: aa nva bh'a bishth'a: aa nva bh'a bish'a th'am /
T12TD4298E:97b-16: aa nva bh'a bi shva ti /
T12TD4298E:97b-18: yang na yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-20: aa nva bha bi sha ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:97b-21: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:97b-22: aa nva bh'a bi bha bo bha ....(nor 'go bar 'byung ngo khyed la /
T12TD4298E:97b-24: de bzhin du du krinyra byed pa la'ang na 'gro ba'i phyogs la aita\ dang 'phel ban 'gro ba ma yin pa'i phyogs la ait mi ster ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-27: aa k'a ri sha ta sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:97b-31: ` nyer bsgyur nira\ dang a'anga\ sngon du bzhag na /
T12TD4298E:97b-32: ni r'a k'a ri sogs so /
T12TD4298E:97b-33: ` / de bzhin du hri nyra 'tshe ba la /
T12TD4298E:97b-36: aa h'a ri sha ta sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:97b-41: aita\ mi 'jug dzha sa dang po can rnams la si dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-47: a'atma ne pa da'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:97b-49: ai tana\ zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:97b-50: ` au pa dh'a ya la gho: au ba dh'a thung du las so //
T12TD4298E:97b-51: rkyen aina\ pha rol la byings kyi au pa dh'a n'a mi'i yi ge thung du yin na 'phel ba mi byed par yon tan bya ste /
T12TD4298E:97b-54: lhag ma rnams la'ang aita\ mi 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-55: dzha sa la si dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-60: ` / nyer bsgyur nira\ dang a'ang sngon ma'i dhrinya 'dzin pa la aita\ sbyor ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-63: ni r'a dh'a ri sha ta /
T12TD4298E:97b-64: nyer bsgyur pra ti sngon ma'i pa da 'gro ba la aati\ mi 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:97b-65: dzha sa dang po rnams la si dbyi ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:98a-5: aa bha ni sha ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98a-11: ` / grah nye bar len pa la /
T12TD4298E:98a-12: na 'gro ba'i ming can du yang na bar byed pas /
T12TD4298E:98a-17: aa gra hi sh'a t'am sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98a-18: ` / nyer bsgyur nir\ sngon ma'i n'inya 'dren pa la /
T12TD4298E:98a-20: ni ra n'a yi sh'a t'am /
T12TD4298E:98a-21: ni ra n'a yi sha ta /
T12TD4298E:98a-22: ni ra n'a yishth'a: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98a-23: ` / pa' btung ba la byung zin gyi rnam dbye rnams sbyor ba las /
T12TD4298E:98a-26: byung zin gyi rnam dbye nya yi dang na yi dang pa yig 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol las byings a'a yig mtha' can la yukra a'a ga ma ster bar byas te /
T12TD4298E:98a-32: ` de bzhin du shn'a gtsang byed la /
T12TD4298E:98a-37: ` nyer bsgyur ni sngon ma'i du dh'anya 'dzin pa la /
T12TD4298E:98a-42: ` / pa dang 'gro ba sogs la dngos po dang las kyi don du ma zad byed pa po'i don du yang si'i yul la tana\ pha rol la aina\ 'gyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:98a-43: nyer bsgyur auta\ sngon du bzhag pas /
T12TD4298E:98a-48: ` / bu dha khongs su chud pa la /
T12TD4298E:98a-53: ` / byings dza ni dang bu dhi dag la aita\ dang bcas pa'i si dang ai na la 'phel ba mi byed bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:98a-57: aa dza ni shth'a: sogs so //
T12TD4298E:98a-58: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'adbha ba ka rma sya pra kri y'a sa m'apt'a: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyings can gyi mdo las dngos po dang las kyi rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:98a-59: ` // de nas byings byings su sgrub pa dang ming byings su sgrub par byed pa'i rkyen rnams kyi 'jug yul dang cho ga rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:98a-60: ` aa ti sha ye na ha s'a der++yanga\ dvishtsa /
T12TD4298E:98a-61: has dang po las phul du byung ba la yanga\ te gnyis kyang ngo //
T12TD4298E:98a-62: byings has so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge dang po can la phul du byung ba dang yang yang gi don la byings byings su sgrub pa'i rkyen yang 'gyur zhing /
T12TD4298E:98b-0: rkyen yang pha rol la byings @98b de'ang gnyis su 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:98b-1: bh'u la yanga\ nga a'atma na pa da sbyor ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:98b-3: dzha pa rnams kyi dza ba dang tsa pa 'os /
T12TD4298E:98b-5: b'u bh'u ya zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:98b-8: byings kyi dang po n'a mi'i dbyangs ni rkyen yang pha rol la yon tan du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:98b-12: yang la sogs pa'i rkyen sbyar ba de la'ang byings zhes zer ro //
T12TD4298E:98b-13: des na byings de tshig tu bsgrub pa'i phyir rnam dbye rnams sbyor ba las /
T12TD4298E:98b-14: aapa\ bi ka ra na sbyor ba sogs gong ltar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:98b-22: bo bh'u ye ran sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:98b-27: de ring ma yin pa lang la /
T12TD4298E:98b-30: aa bo bh'u yanta sogs so //
T12TD4298E:98b-31: de bzhin du bhudza\ skyong ba la /
T12TD4298E:98b-33: bo bhu dzye ta/...(ling) bo bhu dzya t'am/...(lot) aa bo bhu dzya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-35: bo bh'u shya te/...(lat) bo bhu she te/...(ling) bo bh'u shya t'am /
T12TD4298E:98b-36: aa bo bhu ...(lang) shya ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-37: ` mu ha sems nyams pa la /
T12TD4298E:98b-41: aa mo mu ...(lang) hya ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-46: aa le li hya te sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-50: dzo hu ya t'am/...(lot) aa dzo hu ya ta ...(lang) sogs so ;
T12TD4298E:98b-55: aa be bi dya ...(lang) ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-56: ` /du pa tsasha\ 'tshed pa la yang gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:98b-57: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po /
T12TD4298E:98b-59: byings gnyis brjod pa'i dang po'i dbyangs aa thung ni rkyen yang pha rol la ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:98b-60: pa gong ma ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:98b-64: aa p'a pa ...(lang) tsya ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:98b-65: ` / de bzhin du patha gsal bar brjod pa la /
T12TD4298E:98b-70: ` / byings dbyangs dang po can la'ang /
T12TD4298E:98b-74: ri sogs la yanga\ 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:98b-75: ` aata\ 'gro ba la yanga\ gnyis brjod pas /
T12TD4298E:98b-76: aata\ aata\ ya zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:98b-77: ` sva r'a de: pa r: dbyangs dang po'i pha rol lo //
T12TD4298E:98b-78: rkyen yang sogs pha rol la byings kyi dang po dbyangs rkyang ba yin na gnyis brjod pa'i gsal byed de yang mi dbyi zhing dbyangs dang po de las pha rol gyi dbyangs phyi ma de slar yang gnyis su 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:99a-1: phyi ma slar yang gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:99a-2: 'dra ba'i yi ge 'dus pa la ring po sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:99a-3: aa t'a tya te/...(lat) aa t'a tya ta/...(ling) aa t'a ty'a t'am/...(lota) a'a t'a tya ta ...(lang) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99a-4: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:99a-5: aa t'a tya te dhrishta:....(phul du byung ba'i ci brtol/) ` de bzhin du aa sha za ba la /
T12TD4298E:99a-6: aa sh'a shya te/...(lata) aa sh'a shye ta/...(ling) aa sh'a shya t'am/...(lota) a'a sh'a shya ta ...(lang) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:99a-8: aa r'ar++ya te/...(lat) aa r'ar++ye ta/...(ling) aa r'a r++ya t'am/...(lot) a'a r'a rya ta ...(ling) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-9: ` / nyer bsgyur pra sngon ma'i a'urnunyra 'gebs pa la /
T12TD4298E:99a-10: prorno n'u ya te/...(lat) prorno n'u ya ta/...(ling) prorno n'u ya t'am/...(lot) proo rno n'u ya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-11: ` / gamli 'gro ba la yang gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:99a-12: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:99a-16: nya ma dang dzha pa rnams la nukra'o //
T12TD4298E:99a-17: byings nya ma so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge'i mtha' can dang nya ma'i mtha' can ma yin kyang dzha pa so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge gnyis brjod pa'i dang po la rkyen yang pha rol las nukra a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:99a-19: dzam ga mya te/..(lat) dzam ga mya ta/...(ling) dzam ga mya t'am/...(lot) aa dzam ga mya ta ...(lang) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99a-20: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:99a-21: (rta 'gros phul du byung ba/) ....dzam ga mya te tu ram ga: de bzhin du bhra mu g-yo ba la /
T12TD4298E:99a-22: bam bhra mya te/...(lat) bam bhra mye ta/...(ling) bam bhra mya t'am/...(lot) aa bam bhra mya ta ...(lang) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:99a-24: dzam gha n+ya te/...(lat) dzam gha n+ye ta/...(ling) dzam gha n+ya t'am/...(lot) aa dzam gha n+ya ta ...(lang) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:99a-25: yang na han 'tshe ba'i don brjod pa la yang pha rol la ghn'i zhes par sgyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:99a-26: ghn'i ru bsgyur ba'i phyogs la /
T12TD4298E:99a-27: dze ghn'i ya te/...(lat) dze ghn'i ye ta/...(ling) dze ghn'i ya t'am/...(lot) aa dze ghn'i ya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-28: ` / dzapa\ dang dzalpa lhag par smra ba la /
T12TD4298E:99a-29: dza dza pya te/...(lat) dzam dza bye ta/...(ling) dzam dza pya t'am/...(lot) aa dzam dza pya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-30: ` / dzam dzalpya te/...(lat) dzam dzalpye ta/...(ling) dzam dzalpya t'am/...(lot) aa dzam dzalpya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-31: ` / da ha thal bar byed pa la ;
T12TD4298E:99a-32: dam da hya te/...(lat) da da hye ta/...(ling) dam da hya t'am/...(lot) aa dam da hya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-34: yam ya bhya te/...(lat) yam ya bhye ta/...(ling) yam ya bhya t'am/...(lot) aa yam ya bhya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99a-35: ` / dam sha snun pa la yang /
T12TD4298E:99a-36: ` no lo pa: na ni dbyi'o //
T12TD4298E:99a-37: byings kyi au pa dh'a'i na yig ni rkyen ha sa dang po kra yig dang nga yig 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:99a-39: nya ma dang dzha pa rnams la nukra'os /
T12TD4298E:99a-40: nukra a'a ga ma ster ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:99a-41: dam da shya te/...(lat) dam da shye ta/...(ling) dam da shya t'am/...(lot) aa dam da shu ta ...(lang) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99a-42: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar ba'i dpe ni /
T12TD4298E:99a-43: dam da shya te ma sha ka:....(sha sprang gis rmugs pa/) ` de bzhin du bham dzu 'joms pa la /
T12TD4298E:99b-0: bam bha dzya te/...(lat) bam bha dzye ...(ling) @99b ta ;
T12TD4298E:99b-1: bam bha dzya t'am/...(lot) aa bam bha dzya ta ...(lang) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99b-2: bam bha dzya te brto dant'i ta ram/...(so ldan myos pas shing 'joms par byed/) ` nri t'i lus bskyod pa la yang sbyar /
T12TD4298E:99b-4: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po /
T12TD4298E:99b-5: nri nritra ya zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:99b-6: ` r'i gri du pa: dh'a sya /
T12TD4298E:99b-8: byings ritra au pa dh'a can gnyis brjod pa'i thog ma de la yang pha rol las r'ika\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:99b-10: ri aa'os ri aara\ bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:99b-14: (lang) ...aa na r'i nri tya ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99b-15: na r'i nri tya te na ta:....(gar mkhan lhag par gar sgyur ro//) ` de bzhin du bri tu 'jug pa la /
T12TD4298E:99b-19: (lang) ...aa ba r'i bri tya ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:99b-20: ba r'i bri tya te b'art'a su tsinta/....(sems dga' ba'i gtam la 'jug/) ` byings pa da/....('gro ba la'o/) sram sa\/....(/'og tu ltung ba la'o/) .... dhvamsa /
T12TD4298E:99b-25: skamda\ ....(/'gro ba la'o/) rnams la yang pha rol las gnyis brjod pa'i thog ma de la n'i kra a'a ga ma ster bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:99b-26: dgag pa'i na dang nyer bsgyur au pa sngon ma'i pa da 'gro ba la /
T12TD4298E:99b-27: (nye bar yang ma 'gro zhig/) ....no pa pa n'i pa dya te/...(lat) no pa pa n'i pa dye ta/...(ling) no pa pa n'i pa dya t'am/...(lot) no p'a pa n'i ba dya ta/...(lang) ` de bzhin du srasm dang dhvamsa 'og tu ltung ba la /
T12TD4298E:99b-28: sa n'i sra sya te/...(lat) sa n'i ...(ling) sra sye ta /
T12TD4298E:99b-29: sa n'i sra sya t'am/...(lot) aa sa n'i sra sya ta ...(lang) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:99b-30: ` da n'i dhvam sya te/...(lat) da n'i dhvam sye ta/...(ling) da n'i dhvam sya t'am/...(lot) aa da n'i dhvam sya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99b-32: ba n'i bam tsya te/...(lat) ba n'i bam tsye ta/...(ling) ba n'i bam tsya t'am/...(lot) aa ba n'i bam tsya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99b-33: ` / bhram sha 'og tu ltung ba la /
T12TD4298E:99b-34: ba n'i bhram shya te/...(lat) ba n'i bhram shye ta/...(ling) (lot) ...ba n'i bhram shya t'am /
T12TD4298E:99b-35: (lang) ...aa ba n'i bhram sha ta sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99b-42: tsa n'i ska dyate/...(lat) tsa n'i ska dye ta/...(ling) tsa n'i ska dya t'am/...(lot) aa tsa n'i ska dya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:99b-43: ` / tsar g-yo ba la yang sbyar ;
T12TD4298E:99b-45: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:99b-48: tsa ra pa lo rutsts'a sya /
T12TD4298E:99b-49: tsar pa la dag gi aa'i yang auta'o //
T12TD4298E:99b-50: byings tsa ra dang pa la dag gi yang pha rol las byings gnyis brjod pa'i dang po la nuka\ a'a gam 'gyur zhing mtha' ma'i aa yig kyang au yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:100a-3: tsam tsur++ya te/...(lat) tsam tsur++ya ta/...(ling) tsam tsur++ya t'am/...(lot) aa tsam tsur++ya ta ...(lang) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:100a-4: ` de bzhin du pha la rdzogs pa la /
T12TD4298E:100a-5: pam phu lya te/...(lat) pam phu lye ta/...(ling) pam phu lye t'am/...(lot) aa pam phu lya ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:100a-6: ` /du krinyra byed pa la yang sbyar pas /
T12TD4298E:100a-8: ` ri to ri: ri ta kyi bi'o //
T12TD4298E:100a-9: byings ri yig mtha' can ni yang pha rol la ri ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:100a-10: ri ri gnyis brjod sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po /
T12TD4298E:100a-13: ya la 'os phyi ma ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:100a-14: tse kr'i ya te/...(lat) tse kr'i ye ta/...(lang) tse kr'i ya t'am/...(lot) aa tse kr'i ya ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:100a-15: aa ti sha ye na ka ro t'i ti zhes pa'i don la/....('di phul du byung bar byed do//) ....tse kr'i ya te//
T12TD4298E:100a-16: ` de bzhin du hrinyra 'phrog pa la /
T12TD4298E:100a-17: dze hr'i ya te/...(lat) dze hr'i ye ta/...(ling) dze hr'i ya t'am/...(lot) aa dze hr'i ya ta ...(lang) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:100a-19: be br'i ya te/...(lat) be br'i ye ta/...(ling) be br'i ya t'am/...(lot) aa be br'i ya ta ...(lang) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:100a-20: aa ti sha ye na bri no t'i ti ....('di phul du byung bar gang ba'am shin tu gang ba'o//) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:100a-21: be br'i ya te/....('di phul du byung bar gang ba'am shin tu gang ba'o//) ` mring srog gtong ba la /
T12TD4298E:100a-25: aa me mr'i ya ta sogs te /
T12TD4298E:100a-26: aa ti sha ya na mri ya te ....(shin tu shi ba'o//) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:100a-27: me mr'i ya te/....(shin tu shi ba'o//) ` du d'anyra sbyin pa la yang /
T12TD4298E:100a-28: d'a sogs kyi ai 'os a'a ai gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:100a-30: ya la 'os phyi ma ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:100a-31: de d'i ya te/...(lat) de d'i ye ta/...(ling) de d'i ya t'am/...(lot) aa de d'i ya ta/...(lang) ` de bzhin du p'a btung ba la /
T12TD4298E:100a-32: pe p'i ya te/...(lat) pe p'i ye ta/...(ling) pe p'i yam t'am/...(lot) aa pe p'i ya ta ...(lang) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:100a-33: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'a dya dpraty'a ya bra kri ya sa m'apt'a:/
T12TD4298E:100a-34: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las yanga\ rkyen gyi rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:100a-35: ` // de nas yang rkyen 'jig pa rnams kyi bya ba rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:100a-36: ` b'a n+ya tra lu ga nu brta te /
T12TD4298E:100a-37: gzhan la 'jig pa\ yang na rjes su 'jug go / kritra sogs kyi rkyen auka\ dang sbyor ba ma yin pa'i gzhan la yang na yanga\ 'jig pa\'i cho ga rjes su 'jug go ` / aa na bi tsa ha s'a tra /
