T12TD4298E:104b-16: aa shi tu mitstsha ti ....(zas bza' bar 'dod/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:104b-17: aa sha n'a ya ti/....(zas bza' bar 'dod/) ....aa shi shi sha ti /
T12TD4298E:104b-18: ` gu pu sbed ba la ste ngan tshig la'ang zhes pa la /
T12TD4298E:104b-19: gubbhya: gu pa rnams las so //
T12TD4298E:104b-26: d'ana\/ sh'ana\ rnams las rang gi don la sa rkyen du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:104b-29: dzu gupsa ti/...(lat) dzu gupseta\/...(ling) dzu gupsa tu/...(lot) ...dzu gupsa t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:104b-30: (lang) ...aa dzu gupsata\ sogs pa ra smee pa dang nga /
T12TD4298E:104b-31: (lat) ...dzu gupsa te sogs a'atma ne pa da rnams so /
T12TD4298E:104b-32: ` / de bzhin du ti dza bzod pa la /
T12TD4298E:104b-33: ti tiksha ti/...(lat) ti tiksheta\/...(ling) ti tiksha tu/...(lot) ...ti tiksha t'atra /
T12TD4298E:104b-36: ` / kita\ nad sangs pa la ste the tshom la yang ngo zhes pa la /
T12TD4298E:104b-37: tsi kit+sa ti/...(lat) tsi kit+seta\/...(ling) tsi kit+sa tu/...(lot) ...tsi kit+sa t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:104b-39: ` / m'an rnam par dpyod pa la /
T12TD4298E:104b-41: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po /
T12TD4298E:104b-42: sa la aa ai'os sngon ma'i aa ai /
T12TD4298E:104b-43: man sogs kyi dbyangs dang po de sa pha rol la ring por bsgyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:104b-44: ai ring por bsgyur ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:104b-45: m'i m'am sa ti/...(lat) m'i m'am seta\/...(ling) m'i m'am sa tu/...(lot) ...m'i m'am sa t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:104b-49: b'i bhat+sa ti/...(lat) b'i bhat+seta\/...(ling) b'i bhat+sa tu/...(lot) ...b'i bhat+sa t'atra /
T12TD4298E:104b-52: ` / d'an dang sh'an gzi brjid la /
T12TD4298E:105a-0: @105a * // d'i d'am sa te/...(lat) d'i d'am seta\/...(ling) d'i d'am sa t'am/...(lot) aa d'i d'am sa ta\ ...(lang) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:105a-1: sh'i sh'am sa te/...(lat) sh'i sh'am se ta/...(ling) sh'i sh'a sa t'a/...(lot) aa sh'i sh'am sa ta ...(lang) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105a-8: pana\/ pana\ rnams las dngos po dang rang gi don la rkyen a'a ya 'gyur la /
T12TD4298E:105a-9: a'a ya pha rol la byings gupa\ kyi dang po'i dbyangs de yon tan du 'gyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:105a-10: a'a ya sbyar yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:105a-11: go p'a ya ti/...(lat) go p'a yeta\/...(ling) go p'a ya tu/...(lot) ...go p'a ya t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:105a-13: de bzhin du dh'u pa ches gdungs pa la /
T12TD4298E:105a-14: dh'u p'a ya ti/...(lat) dh'u p'a yeta/... (ling) dh'u p'a ya tu/...(lot) ...dh'u p'a ya t'atra /
T12TD4298E:105a-17: bitstsh'a ya ti/...(lat) bitstsh'a yita\/...(ling) bitstsh'a ya tu/...(lot) ...bitstsh'a ya t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:105a-19: ` / pana\ dang pana\ 'du 'god dang bstod pa la /
T12TD4298E:105a-20: pa n'a ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:105a-21: pa n'a ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105a-22: ` / n'a m+no ya a'i ts'a sya /
T12TD4298E:105a-23: ming la ya ste aa'i yang a'i'o //
T12TD4298E:105a-24: ming la bdag nyid 'dod pa dang re smon gyi don la ming byings su bsgrub pa'i rkyen ya 'gyur zhing rkyen ya pha rol la ming dang byings kyi mtha'i dbyangs aa ni a'i ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105a-25: a'atma na: pu tra mitstsha te ....(bdag nyid bu 'dod/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105a-26: pu tr'i ya ti/....(bdag nyid bu 'dod/) dha na mitstsha ti ....(nor 'dod/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105a-27: dha n'i ya ti ...(nor 'dod/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:105a-28: ya rkyen pha rol la ming au da ka ni au danra zhes par bsgyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:105a-29: au da kamitstsha ti ...(chu 'dod/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105a-30: au da n+ya ti ....(chu 'dod/) ming las 'dod pa'i don la rkyen ka mya'ang 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:105a-31: pu tra mitstsha ti ....(bu 'dod par byed/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105a-32: pu traka mya ti ....(bu 'dod par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105a-33: ` / ka ra no tsa ya: byed pa la'ang ya'o //
T12TD4298E:105a-34: byings kandu la sogs pa rnams las byed pa'i don la'ang rkyen ya 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105a-35: kandu ka ro ti zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105a-38: byed pa po la nyi da 'gro ba'o //
T12TD4298E:105b-0: ming gi byings gha ta la sogs pa rnams la byed pa po'i don la rkyen nyi @105b 'gyur zhing nyi de la'ang da 'gro ba'i ming can zhes bya'o /
T12TD4298E:105b-3: spyir btang nya 'gro ba la 'phel ba thob kyang de'i dmigs bsal rkyen nyi la 'phel ba mi 'byung zhing byings kyi dang po'i dbyangs de ring po yin na thung ngur 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105b-5: de da 'gro ba yin pas ti phyis /
T12TD4298E:105b-7: aapra bi k'a ra na sbyar yon tan sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:105b-8: gha ta ya ti ....(bum pa byed/) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:105b-9: gha tam ka ro ti ....(bum pa byed/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105b-10: gha ta ya ti ....(bum pa byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:105b-11: mah'antam ka ro ti ....(chen po byed do//) zhes pa'i don la ma ha ya ti/....(chen po byed do//) baha thob pa la nyi /
T12TD4298E:105b-12: ba ha a'u dha ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:105b-13: a'u dhi ka ro ti ....(thob par byed do//) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:105b-14: a'u dha ya ti/....(thob par byed do//) ` pri th'a der: pri tha sogs kyi ra'o //
T12TD4298E:105b-15: rkyen nyi pha rol la byings pri tha sogs kyi dbyangs ri ni ra ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105b-16: pri tha la nyi ri rara\ bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:105b-17: pra tha ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-18: ` / de bzhin du dri dha la /
T12TD4298E:105b-19: dra dha ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-20: ` / byings la rang gis byed pa'am gzhan byed du 'jug pa'i bya ba'i don la'ang rkyen nyi 'gyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:105b-21: ` du krinyra byed pa la nyi /
T12TD4298E:105b-23: aapa\ sbyor ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:105b-24: ka ra ya ti sogs so //
T12TD4298E:105b-25: de bzhin du b'a tsa ya ti dang /
T12TD4298E:105b-26: aa nu sngon ma'i sh'a su rjes su bstod pa la /
T12TD4298E:105b-27: aa nu sh'a sa ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-28: ` / hana\ 'tshe ba dang 'gro ba la nyi sbyar /
T12TD4298E:105b-31: byings han ni ain rkyen med pa'i rkyen nyra yig dang na\ yig 'gro ba'i ming can dang dbyangs dang bo can pha rol la ghata\ ces par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105b-32: hana\ gha ta\ tu bsgyur aapa\ sbyor ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:105b-33: gha ta ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-38: byings sada\ ni rkyen nyi pha rol la shata\ ces par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:105b-40: au pa dh'a 'phel ba byas pas /
T12TD4298E:105b-41: sh'a ta ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-43: ri a'atra las nyi la buka\'o //
T12TD4298E:105b-44: byings ri dang a'ata\ mtha' la nyi pha rol las puka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:105b-45: ` du d'anyra sbyin pa la nyi sbyar puka\ a'a ga ma byin pas /
T12TD4298E:105b-46: d'a pa ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:105b-48: sth'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-2: y'a pa ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106a-5: puka\ pha rol la ri la yon tan byed par bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:106a-7: ` / byings hr'i kl'i r'i ai ngi kr'i dzi l'i rnams la nyi pha rol la puka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:106a-8: ` hr'i ngo tsha ba la nyi sbyar puka\ byin yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:106a-11: nyi puka\ a'a ga ma byin /
T12TD4298E:106a-12: kl'i pa ai zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:106a-15: kl'i nas l'i'i bar gyi byings de rnams kyi ai yig dag ni puka\ pha rol la a'a ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:106a-16: kl'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-17: ` de bzhin du r'ing nyan pa la /
T12TD4298E:106a-18: r'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-19: ` aa dhi sngon ma'i yid klog pa la /
T12TD4298E:106a-20: aa dhy'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-22: kr'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-24: dz'a pa ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-27: bi l'a pa ya ti sogs so//
T12TD4298E:106a-28: ` / pa ta sogs la nyi pha rol las puka\ gi yul la yuka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:106a-31: p'a ya ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106a-34: shing gi rtag tu yon tan nos /
T12TD4298E:106a-36: mtshams sbyor gyi yi ge sogs kyis de a'a ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:106a-37: sh'a ya ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-38: ` de bzhin du sho phra mor byed pa la'ang mtshams sbyor gyi yi ge sogs kyis ao a'a ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:106a-39: sh'a ya ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106a-40: ` / pr'inyra dang dh'u nyra dag la nyi pha rol la nuka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bshad de nukra byin pas /
T12TD4298E:106a-41: pr'i na ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106a-42: dh'u na ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106a-43: ` / dz'a na sogs kyi dbyangs nyi pha rol la yang na thung ngur bsgyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:106a-44: ` dzny'a khongs su tshud pa la /
T12TD4298E:106a-46: puka\ a'a ga ma byin thung ngur bsgyur ba dang mi bsgyur ba 'dam ka can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:106a-47: dzny'a pa ya ti sogs sam /
T12TD4298E:106a-48: dznya pa ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106a-49: ` / dz'a na la sogs pa rnams kyi pukra dang bcas pa'i sa pha rol la ais su bsgyur ba dang mi bsgyur ba 'dam ka can du bshad de /
T12TD4298E:106a-50: ais su ma bsgyur ba'i phyogs la /
T12TD4298E:106a-52: dzi dzny'a pa yi sha te sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106b-0: ais su @106b bsgyur ba'i phyogs la nyi dang aita\ mi 'jug gnyis brjod pa'i sngon ma phyis /
T12TD4298E:106b-1: ya\ ga\ sogs kyis ai sa\'i sa\ yang phyis ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:106b-3: ` / tsu r'a de rnyi: tsu ra sogs la nyi'o //
T12TD4298E:106b-4: byings tsu ra la sogs pa rnams las rang gi bya ba'i don la nyi rkyen du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:106b-8: yon tan sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:106b-9: tso ra ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106b-10: ` / de bzhin du p'a la bsrung ba la /
T12TD4298E:106b-11: p'a la ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106b-13: tsi ta ya ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106b-15: ai 'gro ba sogs kyi numa\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:106b-19: tsu ra sogs nyi mtha' can la /
T12TD4298E:106b-20: a'atma ne pad rnams kyang 'jug par bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:106b-21: tsor ya te sogs kyang ngo /
T12TD4298E:106b-23: nyi dang aada\ las gnyis kyang ngo //
T12TD4298E:106b-24: byings las 'das pa tsam gyi don brjod pa la nyi mthar aada\ rkyen du 'gyur zhing aada\ dang lhan cig pa'i nyi pha rol la byings de gnyis su'ang brjod par bya la rnam dbye'ang de ring ma yin pa langa\ rnams sbyor te /
T12TD4298E:106b-29: sngon ma'i ha sa dang po lhag po /
T12TD4298E:106b-32: ai aad ces gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:106b-34: 'das pa'i don gyi skabs 'dir rkyen ka nga 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la nyi ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:106b-36: ` la gho d'irgha: thung ngu ring po'o //
T12TD4298E:106b-37: byings kyi thog ma'i dbyangs de thung ngu yin na rkyen aanga\ pha rol la ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:106b-38: tsu gong ma ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:106b-44: ` / de bzhin du bidra shes pa la /
T12TD4298E:106b-45: aa b'i bi data\ sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:106b-47: aa d'u du hata\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:106b-48: ` / aa di la gho hra sva au pa dh'a ya /
T12TD4298E:106b-49: aang la au pa dh'a thung du ni thung ngu'o //
T12TD4298E:106b-50: aanga\ dang bcas pa'i nyi pha rol la byings kyi au padh'a thung du de ni ring por mi bsgyur bar thung du nyid du gnas shing aanga\ pha rol la byings kyi thog ma'i aa ni aira\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:107a-4: aa dz'i gha tana\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:107a-7: byings rita\ rjes 'brel can gyi au pa dh'a ni aanga\ pha rol la thung dur 'gyur ba ma yin te /
T12TD4298E:107a-12: thung du 'os dha gong ma'i aoo a'u /
T12TD4298E:107a-13: dzha pa sogs kyis dha da ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:107a-16: aa d'u dhoo kana\ sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:107a-18: aa ya y'a tsata\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:107a-22: rkyen nyi dang bcas pa'i aanga\ pha rol la byings baha\ la kti a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:107a-25: ya dza sogs kyi sam pra s'a ra nar bsgyur ha'i dha'os /
T12TD4298E:107a-28: ti dhisha\ tu sogs kyis de dha /
T12TD4298E:107a-29: nyi da 'gro ba yin pas dha'i ai phyis /
T12TD4298E:107a-31: dha'i dha la dbyi 'os dha gong ma phyis /
T12TD4298E:107a-32: dha phyi ma aanga\ gi aa la drang /
T12TD4298E:107a-33: nyi dang aangra las gnyis kyang ngos de gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:107a-35: dbyangs dang po aata\ sogs kyis slar yang aata\/
T12TD4298E:107a-39: ` aa ngi p'urba sya dha sya dza: aanga\ la sngon ma'i dha ni dza'o //
T12TD4298E:107a-40: rkyen aanga\ pha rol byings gnyis brjod pa'i sngon ma'i dha ni dza ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:107a-41: dha gong ma dza ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:107a-46: ` / nyer sgyur pra ti sngon ma'i shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la /
T12TD4298E:107a-49: aanga\/ d'a sogs kyis a'a ai ru bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:107a-50: pra tya tishtha yatra sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:107a-54: aanga\/ gong dang 'dra ba la nyi 'os nyi phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:107a-58: ` kri pe ro la: kri pa'i ra\ la'o //
T12TD4298E:107a-59: byings kri pa'i ra\ yig ni la yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:107a-60: yon tan ra\ la\ ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:107a-64: ` / yang bi sngon ma'i kri pu la nyi aanga\ dang bcas pa sbyar na /
T12TD4298E:107b-2: bya ts'i kli pa: sogs so //
T12TD4298E:107b-3: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'a tpra ty'a ya yukta pra kri yas m'apt'a: zhes pa brda sbrod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las rkyen dang sbyor ba'i rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:107b-4: ` // de nas kun nas bsgyur ba'i cho ga rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:107b-5: dri sh'a de: pa shy'a di: dri sha la sogs pa rnams kyi pa shyal sogs ba rnams so //
T12TD4298E:107b-16: d'a na sogs ni aapa\ bi k'a ra na sogs pha rol la rim pa bzhin /
T12TD4298E:107b-29: tipa\ aapa\ bi k'a ra na /
T12TD4298E:107b-30: dri shira\ pa shya ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:107b-38: ritstsha ti/...(lat) ritstsheta/...(ling) ritstshe tu/...(lot) ...ritstshe t'ata\/
T12TD4298E:107b-49: ` ghr'a dri nye bar len pa la /
T12TD4298E:107b-51: ` dhm'a sgra dang mi kun nas sbyor ba la /
T12TD4298E:107b-53: ` shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la /
T12TD4298E:107b-58: yatstsha ti sogs te aapa\ bam k'a ra na'i mtha' can yin pas cho ga rnams go sla'o /
T12TD4298E:107b-59: ` / ga m'am cha: gama\ rnams kyi che'o //
T12TD4298E:107b-62: yama\ rnams kyi mtha' ni tsha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:107b-70: ` / dzny'a dza n+yordz'a: dzny'a dzana\ dag gi dz'a'o //
T12TD4298E:107b-71: byings dzny'a khongs su chud pa dang dzana\ skye ba dag ni aapa\ bi k'a ra na sogs pha rol la dz'a zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:107b-73: di ba sogs kyi ya dang /
T12TD4298E:107b-74: kr'i sogs kyi n'a 'dam ka can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:107b-75: ` dzny'a khongs su chud pa la /
T12TD4298E:108a-1: ` / de bzhin du dzanra skye ba la'ang /
T12TD4298E:108a-6: byings shru ni aapa\ la sogs pa pha rol la shri zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:108a-7: shru thos pa la su sogs kyi nu bi k'a ra na shru shri ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:108a-9: ` / pv'a de hra sva: p'u la sogs pa'i thung du'o //
T12TD4298E:108a-10: byings p'unya la sogs pa rnams ni aapa\ sogs pha rol la thung dur 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:108a-12: n'a bi k'a ra na thung dur bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:108a-14: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'a d'a de sha pra kri ya sa m'a pt'a:/
T12TD4298E:108a-15: zhes ba brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las kun nas bsgyur ba'i rab tu bya ba rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:108a-16: ` // de nas byings dang nyer bsgyur sbyor tshul sogs bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-17: ni bi sh'a de: ni las bi sha sogs la'o //
T12TD4298E:108a-18: nyer bsgyur ni las pha rol gyi byings bi sha sogs la rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-19: bi sngon ma'i bi sha 'jug pa la /
T12TD4298E:108a-20: ni bi sha te ....(nges par 'jug par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108a-22: bi ba r'a dag las dzi la'o //
T12TD4298E:108a-23: nyer bsgyur bi dang pa r'a dag las pha rol gyi byings dzi rgyal nga las rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-24: bi dza ya te/....(rnam par rgyal bar byed/) pa r'a dza ya te/....(mchog tu rgyal bar byed/) nyer bsgyur pra ti /
T12TD4298E:108a-25: aa ba dang sam las pha rol gyi byings shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa dang /
T12TD4298E:108a-26: sam las pha rol gyi dri shir lta ba /
T12TD4298E:108a-27: ga mli 'gro ba shr'u thos pa /
T12TD4298E:108a-29: pritstsha shes par 'dod pa rnams la'ang rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-30: pratya ba tishtha te/....(so so kun nas gnas/) sam tashthi te/....(yang dag par gnas/) sam pa shya te/....(yang dag par lta bar byed/) sam gatstsha te/....(kun tu 'gro bar byed/) sam shri nu te/.... (gang dag par nyan par byed/) sam bitte/....(kun tu shes par byed/) sam pritstsha te/.... (kun nas 'dri bar byed/) nyer bsgyur a'angra las pha rol gyi pritstsha dang ta nu yang ba la'ang a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-31: a'a pritstsha te/....(kun tu 'dri bar byed/) a'a ta nu te ....(kun nas yang bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108a-33: n'a sya bi ha ra ne /
T12TD4298E:108a-34: a'anga\ las d'a la kha gdangs pa ma yin pa la'o //
T12TD4298E:108a-35: nyer bsgyur a'anga\ las pha rol gyi d'a la kha gdangs pa'i don ma yin pa la a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108a-36: a'a datte ....(kun tu sbyin par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:108a-37: kha gdangs pa'i don yin na pa ra smee pa da rnams sbyor bas /
T12TD4298E:108a-38: by'a da d'a ti tsata ....(bye'u tsata ka'i kha la sbyin par byed/) ka: mu ge ` kr'i do& nu sam pa ri bhya shtsa /
T12TD4298E:108b-0: aa nu sam pa ri rnams las kyang @108b kr'ida\ la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-1: nyer bsgyur aa nu sam pa ri rnams dang a'anga\ las kyang pha rol gyi kr'ida\ la a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-2: aa nu kr'i da te/....(mthun par rtse bar byed/) sam kr'i da te/....(legs par rtse bar byed/) pa ri kr'i da te/....(yongs su rtse bar byed/) a'a kr'i da te/....(kun tu rtse bar byed/) ` sa ma ba pro pa bi bhya: sth'a: sama\ aa ba pra au pa bi rnams las sth'a la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-3: nyer bsgyur sam dang aa ba dang pra dang au pa dang bi rnams las pha rol gyi shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la'ang a'atma ne ba da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-4: sam tishtha te/....(yang dag par gnas par byed/) aa ba tishtha te/....(kun tu gnas par byed/) pra tishtha te/....(rab tu gnas par byed/) au pa tishtha te/....(nye bar gnas par byed/) bi tishtha te ....(rnam par gnas par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108b-6: autra bi dag las ta pa la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-7: nyer bsgyur autra dang ji dag las pha rol gyi ta pa la'ang a'atma ne ba da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-8: autta pa te/....(shin tu gdung bar byed/) pi ta pa te ....(rnam par gdung bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108b-9: ` / a'a ngo ya ma ha na: a'anga\ las yama\ hana\ la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-10: nyer bsgyur a'anga las pha rol gyi yama\ dang hana\ dag la'ang a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-12: a'a yatstsha te ....(kun tu 'gog par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:108b-13: a'a sngon ma'i hanra 'tshe ba la /
T12TD4298E:108b-15: aa nu d'atta rnams dbyi ba nyid do //
T12TD4298E:108b-16: byings mtha'i aa nu d'atta ste skad gsang dma' bar 'don pa nya ma so sor bsdu ba rnams ni dzha sa'i yi ge kang 'gro ba rnams pha rol la dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-17: a'a ha te/....(kun tu snun par byed/) a'aghn'a te /
T12TD4298E:108b-24: a'a ham ma he sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108b-25: ` / au tashtsa rasty'a ge auta\ las tsar la 'don pa la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-26: nyer bsgyur autra las pha rol gyi tsar g-yo ba las 'don pa dang bcas pa'i don la a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-27: au tstsa ra te s'u tram/....(spyod cing gzhung 'don bar byed/) rnam dbye gsum pa'i mtha' can dang sbyor ba'i sam sngon ma'i tsa ra la'ang a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:108b-28: aa shve na sam tsa ra te/....(rtsa yis kun tu spyod par byed/) r'a the na sam tsa ra te/....(shing rtas kun tu spyod par byed/) ` by'a ba pa ri bhya: kri ya: bi aa ba pa ri rnams las kr'i la'o //
T12TD4298E:108b-29: nyer bsgyur bi dang aa ba dang pa ri rnams las pha rol gyi kr'e la a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:108b-30: bi kr'i n'i te/....(rnam par 'tshong bar byed/) aa ba kr'i n'i te/....(kun tu 'tshong bar byed/) pa ri kr'i n'i te ....(yongs su 'tshong bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:108b-31: ` / shapa\ khas mi len pa la'o zhes pi'i byings la'ang a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:108b-33: ` / dzny' shr'u smri dri sh'am s'anha n'a m'ata\/
T12TD4298E:109a-1: rnams sa mtha' can la a'ata\'o //
T12TD4298E:109a-2: byings dzny'a khongs su chud pa /
T12TD4298E:109a-5: dri shir lta ba rnams 'dod pa'i don gyi rkyen sa'i mtha' can la'ang a'ata\ de a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:109a-6: dzi dzny'a sa te gu nam/....(yon tan shes par 'dod/) shu shr'u sha te sva ram/....(dbyangs nyan par 'dod/) su sm'ursha te mi tram/....(grogs dran par 'dod/) di driksha te dza na bh'u m'i ....(skye yul lta bar 'dod/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:109a-7: ` / karma bya ti h'a re aa n+yata\ hids'a de r'ata\/
T12TD4298E:109a-8: 'tshe ba sogs las gzhan pa'i las gcig la 'jug pa la a'atra'o //
T12TD4298E:109a-9: 'tshe ba dang 'gro ba'i don dang byings pathra dang ha sa rnams las gzhan pa ste de rnams kyi don ma yin pa'i byed pa po dang bya ba du ma las gcig la byed pa gcig gis 'jug pa'i don la a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:109a-10: bi ba dante ba di na:....(rtsod par byed rtsod pa mkhan/) shr'addha bya ti bha ba te ....(shin tu dad par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:109a-11: 'tshe ba sogs la a'atma ne pa da mi 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:109a-12: bya ti ghanti/....(rnam par shin tu 'tshe bar byed/) bya ti gtstsha ti/....(rnam par shin tu 'gro bar byed/) bya ti ha santi/....(shin tu rnam par gnod par byed/) bya ti pa tha ti ....(shin tu rnam par klog par byed/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:109a-13: nyer bsgyur sngon ma'i kra mu rkang pa bskyod pa la pa ra smee pa da rnams 'jug cing au pa dh'a'ang ring por bsgyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:109a-14: sam kr'a ma ti/....(yang dag par gom pa 'dor bar byed/) au pa kr'a ma ti ....(nye bar gom pa 'dor bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:109a-15: ` / by'anga\ par++yu pe bhyo ra ma: bi a'anga\ pa ri au pa rnams las ra ma la'o //
T12TD4298E:109a-16: nyer bsgyur bi dang a'anga\ dang pa ri dang au pa rnams las pha rol gyi ra mu rtse ba la rnam dbye pa ra smee pa da rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:109a-17: bi ra ma ti/....(rnam par dga' bar byed/) a'a ra ma ti/....(kun nas dga' bar byed/) pa ri ra ma ti/....(yongs su dga' bar byed/) au pa ra ma ti ....(nye bar dga' bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:109a-19: britra rnams las sya sa dag la yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:109a-20: nyer bsgyur sngon ma'i byings bri tu bri dhu shri dhu syam du ka p'u rnams sya dang sa'i rkyen can la rnam dbye a'atma ne pa da rnams sbyor ba dang par smee pa da rnams sbyor ba yang na bar bya zhing aita\ ster mi ster 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:109a-34: lutshhhhhha\/ bida\/ lipa\/ sitshhha\/ krita\/ khida\/ shi sha rnams la aapa\ bi k'a ra na sogs pha rol las muma\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:109b-1: byings mtha' ai yig rjes 'brel 'gro ba la muma\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:109b-4: ` tu na di yongs su 'dzin pa la /
T12TD4298E:109b-7: bi di 'dud pa dang bstod pa la /
T12TD4298E:109b-9: ` sha ki ngo zhum pa la /
T12TD4298E:109b-11: ` / sha m'am d'i rgha: shama\ rnams kyi ring po'o //
T12TD4298E:109b-19: dama\/ tama\/ bhrama\/ shrama\/ kshama\/ klama\/ mada\ rnams kyi au pa dh'a ni aapa\ la sogs pa pha rol la ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:109b-20: ` sha mu dang dmu nye bar zhi ba la /
T12TD4298E:109b-21: dipa\ sogs kyi ya bi k'a ra na au ba dh'a ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:109b-33: lasha\/ bhr'a sha\ / shl'a sha rnams la aapa\ bi k'a ra na dang ya bi k'a ra na yang na bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:109b-35: aapra dang ya 'dam ka can du byas /
T12TD4298E:109b-43: ` / dusha\ log par spyod pa la rkyen nyi sbyor bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:109b-44: d'u sha ya ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:109b-46: rkyen ya pha rol la byings kyi ao yig ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:109b-47: ` do dum bur byed pa la dpri sogs kyi ya /
T12TD4298E:109b-51: sho phra mor byed pa la /
T12TD4298E:109b-55: ` / po ru ra: pu'i ri aura\'o //
T12TD4298E:109b-56: pu ste byings pa sde'i yi ge sngon na yod pa'i ri yig ni kang 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la aura\ du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:109b-58: 'dod pa'i don gyis ri aura\ gnyis brjod pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:109b-60: mring la sa rkyen dang lkog gyur gyi don la pa rasmee pa da rnams 'jug par bshad pa las /
T12TD4298E:109b-64: de gnyis las gzhan du a'atma ne pa da rnams 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:109b-66: ` / ru d'a de tsa turn'am hva s'a de: rud sogs las bzhi po rnams kyi ha dang ba sa la'o //
T12TD4298E:109b-67: byings rud la sogs pa las pha rol gyi rnam dbye byings thams cad pa'i ming can bzhi po rnams kyi rkyen dang rnam dbye ha yig dang ba sa'i yi ge dang po la aita\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:109b-68: ` ru dir\ dra mchi ma 'dzag pa la aanga\ sogs kyi aapa\ 'jig / ha dang ba sa'i yi ge dang po can la ait\ ster ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:110a-3: ru di tha: ru di tha /
T12TD4298E:110a-5: ru di ba:ru di ma:sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110a-6: de ring ma yin pa lang gi dipa\ dang sipa\ la a'ita\ dang aata\ 'dam ka can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:110a-9: aa ro d'i: aa ro da: sogs so //
T12TD4298E:110a-13: aa shva s'ita/...(lang) aa shva satra sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110a-14: ` nyi shva pa nyal ba la /
T12TD4298E:110a-15: sva pa ti/...(lat) aa sva p'ita\ ...(lang)/
T12TD4298E:110a-24: yang dzaksha sogs la aanta rnams kyi na dbyi ba dang aa na ausa\ su bsgyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:110a-26: de rnams ni rud la sogs pa ste ji skad du /
T12TD4298E:110a-27: sva ...(lat) pa ti tse ba shva ...(lat) si ti pr'a ni ti ta th'a ...(lat) dzakshi ti tsee ba bidznye yo ru d'a di: panytsa ko ga na /
T12TD4298E:110a-28: 'di dang 'dra bar sva pi ti yang ste //
T12TD4298E:110a-29: de bzhin shva si ti dang pr'a ni ti //
T12TD4298E:110a-30: dzakshi ti yang 'di 'drar shes bya ste //
T12TD4298E:110a-31: rud la sogs pa lnga po'i tshogs rnams so /
T12TD4298E:110a-32: ` / yang aanta dang aa na (aantam aanra) bsgyur ba'i dzaksha'i sogs khongs ni /
T12TD4298E:110a-39: tsa k'a sri ste byings bdun po de rnams yin la de rnams la aa bhyasta zhes sngon gyi thub pa rnams kyi ming du btags so //
T12TD4298E:110a-41: aana\ ausa\ bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:110a-42: ` tsa k'a sri snang byed la /
T12TD4298E:110a-44: tsa k'asta: tsa k'a sa ti /
T12TD4298E:110a-45: aa tsa k'a su: sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110a-46: ` dz'a gri gnyid sangs pa la /
T12TD4298E:110a-48: dz'a gri ta: dz'a gra ti /
T12TD4298E:110a-49: aa dz'a ga du: sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110a-50: ` da ri dr'a de ri d'a lo pashtsa di ti /
T12TD4298E:110a-51: da ri dr'a sogs kying 'gro ba la aitra ste a'a dbyi ba yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:110a-52: byings da ri dr'a sogs kyi a'a ni rkyen dang rnam dbyed 'gro ba'i ming can has dang po can la ai ru 'gyur zhing dbyangs dang po can la a'a de ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:110a-53: ` da ri dr'a ngan 'gro la'o zhes pa la /
T12TD4298E:110a-56: da ri dra ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:110a-59: shishta: sh'a sa ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110a-60: ` a'i d'i sho: a'ida\ a'isha\ dag las so //
T12TD4298E:110a-61: byings a'ida\ dang a'isha\ dag las pha rol gyi rnam dbye sa yig dang dhve dag la aita\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:110a-73: a'isha\ mchog gi dbang phyug la /
T12TD4298E:110b-0: yu sogs byings mang po @110b zhig gi mtha'i au ni rnam dbye pa 'gro ba'i ming can ta yig dang sa yig dang ma yig dang po can pha rol las aoo ru 'gyur ro /
T12TD4298E:110b-1: ` yu nu ru stu bhya a'irb'a /
T12TD4298E:110b-2: yu nu ru stu rnams las a'ira\ yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:110b-3: byings yul la sogs pa 'di rnams kyi au ni rkyen bshad ma thag pa'i tshad nyid de rnams tshang ba pha rol la aoo ru bsgyur ba dang yang na ao ru 'gyur zhing ao ru bsgyur ba'i phyogs la a'ira\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:110b-5: aoo dang ao 'dam ka can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:110b-9: ` / de bzhin du nu ded pa la /
T12TD4298E:110b-18: nga 'gro ba rnams la bya ba lhag po med pas /
T12TD4298E:110b-19: yu ta: yu banti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:110b-20: ` / lo pa sta nu d'atta ta nam /
T12TD4298E:110b-21: tana\ rnams kyi aa nu d'atta dbyi ba nyid do //
T12TD4298E:110b-22: byings ta nu la sogs pa rnams kyi mtha'i aa nu d'atta ste nya ma so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge rnams ni kra nga\ 'gro ba'i ming can dzha sa'i yi ge dang po pha rol la dbyi bar bya ba nyid de /
T12TD4298E:110b-27: nama\ bi k'a ra na pha rol la'ang byings kyi nya ma'i yi ge rnams dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:110b-29: rundha sogs kyi nam\ sbyar nga\ dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:110b-33: nama\ bi k'a ra na sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:110b-36: ` / aa pi ranydza dam sha sham dza shvam dz'am /
T12TD4298E:110b-37: aapa\ la ranydza dam sha\ shanydza shvanydza rnams kyi'o //
T12TD4298E:110b-38: aapa\ bi k'a ra na pha rol la byings ranydza la sogs pa 'di rnams kyi au pa dh'a'i na\ yig ni dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:110b-41: ra dza ta:ra dzanti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:110b-46: ` / bi don p'a n'am ty'a d'i n'am na b'a dirb'a /
T12TD4298E:110b-47: bing las tipa\ la sogs pa dgu rnams ni napa\ la sogs par yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:110b-48: byings bid shes pa las pha rol gyi rnam dbye tipa\ la sogs pa dgu ni yang na rim pa ltar napa\ la sogs pa dgu ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:110b-49: napa\ bsogs su sgyur ba dang mi sgyur ba yang na bar byas pas /
T12TD4298E:111a-10: de ring ma yin pa lang la /
T12TD4298E:111a-14: ` / yang bid la a'atma ne pa da rnams kyang 'jug cing de'i tshe aap\ bi k'a ra na yang mi 'jig la byings mthar rut a'a ga ma ster ba dang mi ster ba 'dam ka can du bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:111a-23: nga 'gro ba pha rol la aas\ kyi aa dbyi ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:111a-24: brta ma na'i skyes bu dang po gsum la /
T12TD4298E:111a-25: aasti sta: santi skyes bu dbus ma'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:111a-27: rnam dbye sipa\ pha rol la aas\ kyi sa\ dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:111a-29: aa si lhag ma rnams la /
T12TD4298E:111a-37: shis byed lota\'i skyes bu dang po gsum la /
T12TD4298E:111a-41: skyes bu dbus ma'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:111a-43: dza hi ai dhi sh'a dhi'o //
T12TD4298E:111a-46: aasa\/ sh'sa\ rnams ni rnam dbye hi dang lhan cig pa rim pa bzhin dza hi aae dhi sh'a dhi rnams su tshig phrad kyis bsgyur ba ste /
T12TD4298E:111a-55: de ring ma yin pa lang gi skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:111a-58: byings aasa\ las pha rol gyi rnam dbye dipa\ dang sipa\ la a'it\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:111a-61: lhag ma rnams la sipa\ la a'ita\/
T12TD4298E:111a-62: aa mipa\ la aa mi dbyi /
T12TD4298E:111a-63: nga 'gro ba rnams la aa dbyi bar byed kyang dipa\ sogs kyi aata\ dang /
T12TD4298E:111a-64: dbyangs dang po'i aata\ mtshams sbyar bas gzugs 'dra ste /
T12TD4298E:111a-72: ` liha\ ro kun tu myang ba la /
T12TD4298E:111a-73: brta ma na'i skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:111b-2: ta tha dag gi dh'os ta dha /
T12TD4298E:111b-4: pa 'gro ba'i yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:111b-6: ledha\/ dhi zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:111b-7: ` dhi dho lo po d'i rgha shtsa /
T12TD4298E:111b-8: dh'i dha la dbyi zhing ring po yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:111b-9: tshu rol gyi mtha'i dha yig ni dha yig pha rol la dbyi zhing /
T12TD4298E:111b-10: dbyangs sngon ma de thung ngu yin na ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:111b-29: ` de ring ma yin pa lang la /
T12TD4298E:111b-33: ` / bi a'adra sngon ma'i tsakshidra gsal bar brjod pa la /
T12TD4298E:111b-35: sa ka sogs kyi yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:111b-36: dzha sa so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge pha rol la byings mtha'i sra yig dang kra yig sogs brtsegs pa yod na'ang sra kra mtha' ma de dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:111b-37: sha sar log de phyis pas kra yang shar log /
T12TD4298E:111b-38: shtu la sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:111b-58: ` / de ring ma yin pa lang la /
T12TD4298E:111b-63: ` / aao lasdzi ngo tsha ba la /
T12TD4298E:111b-64: aa n+ya tra so dza: gzhan du sa\ dza\'o //
T12TD4298E:111b-65: gzhan du skabs la lar brtsegs pa'i sa yig mi dbyi par dza ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:111b-68: ` / tsa k'a sri gnang byed la /
T12TD4298E:111b-69: de ring ma yin pa lang gi skyes bu dang po'i gcig tshig la /
T12TD4298E:111b-70: ` di bi sa sya ta:si bi b'a /
T12TD4298E:111b-71: dip la sa'i ta ste si pa la yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:111b-72: byings mtha'i sa yig ni rnam dbye dip\ pha rol la ta yig tu 'gyur zhing sip\ pha rol la'ang yang na 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:111b-75: aa tsa k'ata\ lhag ma rnams la /
T12TD4298E:112a-2: aa tsa k'a su: aa tsa k'a:...(sib) aa tsa k'a ta\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:112a-3: ` / a'ang sngon ma'i khy'a gtam gyi sbyor ba la /
T12TD4298E:112a-11: ba 'gro ba la mri dzi'i 'phel ba'o //
T12TD4298E:112a-12: rkyen pa 'gro ba pha rol la mri dza'i au pa dh'a ni 'phel bar 'gyur zhing nga 'gro ba'i ming can dbyangs dang po pha rol la 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:112a-16: ` / ni dz'i gu na: ni dza rnams kyi yon tan no //
T12TD4298E:112a-17: apa\ bi k'a ra na 'jig pa las ni ja la sogs pa rnams kyi gnyis brjod pa'i dang po de yon tan du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:112a-18: nyer bsgyur ni ra sngon ma'i ni dzi dag byed la aapa\ 'jeg / dzu ha sogs kyis gnyis brjod /
T12TD4298E:112a-19: sngon ma'i has dang po lhag po //
T12TD4298E:112a-20: ni dza sogs kyis sngon ma yon tan /
T12TD4298E:112a-21: de nas pa 'gro ba rnams la yon tan byed pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:112a-23: nirne nikta: nirne ni dza ti /
T12TD4298E:112a-25: aa ba ne nikte sogs te gnyis ka'i tshig can no /
T12TD4298E:112a-27: bi dzira\ tha dad du gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:112a-29: be ba kta: be bi dza ti sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:112a-32: be bishta: be bi sha ti sogs so /
T12TD4298E:112a-33: ` / bi a'ang sngon ma'i pri srung ba dang gang ba la /
T12TD4298E:112a-35: sngon ma'i ri pri dag gi ai'o //
T12TD4298E:112a-36: aapa\ 'jig pa las byings gnyis brjod pa'i sngon ma'i ri 'gro ba dang pri dag gi ri yig ni ai ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:112a-39: de nas ba 'gro ba la yon tan sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:112a-44: (lot) ...by'a po pri t'a ta\ sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:112a-45: ri dang pri las pha rol gyi rnam dbye dip\ dang sipa\ la aat\ a'a ga ma ster ba dang mi ster ba 'dam ka can du bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:112a-46: by'a bi pa ra ta\/...(dip) ...by'a pi pa: by'a pi par:(sip) ...by'a pi pa:sogs so /
T12TD4298E:112b-0: ri dang po ai 'dra ba ma yin pa'i dbyangs pha rol @112b la sngon ma'i ai ni aiya\ zhes par bsgyur par bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:112b-19: dngos po dang las kyi don la /
T12TD4298E:112b-22: ya la'os ring por bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:112b-26: a'i ya tu: a'i yu: sogs so //
T12TD4298E:112b-30: slar yang ai phyi ma gnyis brjod pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:112b-34: dh'a t'u n'a ma nanta tv'a tra bi shv'artha tv'anytsa sarbath'a /
T12TD4298E:112b-35: aa bhi dh'a tu ma sha kya mi tya la m'a khy'a ta khy'a pa ne /
T12TD4298E:112b-36: de ltar byings rnams kyang ni mtha' yas nyid //
T12TD4298E:112b-37: sna tshogs don nyid kyang ni thams cad du //
T12TD4298E:112b-38: bying rnams 'di zhes mngon gsal mi nus kyang //
T12TD4298E:112b-39: kun nas bshad ba rdzogs par bshad zin to //
T12TD4298E:112b-40: ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a k'a ra na sya s'u tr'a d'a khy'a ta pra kri ya sa m'a pt'a:/
T12TD4298E:112b-41: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las kun nas bshad pa'i rab tu byed pa rnams rdzogs so /
T12TD4298E:112b-43: // / de nas byings las ming du bsgrubs pa krit sogs kyi chog rnams bshad par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:112b-46: 'chad 'gyur tri la sogs pa'i rkyen rnams la kritra rkyen zhes bya la /
T12TD4298E:112b-47: rkyen de rnams gtso bor byed pa'i don la 'jug pa shas che'o /
T12TD4298E:112b-49: tri buna\ dag go / byings las byed pa'i don gyi ming du bsgrub pa la rkyen tri dang bun dag 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:112b-50: ` du pa tsasha 'tshed pa la tri /
T12TD4298E:112b-51: tsu'i ku'os tsa ka ra bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:112b-53: de ni ming du 'grub pa yin la /
T12TD4298E:112b-54: slar de tshig tu bsgrub pa'i phyir so sogs rnam dbye rnams ster dgos pa las cho ga rnams gong ming ler bshad pa ltar gyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:113a-6: byings las pha rol gyi kri ta\ sogs kyi rkyen pas so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge dang po can la aita\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:113a-8: (si) ...ae dhi t'a/....('phal bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113a-10: a'u ta\ 'gro ba las yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:113a-11: byings a'u ta\ rjes 'brel 'gro ba las pha rol gyi krita\ sogs kyi rkyen bas dang po can la aita\ yang na 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:113a-12: (srung bar byed dam/) ....go pi t'a/...(si) (sbed par byed/) ....gopt'a ...(si) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:113a-13: ` sa ha ba ho ro da barna sya /
T12TD4298E:113a-14: saha\ baha\ dag gi aa yig ni aota\'o //
T12TD4298E:113a-15: byings saha\ dang baha\ dag gi aa yig ni rkyen tri pha rol la ao ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:113a-22: so dh'a/...(si) (thob par byed/) ....bo dh'a ...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113a-24: yu bu dag gi aa na aa ka dag go / rkyen yu dang bu dag ni rim pa ltar aa na dang aa ga zhes par bsgyur bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:113a-25: pa tsa\ la bu nya\ nya\ 'gro ba la 'phel ba /
T12TD4298E:113a-27: p'a tsa ka zhes 'grub pa la rnam dbye rnams sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:113a-28: (smin par byed dam 'tshod par byed/) ....p'a tsa ka:...(si) p'a tsa koo / p'a tsa k'a: sogs so //
T12TD4298E:113a-30: (klog par byed/) ....p'a tha ka:...(si) (byed do/) ....k'a ra ka:...(si) (yod par byed/) ....bh'a ba ka:...(si) (gcod par byed/) ....l'a ba ka:...(si) (sre bar byed/) ....y'a pa ka:...(si) (dag par byed/) ....p'a ba ka:...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113a-31: ` / n'a myu pa dh'a tka: n'a mi'i au pa dh'a las ka'o //
T12TD4298E:113a-32: byings n'a mi'i yi ge au pa dh'a can la /
T12TD4298E:113a-33: krita\ sogs ming du sgrub pa'i rkyen ka 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:113a-34: ` kshi pa byed du 'jug pa la /
T12TD4298E:113a-35: ka ka\ yig yon tan 'gog pa'i don /
T12TD4298E:113a-36: kshi pa:...(si byed du 'jug/) kshi poo:...(aoo) kshi p'a:...(dzas) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:113a-38: bhi da:...(si 'joms par phyed/) tshid:...(si dum bur byed/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:113a-39: byings dzny'a longs su chud pa la'ang rkyen ka 'jug par bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:113a-40: dzny'a:...(si shis par byed/) dznyoo:...(soo) dzny'a:...(dzas) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113b-0: ` / pa tsi nam @113b di gra h'a dir yu ni na /
T12TD4298E:113b-1: pa tsi nandi gra h'a sogs la aa yu ni ni'o //
T12TD4298E:113b-2: byings pa tsi sogs dang nandi sogs dang gra h'a la sogs pa rnams la rim pa bzhin rkyen aa dang yu dang ni ni rnams 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:113b-6: aa) ....ba da:...(si) (rtse bar byed dam lha /
T12TD4298E:113b-9: ` (yu) ...nanda na:...(si dga' bar byed/) (yu) ...ra ma na:...(si dga' bar byed dam rtsed mo byed/) (yu) ...b'a ma na:...(si dga' bar byed dam rtsed mo byed/) (yu) ...kra ma na:...(si dga' bar byed dam rtsed mo byed/) (yu) ...aa-rda na:...(si 'joms par byed/) (yu) ...ma-rda na:...(si 'joms par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:113b-12: ` ror++yu na: ru la yu na'o //
T12TD4298E:113b-16: r'a ba na:...(si sgra sgrog par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:113b-20: (si) ...gr'a h'i/....('dzin par byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:113b-21: (rnam dpyod/) ....bi ts'a r'i/...(si) (rnam par rjod par byed/) ....bi b'a d'i/...(si) bi h'a r'i ...(si rnam par 'phrog par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113b-22: ` / dri sh'a de: sha: dri sha\ sogs la sha'o //
T12TD4298E:113b-23: byings dri sha\ sogs la kri ta\ sogs kyi rkyen sha 'jug go ` / shi ti tsa tu rba ta /
T12TD4298E:113b-24: sha 'gro ba la bzhi po bzhin no //
T12TD4298E:113b-25: rkyen sha yig rjes 'brel 'gro ba pha rol las /
T12TD4298E:113b-26: byings la kun nas bsgyur ba sogs byings thams cad pa bzhi po'i cho ga rnams 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:113b-27: ` au ta\ sngon ma'i dri shir\ lta ba la sha dri sha ba shya ru bsgyur sha\ de'i don /
T12TD4298E:113b-28: autpashya:...(si shin tu lta bar byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:113b-30: (sha shin tu 'thung bar byed/) ...auddha ya:...(si) ` dhma sgra dang me kun nas sbyor ba la /
T12TD4298E:113b-31: (sha) ...auddha ma:...(si shin tu sgra sgrog par byed/) ` p'a btung ba la /
T12TD4298E:113b-32: (sha shin tu 'thung bar byad/) ...autpi pa:...(si) ` ghra dri snom pa la /
T12TD4298E:113b-33: (sha shin tu dri snom par byed/) ...audzdzi gha:...(si) ` go sngon ma'i han\ 'tshe ba la /
T12TD4298E:113b-34: (sha ba lang gsod par byed/) ...go gh'o :...(si) ` shth'a 'gro ba las ldog pa la /
T12TD4298E:113b-35: (sha shin tu gnas par byed/) ...au ttishtha:...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:113b-36: ` / dzva l'a derna: dzva la sogs la na'o //
T12TD4298E:113b-37: byings dzva la la sogs pa rnams la rkyen na 'gyur te na\ 'phel ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:113b-39: (na) ...dzv'a la:...(si 'bar bar byed/) ` tab gdung ba la /
T12TD4298E:114a-4: byings las las dang sbyor ba'i byed pa'i don la aana\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114a-5: (si aa bum pa byed/) ...ku mbham k'a ra:...(na si) grantham k'a ra:....(glegs bam byed/) ` a'ata\ da:/
T12TD4298E:114a-7: byings a'at mtha' can las las dang sbyor ba'i byed pa la rkyen da 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114a-8: da yig ti dbyi ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:114a-9: (da shes pa/) ...dznya:...(si da) ...pa:...(si 'thung ba/) da:...(da si sbyin pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114a-12: ming sngon na yod pa'i byings la'ang da rkyen du 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114a-13: go sngon ma'i d'a sbyin pa la /
T12TD4298E:114a-14: (da) ...go da:...(si ba lang sbyin/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:114a-15: (nor sbyin/) ....dha na da:...(da si) (da) ...dvi pa:...(si nyis 'thung/) (da) ...dvi dza:...(si nyis skyes/) (da) ...gri hastha:...(si khyim gnas/) shu tsi gtsang sbra la'o zhes pa'i byings sngon ma'i dru 'gro ba la da ti phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:114a-16: shu ca dra zhes gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:114a-19: byings shu tsa ni ming dra pha rol la /
T12TD4298E:114a-21: shu tsa sh'u ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:114a-22: sh'u dra:....(gtsang sbra song bste dmangs rigs so//) ` au ra sa: lo po mumb'a /
T12TD4298E:114a-23: au rasa\ kyi dbyi zhing muma\ yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:114a-24: da rkyen can gyi ming dang sbyor ba la au rasa\ kyis dbyi zhing muma\ a'a ga ma yang na ster te /
T12TD4298E:114a-25: au ra ga:....(brang 'gro ste sprul/) ....au ram ga: ` bi h'a ya so bi ha tsa /
T12TD4298E:114a-26: bi h'a ya sa'i bi ha 'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:114a-27: da rkyen can gyi ming dang sbyor ba la ming gi byings bi h'a ya sa ni bi ha zhes par 'gyur zhing muma\ a'a ga ma'ang yang na ster par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:114a-28: bi ham ga:...(da si nam mkha' la 'gro/) ...bi ha ga: ` aa too /
T12TD4298E:114a-29: aa ta dag go / byings las sngon na ming yod cing ming de dang 'brel ba'i las dang sbyor ba'i byed pa'i don la rkyen aa dang ta dag 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114a-30: aasthi sngon ma'i hrinya\ 'phrog pa la aa yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:114a-31: aasthi ha ra:...(aa si rus pa khyer ro khyis/) shv'a /
T12TD4298E:114a-33: ka ba tsa ....(go cha phrogs so rgyal rigs kyis//) (aa si) ...ha ra:ksha tri ya: (aa si) ...bha ram ha ra:....(khur phrogs so//) (aa si) ...dha nu dha ra:ku m'a ra:....(gzhu 'dzin no gzhon nus/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:114a-34: ` ca ra g-yo ba la ta /
T12TD4298E:114a-35: ta yig mo rkyen a'i pra 'jug ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:114b-0: (ta si) ...ku ru ca ra:....(yul sgrang ngan du spyod/) (ta a'ipa\) ...ku @114b ru tsa r'i ....(yul sgra ngan du spyod ma/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114b-3: ming sngon ma'i byings las rkyen ai dang kha dang khi rnams 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114b-4: stamba sngon ma'i krinya byed pa la rkyen ai /
T12TD4298E:114b-5: stamba ka ri pri hi/....('bru 'debs par byed/) de ba sngon ma'i aapli khyab pa la /
T12TD4298E:114b-6: de b'a pi:....(lhas khyab po//) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114b-7: ` / khi ti p'urba pa da sya /
T12TD4298E:114b-8: kha 'gro ba la sngon ma'i tshig gi'o //
T12TD4298E:114b-9: rkyen kha yig rjes 'brel 'gro ba pha rol la sngon ma'i tshig de la muma\ a'a ga ma ster par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:114b-10: ksha ma sngon ma'i kri la //
T12TD4298E:114b-11: ga tshig sngon mar muma\ a'a ga mama\ gnas don /
T12TD4298E:114b-13: rkyen gyi khra yig de'i don yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:114b-14: kshe mi ka ra:....(bde bar byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:114b-15: pri yam bada:....(dga' ba'i gtam/) a'atmam bhara:....(bdag nyid rgyas pa/) au da ram bha ri:....(lto ba khengs pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114b-16: ` / aae dz'am khasha\ / ae dza rnams kyi khasha\'o //
T12TD4298E:114b-17: byings aee dza la sogs pa rnams la rkyen khasha\ 'gyur ta /
T12TD4298E:114b-18: dza na sngon ma'i ae dzri 'dar ba la /
T12TD4298E:114b-19: khasha\ / sha\ yig byings thams cad pa bzhi po'i cho ga 'jug pa'i don /
T12TD4298E:114b-21: tsur sogs kyi nyi yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:114b-22: dza na me dza ya:....(skye bo rnams 'dar bar byed/) pandi ta sngon ma'i ma nu shes pa la khasha\ / dib sogs kyis ya bi k'a ra na muma\ ster ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:114b-23: pandi tam ma n+ya:....(mkhas par shes/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114b-26: byings las byed pa'i don gyi ming du bsgrub pa la rkyen khyut\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114b-27: aa nagna:nagna kri ya te aa ne na/....('di gcer bu min pa gcer bur byas so//) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:114b-33: nagnam ka ra nam/....(gcer bur rgyas so//) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:114b-34: aa sthu lam sthu lam kri ya te zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:114b-35: sthu lam ka ra nam ....(gar po min pa gar por ma byas so//) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:114b-37: bha dza rnams kyi bi na\'o //
T12TD4298E:114b-38: byings bha dza\ la sogs pa rnams las byed pa po'i don la rkyen pina\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:114b-39: aardha sngon ma'i bha dza\ nyed pa la /
T12TD4298E:114b-46: rkyen bi ni dbyi bar bya ba nyid de /
T12TD4298E:115a-3: aardha bh'aka\/....(phyed mar byas so//) de bzhin ta tva sngon ma'i bra tsha dang bh'a ra sngon ma'i baha\ la /
T12TD4298E:115a-4: (de kho na nyid 'dri bar byed/) ....ta tva pr'ata\/...(si) (khur skyed de bung bu/) ....bh'a ra b'ata ...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115a-5: ` / b'a horboo sha s'a doo sva re /
T12TD4298E:115a-6: shas\ sogs dbyangs la baha\'i ba aoo'o //
T12TD4298E:115a-7: tshig sngon ma aa yig mtha' can las pha rol gyi baha'i ba yig ni rnam dbye shas\ sogs dbyangs dang po can pha rol la aoo ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115a-13: sa ha'i s'a dha la sha'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:115a-14: rkyen bina\ pha rol la byings sa ha\ ni s'a dha zhes par 'gyur ba'i sa yig ni sha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115a-15: tu r'a sngon ma'i saha\ lhan cig la /
T12TD4298E:115a-18: bi phyis sa shar bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:115a-19: (lhan cig mgyogs/) ....tu r'a sh'ata\/...(si) tu r'a s'a hoo sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115a-20: ` / mo no dh'a ta: byings kyi ma'i na'o //
T12TD4298E:115a-21: byings mtha'i ma yig ni rkyen ra sa so sor bsdu ba'i yi ge pha rol dang tshig mtha' las kyang na yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115a-22: bra sngon ma'i sha mu dang da mu nye bar zhi ba la /
T12TD4298E:115a-25: ra sa la nar bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:115a-26: pra sh'ana\/....(rab tu zhi ba'am rab tu dul/) pra sh'a moo /
T12TD4298E:115a-27: (rab tu zhi ba'am rab tu dul/) ....pra d'ana\/
T12TD4298E:115a-29: ` / aa bh'u tadbha be kri bhva sti yo ge tsvi: byung ba ma yin pa las kri bh'u aa sa sbyor ba la tsvi'o //
T12TD4298E:115a-30: byung nas yun ring 'das pa'i don ma yin pa'i sar byung gi don la kri bh'u aas sbyor ba la bar rkyen tsvi 'gyur ro /
T12TD4298E:115a-32: tsvi la ring po ste aa'i yang a'i'o //
T12TD4298E:115a-33: rkyen tsvi pha rol la byings dang ming gi mtha'i dbyangs thung ngu ni ring por 'gyur zhing mtha' aa yig yin na aa de a'i ru yang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115a-34: aa mi thu nam mi thu nam kri ya te aa ne na ....(mi 'khrig pa las 'khrig par byed/) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:115a-35: mi thu na dang ka ra na'i bar du rkyen tsvi /
T12TD4298E:115a-36: tsa\ yig tsvi la ring po sogs kyi don /
T12TD4298E:115a-39: mi thu n'i ....(mi 'khrig pa las 'khrig par byed/) ka ra nam sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:115a-40: de bzhin du bh'u dang sbyor ba la /
T12TD4298E:115b-0: aa shukla:shukla:bha ba ti zhes pa'i don la/....(dkar po min pa dkar por song/) ....shukl'i bh'a @115b ba:sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:115b-1: aas\ dang sbyor ba la aa sa h'a ya:sa h'a yo bha ba ti ....(lhan cig ma yin pa lhan cig par gyur to//) zhes pa'i don la /
T12TD4298E:115b-2: (lhan cig ma yin pa lhan cig par gyur to//) ....sa h'a y'i tsvi sy'ata\ sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:115b-3: aa he tu: he tu: kri tam ....(rgyu med pa la rgyu byas so//) zhes pa'i don las he (tsvi) t'u kri tam ....(rgyu med pa la rgyu byas so//) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115b-5: tsvi la sa dbyi ba'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:115b-6: gsar byung gi rkyen tsvi pha rol la sngon ma'i mtha' sa yig yin na dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:115b-7: auta\ sngon ma'i ma na sa\ la tsvi sa\ phyis aa a'i ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:115b-8: aunma n'i bh'a ba:....(skyo bar gyur to//) yang skabs la lang tsvi'i don la rkyen d'a ster bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:115b-9: du: kh'a ...(d'a) ka ro ti/....(sdug bsngal bar byed/) bha (d'a) dr'a ka ro ti ....(bzang por byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115b-10: ` / a'a te ma ni pa\ kva ni pa\ ba ni\ ba: a'ata la ma ni pa\ kva ni pa\ ba ni pa\'o //
T12TD4298E:115b-11: byings a'ata\ mtha' can la ming du sgrub pa'i rkyen ma nipa\ dang kva nipa\ dang pa nipa rnams 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115b-12: su sngon ma'i ng'a la ma nipa\ pa\ rjes 'brel ai brjod don /
T12TD4298E:115b-13: su d'a man\ zhes 'grub pa la rnam dbye sbyor ba'i cho ga gong r'a dza na ltar bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:115b-14: su d'a m'a ...(si legs pa'i sbyin pa byin/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115b-17: byings sth'a g'a b'a rnams kyi mtha'i aa yig ni kvi pa\ ma yin pa'i rkyen kra 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la a'i ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115b-18: su sngon ma'i sth'a dang b'a la kva nipa /
T12TD4298E:115b-21: ka\ yig ka\ 'gro ba'i khyad don /
T12TD4298E:115b-23: (legs par gnas/) ....su sth'i b'a/...(si) (legs par 'thung/) ....su p'i b'a (si) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:115b-29: (sa gzhi sbyin par byed/) ....bh'u m'i d'a b'a ...(si)/
T12TD4298E:115b-30: skabs la lar a'a yig mtha' can ma yin pa la'ang ma nipa sogs 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:115b-31: (/ legs pa'i las/) ....su karm'a/...(si) (legs par thos/) ....su sharm'a (si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:115b-33: byings thams cad la ming du sgrub pa'i rkyan kvi pa\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:115b-34: karma sngon ma'i kri la kvipa\/
T12TD4298E:115b-35: ` hra sva sya pi ti kri ti tuka / thung ngu'i krita kyi pa\ 'gro ba la tuka'o byings mtha' thung ngu la krita sogs kyi rkyen pa\ yig 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol las tuka a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:116a-4: rkyen kvipa\ ni yongs rdzogs dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:116a-6: karma krita/....(las byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:116a-7: (me gsog go/) ....aagnim tsita\/...(si) (/ lha la bstod do//) ....de bam stu ta\ ...(si) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:116a-8: thung ngu ma yin na tuka\ a'a ga ma mi 'jug pas /
T12TD4298E:116a-9: (zhib 'thung/) ....so ma p'a:...(si) (thams cad mthong/) ....sarba drika\ ...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116a-11: ` / yang pratstsha la sogs pa ni kvipa\ pha rol la ring por bsgyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:116a-12: (de kho na nyid 'dri/) ....ta tva pr'ata\/...(si) (si legs pa'i grogs/) ....su shr'i: (si ngag/) ....b'aka\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116a-13: ` / yang rkyen kvipa\ pha rol can gyi naha\ 'cheng ba las sngon ma'i nyer bsgyur gyi mtha' ni ring por bsgyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:116a-14: au pa sngon ma'i na ha\ la kvipa\/
T12TD4298E:116a-17: naha\'i dha 'os ha\ dha\ ru bsgyur ba sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:116a-18: (nye bar 'ching ste lha ma sgrog/) ....au p'a nata\ ...(si) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116a-19: ` / kvipa\ pha rol la dhyee la sogs pa ni sam pra s'a ra nar bsgyur zhing de yang ring po kho nar 'gyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:116a-20: su sngon ma'i dhyee sems pa la /
T12TD4298E:116a-22: kvipa\/ ya\ aee dang bcas pa a'i ru bsgyur /
T12TD4298E:116a-24: su dh'i:....(blo bzang ngam legs pa'i blo/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116a-25: ` / dri sheshtaka sa koo tso pa m'a ne kar++ye /
T12TD4298E:116a-26: nye bar 'jal ba'i bya ba la drisha\ la taka\ saka\ dag kyang ngo //
T12TD4298E:116a-27: nye bar 'jal ba'i bya ba'i don la byings dri sha\ las rkyen taka\ dang saka\ dang kvipa\ yang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116a-28: aa n+ya sngon ma'i drisha\ la rkyen de gsum sbyar /
T12TD4298E:116a-29: ` a'a sarb'a de: sarba sogs kyi a'a'o //
T12TD4298E:116a-30: rkyen taka\ dang saka\ dang kvipa\ rnams pa rol can gyi sngon ma'i sarba la sogs pa rnams kyi ti ni a'a ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116a-31: aa n+ya kyi ti a'a ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:116a-32: aa n+y'a dri sha:...(ka\ gzhan dang 'dra bar ltos shig/) aa n+y'a driksha:...(sak\ gzhan dang 'dra bar ltos shig/) aa ...(kviba) n+y'a drika\ ....(gzhan dang 'dra bar ltos shig/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:116a-34: (taka\) ...t'a drisha\:....(de dang 'dra bar ltos shig/) (saka) ...t'a driksha:....(de dang 'dra bar ltos shig/) (kvipa) ...t'a drika\ sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116a-35: ` / ki mi da ma: k'i shoo\ //
T12TD4298E:116a-36: kima\ ai dam\ dag gi k'i a'i sha\ dag go / rkyen taka\ dang saka dang kvipa\ rnams pha rol can gyi sngon ma'i kima\ dang ai dam\ gyi sgra ni rim pa ltar k'i dang a'isha dag tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116b-0: k'i dri sha:....(tak\ ci 'dra bar ltos shig/) (sak\) ...k'i driksha:....(ci 'dra bar ltos shig/) ....k'i drika\ ...(kvipa\) / a'i dri sha:...(tak\ 'di 'dra bar ltos shig/) @116b a'i driksha:...(saka\) a'i drika\/...(kvipa\) ` drisha rkyen taka\ la sogs pa'i mtha' can dang sbyor ba las bha bata\ la sogs pa'i rnam par gnas pa'i don la ti a'a ru 'gyur bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:116b-1: (tak\) ...bha b'a dri sha:...(khyod dang 'dra bar shes/) ....bha b'a driksha:...(saka\) bh'a ...(kvipa) b'a drika ....(khyod dang 'dra bar shes/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116b-4: byings las 'das pa'i don dang de'i ngang tshul gyi don la rkyen ni ni 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116b-5: aagnishto ma sngon ma'i yadza\ la ni ni na\ 'phel ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:116b-7: aagnishto ma y'a dz'i/...(si me'i sbyin sreg mchod zin/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:116b-8: pra br'a dz'i/...(si rab tu spong ba/) aushma bho dz'i ...(si zas dron mo zos/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116b-9: ` / kvipa\ ba ni pa\ d'a: kvipa\ ba ni pa\ da rnams so //
T12TD4298E:116b-10: byings las 'das pa'i don dang ngang tshul brjod pa la rkyen kvipa\ dang ba nipa\ dang da rnams kyang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116b-11: bri t'a sngon ma'i han\ la kvipa\/
T12TD4298E:116b-12: bri t'a h'a ...(si lha min 'joms te brgya byin/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:116b-14: ba ni pa\ pa\ 'gro ba la tuka\ a'a ga ma byin pas /
T12TD4298E:116b-15: su tv'a ...(si 'tsho ba rgyas/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:116b-16: sa ra si sngon ma'i dzan dang sarba sngon ma'i gam\ dang s'a ma sngon ma'i gee dang sarbasngon ma'i dzny'a rnams la da /
T12TD4298E:116b-17: da 'gro ba la ti phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:116b-18: sa ra si dza:...(si mtsho skyes/) sarba ga:...(si thams cad du 'gro/) s'a ma ga:...(si snyan tshig 'don/) sarba dznya:...(si kun mkhyen nam thams cad mkhyen pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116b-21: byings las 'das pa'i don gyi dngos po'i don gyi bya ba la rkyen kta dang /
T12TD4298E:116b-22: 'das pa'i byed pa po'i don la kta ba tu 'gyur zhing /
T12TD4298E:116b-23: rkyen de gnyis la nishtha zhes ming 'dogs kyang byed de /
T12TD4298E:116b-24: kri la kta dang kta ba tu sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:116b-25: ka tam kri ta:...(si sngon rtsva las byed/) ka tam kri ta b'an/...(si rtsva lhas byas zin/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:116b-26: a'a ga ta:....(tshur shog/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116b-27: ` / ga tyarth'a da karma k'a tstsha karta ri kta: las med pa las 'gro ba'i don dang byed pa po la kta'o //
T12TD4298E:116b-28: byings las med pa la 'gro ba'i don dang /
T12TD4298E:116b-29: byings las bcas rnams la byed pa po'i don la rkyen kta 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:116b-30: sthi ta:....(gnas/) sh'anta:....(zhi bar byed/) ....d'anta:sogs so /
T12TD4298E:116b-32: aita\ dang bcas pa'i kta la yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:117a-0: dmigs bsal med pa'i aita dang bcas pa'i kta ni ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can du byed pa dang @117a * //
T12TD4298E:117a-1: mi byed pa 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:117a-2: pra sngon ma'i dyu ta\ la kta aita\/
T12TD4298E:117a-3: yon tan yang na bar byas pas /
T12TD4298E:117a-4: pra dyo ti ta:....(rab tu gsal bar byas/) ....pra dyu ti ta: de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:117a-6: ka 'gro ba'i phyogs la slar yang dag par bsgyur ba dang /
T12TD4298E:117a-7: ka 'gro ba ma yin pa'i phyogs la rang gnas byas pas /
T12TD4298E:117a-8: au di ta:....(smra bar byed/) ....ba di ta: ru de ta:....(mchi ma 'dzag par byed/) ....ro di ta: mu shi ta:....(rku bar byed/) ....mo shi ta: gri hi ta:....(bzung bar gyur/) ....gra hi ta: nu di ta:....(byed du 'jug/) ....no di ta: bi di ta:....(rig par byed/) ....be di ta: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:117a-10: byings ram yig mtha' can dang au yig mtha' can dang /
T12TD4298E:117a-11: shr'i rnams las pha rol gyi rkyen ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can la aita\ a'a ga ma 'gyur ba ma yin te /
T12TD4298E:117a-12: yu ta:....(bsres so//) nu ta:....(ded do//) bh'u ta:....(byung ngo//) smri ta:....(dran no//) shr'i ta:....('byor par gyur/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:117a-13: ` / a'a d'i di ta: a'ata\ a'ita\ 'gro ba la'o //
T12TD4298E:117a-14: byings mtha' a'ata\ dang a'ita\ 'gro ba las kyang pha rol gyi rkyen ka\ 'gro ba la aita\ 'gyur ba ma yin no /
T12TD4298E:117a-15: ` / ny'i t'am taka\ barta m'a nenya [?] pi /
T12TD4298E:117a-16: nyi aita\ 'gro ba la da ltar ba la taka\ kyang ngo//
T12TD4298E:117a-17: byings nyi dang aita\ rjes 'brel 'gro ba la da ltar ba'i don la rkyen taka 'gyur zhing aita yang ster ba ma yin no /
T12TD4298E:117a-19: da las ta'i na ste da'i yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:117a-20: byings da yig mtha' can las pha rol gyi rkyen ta yig ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can ni na yig tu 'gyur zhing byings mtha'i da de yang na yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:117a-21: nyi mi d'a snum pa'am bsres pa la /
T12TD4298E:117a-22: nyi aita\ 'gro ba la zhes pas /
T12TD4298E:117a-23: taka\ / nyi de'i don a'ata\ a'ita\ 'gro ba la'os /
T12TD4298E:117a-24: aita\ mi 'jug byings mtha'i a'a de'i don /
T12TD4298E:117a-29: pra sngon ma'i nyi shva d'a lus gsher ba la ;
T12TD4298E:117a-30: pra svanna:....(rdul nag gi gsher/) nyi kshvi d'a phye mar 'thag pa la /
T12TD4298E:117a-32: ` / aa do dza ghu: ki ti /
T12TD4298E:117a-33: aata\ kyi ka\ 'gro ba la dzaghu'o //
T12TD4298E:117a-34: byings aad ni rkyen ka 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la dzagha\ zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:117b-1: ta tha dag gi dhar bsgyur ba sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:117b-2: dzagdham/....(sha za'o//) ` ra: ra las so //
T12TD4298E:117b-3: byings ra yig mtha' can las kyang pha rol gyi rkyen gyi ta yig ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can ni na yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:117b-6: ya ba sogs kyi ring po //
T12TD4298E:117b-7: ta na sha ra ri sogs kyis /
T12TD4298E:117b-8: bi k'irnam/....(rnam par bcom mo//) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:117b-9: dzr'i shu dang dzhr'i shu lang tsho nyams pa la /
T12TD4298E:117b-10: dz'irnam sha r'i ram/....(lus rgas so lang tsho nyams pa/) ....dzh'irnam sha r'i ram sogs so /
T12TD4298E:117b-11: ` / lv'a dyo di ta: l'u sogs dang aota 'gro ba las so //
T12TD4298E:117b-12: byings l'u la sogs pa dang ao yig 'gro ba las kyang pha rol gyi rkyen ta yig ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can ni na yig tu 'gyur zhing byings mtha' ai thung yin na ring por 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:117b-15: l'u na:....(gcod par byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:117b-16: d'unya nye bar gdung ba la /
T12TD4298E:117b-17: d'u na:....(gdung bar byed/) yang l'u'i sogs khongs kshi zad pa dang nges par rtogs pa la'o zhes pa'i byings las pha rol gyi ta yig ni nges par rtogs pa'i don la nar bsgyur zhing zad pa'i don la ta rang du gnas par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:117b-18: ksh'i na:....(nges par rtogs/) kshi ta:....(zang bar byed/) glee dang mlee la kta /
T12TD4298E:117b-19: mtshams sbyor gyi yi ge a'a /
T12TD4298E:117b-20: l'u sogs kyis ta nar bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:117b-21: gl'a na:....(mi dga' ba/) ....ml'a na: sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:117b-22: ao h'aka\ gtong ba la kta /
T12TD4298E:117b-23: h'i na:....(nyams pa/) yang rkyen ta yig ka 'gro ba pha rol la byings ao by'a yi rgas pa la'o zhes pa ni p'i zhes par 'gyur bar bshad pas /
T12TD4298E:117b-24: p'i na:....(rgan po'am rtsub bo//) ` do datti /
T12TD4298E:117b-26: rkyen ta yig ka 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la byings du d'anya\ ni dad\ ces par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:117b-27: datta:...(kta\ byin/) (sbyin pa byed/) ....datta b'an/...(kta ba tu/) ` sva r'anto b'a /
T12TD4298E:117b-29: nyer bsgyur dbyangs mtha' can sngon ma'i d'anya\ ni rkyen ta yig ka 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la dad du bsgyur ba dang da\ zhes par bsgyur ba 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:117b-30: pra ratta:....(rab tu byin/) ....pratta: aa pa datta:....(kun tu byin/) ....aa batta:sogs so //
T12TD4298E:117b-31: yadza\ lata dang kta ba tu /
T12TD4298E:117b-32: sam pa s'a ra nar bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:118a-0: aishtam/....(lha mchod do//) aishta b'an/....(lha mchod par byed/) @118a * //
T12TD4298E:118a-1: de bzhin du tu bab\ la /
T12TD4298E:118a-2: auptam/....(sa bon btab/) ba ha la /
T12TD4298E:118a-3: a'u dha:....(thob bo//) a'a sngon ma'i hve nya\ la /
T12TD4298E:118a-4: a'a h'u ta:....(kun nas drangs so//) sam sngon ma'i bye nya\ la /
T12TD4298E:118a-5: sa mb'i ta:....(yang dag par g-yogs so//) bad la /
T12TD4298E:118a-7: auktam/....(/ smras so'am brjod do//) ` ba si kshu dho ri ta\/
T12TD4298E:118a-8: bas\ kshu dha\ dag la aita\'o //
T12TD4298E:118a-9: byings pas dang kshudha dag las pha rol gyi kta la aita\ ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:118a-10: au shi ta:....(bkab po//) kshu di ta:....(bkres so//) ` gha s'a de:sha /
T12TD4298E:118a-12: rkyen ta yig ka 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la byings ghasa\ sogs kyi mtha'i sa yig ni sha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118a-14: ` tr'a n'a dy'a b'a ni patyante /
T12TD4298E:118a-15: tr'a na sogs ni ni b'a ta yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:118a-16: rkyen kta pha rol la byings tri la sogs pa las ta nar bsgyur bas tr'a na sogs su byed pa ni b'a ta dang yang na ta yig rang du gnas pa 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:118a-18: tr'a na:....(bsrungs so//) ....t'a ta: de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:118a-19: hr'i na:....(ngo tsha/) ....hr'i ta: ghr'a na:....(snom byed de sna/) ....ghr'a ta: binna:....(rig pa'am shes pa/) ....bitta: nunna:....(byed du 'jug gam gyis shig/) ....nutta: nirb'anna:....(kun spangs sam myang 'das/) ....nirb'atta: ` sambar++yu pe bhya:ka ro ti bh'u sha ne suta\/
T12TD4298E:118a-20: sam\ pa ri au pa rnams las kri la rgyan gyi don la suta'o //
T12TD4298E:118a-21: nyer bsgyur sam\ dang ba ri dang au pa rnams las pha rol gyi byings krinya\ la rgyan dang gzhan las phul du byung ba'i don la suta\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:118a-22: sam skri ta:....(legs byas sam legs sbyar/) pa ri skri ta:....(yongs su byed/) au paskri ta:....(nye bar sbyor ba/) sogs so ;
T12TD4298E:118a-23: ` / bha the ghanya\ dngos po la ghanya\'o //
T12TD4298E:118a-24: byings la dngos po'i don la rkyen ghanya\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118a-25: sa ma sngon ma'i krinya\ lagha nya nya 'phel ba'i don /
T12TD4298E:118a-28: samsk'ar:....('du byed dam legs byas/) ` dza nerdz'a /
T12TD4298E:118a-30: rkyen kta pha rol la byings dzana\'i dz'a zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118a-31: dz'a ta:....(skyes so//) ` pa tse rb'a: pa tsa las ba'o //
T12TD4298E:118a-32: byings ba tsa las pha rol gyi rkyen kta ni ba zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118a-33: ba kva:....(tshos pa'am smin pa/) ` shu she:ka: shu sha la ka'o //
T12TD4298E:118b-0: byings shu sha las pha rol gyi rkyen kta ni ka @118b zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118b-1: shu shka:....(bskams so//) ` ksh'a derma:ksh'a sogs la ma'o //
T12TD4298E:118b-2: byings ksh'a la sogs pa las pha rol gyi rkyen kta ni ma zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118b-4: ksh'a ma:....(zad byed/) ` sph'a ya:sph'i: sph'a ya'i sph'i'o //
T12TD4298E:118b-5: rkyen kta pha rol la byings sph'a yi rgas pa la'o zhes pa ni sph'i zhes par 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:118b-6: sph'i ta:....(rgas so//) ` kva su k'a noo na be ba ta\/
T12TD4298E:118b-7: kva su k'a na dag na ba ae bzhin no //
T12TD4298E:118b-8: byings la kva su dang k'a na rkyen du 'gyur zhing rkyen de gnyis kyang don dang bya ba so kva su ni lkog gyur gyi rnam dbye bar smee pa da napa\ sogs dang 'dra la k'a na ni a'atma ne pa da aa sogs dang 'dra ba nyid de bhi dir gnyis su byed pa la /
T12TD4298E:118b-9: kva su ka yon tan 'gog pa'i don /
T12TD4298E:118b-11: gnyis brjod pa sogs kyis bsgrubs pas /
T12TD4298E:118b-12: bi bhi dv'ana\/....('byed par byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:118b-13: kri la tsa kri b'ana\/....(byas so//) yang kri la k'a na /
T12TD4298E:118b-16: tsa kr'a na:....(byas so//) de bzhin du han\ la /
T12TD4298E:118b-17: (kva su aita si/) ...dza ghi b'ana\/....('tshe ba byas/) ....dza gh'a na:...(k'a na/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:118b-18: ` / sha tri sh'a shoo tipa\ te pata\ kri y'a y'am /
T12TD4298E:118b-19: bya ba la sha tri sh'a na dag ste tipa\ te bzhin no //
T12TD4298E:118b-20: byings las bya ba'i don la rkyen sha hri dang sh'a na dag 'jug la rkyen de gnyis kyi cho ga sogs sha tri ni barta ma na'i pa rasmee pa da tipa\ sogs dang 'dra zhing sh'a na ni a'atma ne pa da'i te sogs dang 'dra ba nyid de /
T12TD4298E:118b-21: pa tsa la sha tri ri num gyi don /
T12TD4298E:118b-23: pa tsan\/...(si 'tshed par byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:118b-24: pa thana/...(si klog par byed/) gee la /
T12TD4298E:118b-25: g'a yan\ ...(si smra bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:118b-26: ` / mu g'a nenyata: a'an las aata\ la muka\'o //
T12TD4298E:118b-27: rkyen a'ana ste sh'a na pha rol la byings aa yig mtha' can la muka\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:118b-31: muka\ a'a ga ma byin pas /
T12TD4298E:118b-32: pa tsa m'a na:....('tshod par byed/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:118b-33: pi ba m'a na:....('thung bar byed/) ya dza m'an:....(mchod par byad/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:118b-35: ta na\ sogs kyis au bi k'a ra na de ba\ra bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:118b-36: ma nv'a na:....(gus par byed/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:119a-1: pha rol gyi rkyen a'a na'i a'a yig ni a'i ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119a-2: a'a s'i na:....(gnas par byed/) ` b'a d'i yo: sha tu: aata\ la sha tu ste a'ipa la yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:119a-3: byings aata\ mtha' can la rkyen sha tu 'gyur zhing ming de mo rtags su byed na a'ipa\ pha rol las numa\ a'a ga ma ster ba dang mi ster ba 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:119a-4: tud la sha tu au dang sha\ phyis /
T12TD4298E:119a-5: tu dada\ ....(gdung ba/) ces 'grub pa la mo rkyen a'ipa numa\ yang na bar byas pas /
T12TD4298E:119a-6: tu dant'i/....(gdung ba ma/) ....tu da t'i sogs so /
T12TD4298E:119a-8: aata\ las aapa\ kyi aa la rtag tu'o //
T12TD4298E:119a-9: byings aa yig mtha' can aapa\ bi k'a ra na dang 'brel ba'i sha tu'i rkyen can la mo rkyen a'ipa\ dang ma ning las dzas shas 'gyur ba'i ai pha rol la numa\ rtag tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119a-10: (a'ipa\) ...bha bant'i/....(yod ma/) (dza sa) ...bha ....(yod pa rnams/) banti /
T12TD4298E:119a-11: (a'ipa\) ...pa tsant'i/....('tshed ma/) (dzas) ...pa tsanti ....('tshed pa rnams/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:119a-12: yang di bu rtsed mo dang shli sha dga' ba la /
T12TD4298E:119a-13: di ba sogs kyis ya bi k'a ra na /

T12TD4298E:119a-17: byings d'a sogs dang dzaksha sogs la sha tu rtag par 'jug kyang numa\ mi ster bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:119a-18: d'a la sha tu da da ta\ ...(si /
T12TD4298E:119a-19: sbyin pa/) (a'ipa\) ...da da d'i/....(sbyin pa ma/) (dzas\) ...da da di/....(sbyin pa rnams/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:119a-20: dzaksha ta\ ...(si dgod pa/) (a'ipa\) ...dzaksha t'i/....(dgod pa ma/) (dzasa\) ...dzaksha ti/....(dgod pa rnams/) dz'a gra ta/...(si mel tshe byed/) da ri dra ta\/
T12TD4298E:119a-21: ...(si dbul phongs/) tsak'a sa ta\/...(si 'od byed/) (si) ...sh'a sat\ ....(bstod pa byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:119a-22: ` / bi derb'a ba su: bid sogs las ba su yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:119a-23: byings bid la sogs pa rnams las sha tri'i yul la rkyen ba su sbyor ba dang sha tri nyid sbyor ba yang na bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:119a-24: bi dv'ana\/....(rig pa can nam mkhas pa/) ....bi dana\/
T12TD4298E:119a-25: yang aata\ bha bata\ dang ta tr'a bha bata\ dag mchod pa'i don la ni p'a ta ste /
T12TD4298E:119a-26: aa tra bha banto bhatta mi shr'a/....('dir yod pa ni rje bo gsal ba'o//) ta tra bha badbhirbha ga batb'a da rboo ni tam/....(der gnas pa'i bcom ldan gyi zhabs la bsngags so//) ` sh'i le trina\/
T12TD4298E:119a-28: byings las ngang tshul brjod pa'i don dang 'brel ba la rkyen trina\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119a-30: yon tan na\ khyad don si d'a ti phyis pas /
T12TD4298E:119a-31: kart'a/...(si byed po'am byed pa'i ngang tshul/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:119b-0: 'phrog pa'i ngang tshul/) @119b mart'a/...(si 'chi ba'i ngang tshul/) bhart'a/...(si khrims 'jug/) ` aishnu snu knu /
T12TD4298E:119b-2: byings las ngang tshul dang 'brel ba'i don la rkyen aishnu dang snu dang knu rnams kyang 'gyur te /

T12TD4298E:119b-4: aa lam ka rishnu:....('di ltar tshul khrims kyis brgyan pa/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:119b-5: bha dzishnu:...(aishnu gsal ba'i khrims/) gra sishnu:...(aishnu bzang ba'i khrims/) sa hishnu:...(aishnu bzod pa'i ngang tshul/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:119b-6: bh'ushnu:...(snu khrims yod/) dzishnu:...(snu rgyal ba'i ngang tshul/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:119b-7: gridnu:...(snu 'dod pa'i ngang tshul/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:119b-8: ` /sh'a ko ka na: sh'a ka au au ka na\'o //
T12TD4298E:119b-9: byings las ngang tshul sogs kyi don la rkyen sh'a ka dang au dang au ka na\ rnams kyang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-10: (sh'a ka si) ...ba r'a ka:....(smad pa'i khrims/) (a'ipa\) ...ba r'a k'i ....(smad pa'i khrims ma/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:119b-11: bikshu:...(au slong ba'i tshul khrims can te dge slong/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:119b-12: (au ka na 'dir 'phel ba mi byed/) ....bikshu ka:....(slong ba'i tshul khrims can te dge slong/) k'a mu ka:...(au ka na 'phel ba /
T12TD4298E:119b-13: 'dod pa'i tshul/) bh'a bu ka:...(yod pa'i tshul/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:119b-15: sa mtha' sham sa dag la au yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:119b-16: 'dod pa'i don gyi rkyen sa'i mtha' can dang a'anga\ sngon ma'i sham sa\ dag la ngang tshul sogs kyi don ma yin pa la'ang rkyen au 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-20: a'a sngon ma'i sham su bstod pa la /
T12TD4298E:119b-21: a'a sham su:....(kun tu bstod par 'dod/) ` na m'a de:ra: na ma sogs la ra'o //
T12TD4298E:119b-22: byings nam la sogs pa rnams la rkyen ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-23: na mra:....(phyag 'tshal/) hidsra:....('tshe ba'i ngang tshul/) ya shra:....(grags ba'i ngang tshul/) ka mra:....(mdzes pa'i ngang tshul/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:119b-24: ` / gha s'a de: kma ra: gha sa sogs la kma ra'o //
T12TD4298E:119b-25: byings gha sa sogs las rkyen kma ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-27: ghasma ra:....(za ba'i ngang tshul/) sri sma ra:....(skyong ba'i ngang tshul/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:119b-28: tshi di bhi di bi d'am ku ra: tshi di bhi di bi da rnams la ku ra'o//
T12TD4298E:119b-29: byings tshi dir gnyis su byed pa bhi dir 'joms pa bi da shes pa rnams las ngang tshul sogs kyi don la rkyen ku ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-31: tshi du ra:...(dum bur byed pa'i ngang tshul/) bhi du ra:....('jigs pa'i ngang tshul/) bi du ra:....(shes pa'i tshul/) ` bh'a s'a de rghu ra: bh'asa\ sogs la ghu ra'o //
T12TD4298E:119b-32: byings bh'asa\ la sogs pa rnams la rkyen ghu ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:119b-33: ghra khyad par gyi don la /
T12TD4298E:119b-34: bh'a su ra:...(si 'od kyi ngang tshul/) bham gu ra:....('joms pa'i ngang tshul/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120a-2: byings phul du byung ba'i rkyen ya nga\ gi mtha' can la ngang tshul sogs kyi don la rkyen a'uka\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120a-3: y'a ya dzu ka:....(phul du byung ba'i mchod pa'i ngang tshul/) da dam shu ka:....(so phul du byung ba'i ngang tshul/) b'a ba du ka:....(phul du byung ba'i skad kyi ngang tshul/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120a-4: ` / a'a dri ta: kirdvi shtsa bh'u te /
T12TD4298E:120a-5: a'ata\ rita\ la byung zin la ki ste gnyis kyang ngo //
T12TD4298E:120a-6: byings a'ata\ dang rita\ kyi mtha' can las byung zin gyi don dang 'brel ba'i ngang tshul sogs kyi don la rkyen ki 'gyur zhing byings de gnyis su'ang brjod par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:120a-8: pa pi:....('thungs zin pa'i tshul/) da di:....(byin pa'i ngang tshul/) sogs dang /
T12TD4298E:120a-10: tsakri:....(byas pa'i tshul/) ba bri:....(smras pa'i tshul/) dza hri:....(phrogs pa'i tshul/) sogs te /
T12TD4298E:120a-12: r'a ma: so mamba pir++ya dznye da di rg'ashtsa kri ra dbhu tam /
T12TD4298E:120a-13: y'a dza k'am ba bri r'a dza hri: punda ri ka ma h'a dvi dz'a na\/
T12TD4298E:120a-14: dga' byed mchod sbyin la ni zhi ba 'thungs //
T12TD4298E:120a-15: ba yi sbyin pa rmad du byung ba byas //
T12TD4298E:120a-16: bka' yis mchod sbyin byed po bos te 'ongs //
T12TD4298E:120a-17: gnyis skyes chen pos pad dkar dus ston no /
T12TD4298E:120a-18: ` / s'a do n'a da ya: auna\ la sogs pa ni rtag tu'o //
T12TD4298E:120a-19: byings la rkyen auna\ la sogs pa rnams ni 'das ma 'ongs da ltar ba sogs dus thams cad la rtag tu 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:120a-21: auna\ na\ 'gro ba la 'phel ba byas pas /
T12TD4298E:120a-22: k'a ru:....(byed pa po//) b'a 'gro ba la /
T12TD4298E:120a-24: auna\/ a'ata\ la yuka\ a'a ga ma byin pas /
T12TD4298E:120a-25: b'a yu:....(rtag par 'gro ba ste drung/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:120a-30: krosht'a/....(ce sbyang/) aa ba\ bsrung zhing skyong ba la /
T12TD4298E:120a-32: sam bra s'a ra nar bsgyur /
T12TD4298E:120a-35: mtshams sbyar bas aom zhes so //
T12TD4298E:120a-36: aang bden par 'gro ba la rkyen ma ni na\/
T12TD4298E:120a-39: a'atma/....(bdag nyid/) gri hi bri dhi la ma ni na /
T12TD4298E:120a-40: ` ma n+yu pa dh'a ya ri ra: ma ni la au pa dh'a'i ri ra'o //
T12TD4298E:120a-41: rkyen ma ni pha rol las byings kyi au pa dh'a'i ri yig ni rar 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120a-43: brahma/....(chen po dang 'phel ba dang grags shing grub pa dang tshangs pa dang srog can rnams la/) bradhma/....('phel ba/) dhri nya\ 'dzin pa la rkyen ma yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:120a-44: dharma:....('chang bar byed dam chos/) ` dhv'a de ru li: bhu sogs la au li'o //
T12TD4298E:120a-45: byings dhu sogs la au na\ sogs kyi rkyen au li 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120a-46: dh'u li:....(skyod par byed/) aam gi dang ram gi dang lam gi 'gro ba la rkyen au li /
T12TD4298E:120b-0: aanggu @120b li:....(cha shas sam yan lag/) ....ranggu li: langgu li:....(cha shas sam yan lag/) byings shas gnod pa sogs la rang bzhin gyi bya ba la auna\ sogs kyi rkyen tra 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:120b-1: shastra:....(gnod byed de mtshon cha/) aa su 'phen pa la /
T12TD4298E:120b-2: aa stra:....('phen pa'i mtshon cha/) p'a srung ba la /
T12TD4298E:120b-3: p'a tram/....(snod dam 'dab ma/) ni gsal ba la /

T12TD4298E:120b-6: a'a nga sngon ma'i ga ma\ 'gro ba la rkyen ni ni sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:120b-7: a'a g'a m'i/....(tshur 'ong ba'i tshul/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:120b-9: bh'a b'i ....(bden pa'i khrims/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120b-10: ` / a'i sh'a de rba ra: a'i sha sogs la bar 'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-11: byings a'i sha la sogs pa la auna\ sogs kyi rkyen bar 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120b-12: a'i shva ra:....(dbang phyug/) sth'a ba ra:....(brtan pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120b-16: byings r'a dzra sogs la auna\ sogs kyi rkyen aana\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120b-17: (gsal ba'am rgyal po/) ....r'a dz'a/...(si) yu b'a ...(si lang tsho/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120b-18: ` / ai ma na tr'ask'a: ai ma na\ tra aa su ka\'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-19: byings gang la'ang auna\ sogs kyi rkyen ai mana\ dang tra dang aa suka\ rnams 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120b-20: (ai mana\) ...pa tsi m'a/....(mchod pa/) (tra/) ...p'a tram/....(snod/) (aa suka\/) ...te dza:....(gzi brjid/) (aa suka\/) ...bho ka:....(skyong ba/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:120b-22: ba tsa sogs la aa sa\'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-23: byings btsal sogs pa rnams la rkyen aasa\ 'jug ste /

T12TD4298E:120b-25: byings la mchog ma yin pa'i las ngan pa'i don la rkyen ke li ma 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120b-26: bhi dir la ke li ma /
T12TD4298E:120b-28: (shing gshog ma legs pa/) ....bhi de li mam kashtham /
T12TD4298E:120b-30: (cung zad bcos te gzhal/) ....pa tse li mam a'a dha kya:sogs so//
T12TD4298E:120b-31: ` sham pra bi bhyo bhu bo du: sham pra bi rnams las bh'u lu da'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-32: sham dang pra dang bi rnams las pha rol gyi bh'u la auna\ sogs kyi rkyen du 'gyur te /
