T12TD4298E:120b-35: yu baha\ aa gi rnams las nipa\'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-36: byings yu dang baha\ dang aa gi rnams las auna\ sogs kyi rkyen nipa\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:120b-37: yo ni:....(skye gnas/) bahni:....('tshed cing 'gro ba/) aakni:....(yan lag med bar 'gro ba ste me/) ` ai di tsa di sha ki ru di bhyo ra: ai di tsa di sha ki ru di rnams las ra'o //
T12TD4298E:120b-38: byings ai di dbang phyug tsa di bsil ba sha ki nus pa ru di mchi ma 'dzag pa rnams las auna\ la sogs pa'i rkyen ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121a-1: sogs kyi nu ma\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:121a-2: aindra:....(dbang po/) tsandra:....(bsil byed de zla ba/) sham kra:....(nus pa/) ru dra:....(drag po/) yang pusha\ rgyas pa la rkyen pa dang la sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:121a-3: pushpa:/....(me tog/) ....pushya: pha la dang m'u la rkyen aa sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:121a-4: pha lam/....('bras bu/) m'u lam ....(rtsa ba/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121a-5: ` / au n'a da yo nya pa ri mi t'a: auna\ la sogs pa dpag tu med pa'o //
T12TD4298E:121a-6: 'dir bshad pa rnams ni mtshon byed tsam ste gzhan au na la sogs pa'i rkyen ni dpag tu med pa yod do//
T12TD4298E:121a-7: de rnams ni auna\ sogs khongs dang bcas pa mtshon byed tsam mo /
T12TD4298E:121a-8: ` / tu ma ta darth'a yam bha bishya ti /
T12TD4298E:121a-9: 'byung 'gyur las de'i don la tu ma\'o//
T12TD4298E:121a-10: byings las ma 'ongs pa 'byung 'gyur gyi de'i don la rkyen tuma\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121a-11: bhoktum br'a dza ti/....(bzos nas 'gro/) pa thi tu mishte/....('dod pa ltar klog/) sn'a tu mi ha ta ....(khrus byas nas rtse'o//) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121a-14: da byings las dngos po don brjod la rkyen ghanya\ 'gyur te ` ce dzo: ka goo ghi ti /
T12TD4298E:121a-15: tsa dza dag gi gha\ 'gro ba la ka ga dag go //
T12TD4298E:121a-16: byings mtha'i ca yig dang dza yig dag ni rkyen gha 'gro ba'i ming can pha rol la rim pa bzhin ka dang ga ru 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121a-19: ghanya\/ au padh'a 'phel ba nya\ de'i don /
T12TD4298E:121a-20: tsa\ ka\ gha\ yig de'i don /
T12TD4298E:121a-21: p'a ka:....(chos pa'am smin pa/) tya dza la /
T12TD4298E:121a-22: ty'a ga:....(byin can/) ya dza la /
T12TD4298E:121a-23: y'a ga:....(mchod pa/) bha dza la /
T12TD4298E:121a-24: bh'a ga:....('byed do//) yu jir\ sbyor ba la /
T12TD4298E:121a-25: yo ga: ai na\ ....(rnal 'byor/) 'gro ba la /
T12TD4298E:121a-27: rkyen yu dang ghanya\ 'dam ka can du byas pas /
T12TD4298E:121a-29: a'a ya:....('gro ba/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121a-31: bha ...(yu) ba nam/....(bden pa'am yod pa/) bh'a ba:...(ghanya\) d'a dang p'a la /
T12TD4298E:121a-32: (yu) ...d'a nam/....(sbyin bya/) .... d'a ya/...(gha nya a'ata\ la yuka\ a'a ga ma byin/) p'a ni/....('thung bya/) ....p'a ya:...(gha nya a'ata\ la yuka\ a'a ga ma byin/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121a-33: ` / sam dzny'a ya ma karta ri tsa byed po ma yin pa'i ming la'o //
T12TD4298E:121a-34: byings las byed po'i don ma yin pa'i dngos po dang las /
T12TD4298E:121a-35: dang mid brjod pa la'ang rkyen ghanya\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121a-36: pra ti dang a'anga\ sngon ma'i hrinya\ la /
T12TD4298E:121a-37: (so sor bsdu ba/) ...bra ty'a h'a ra: ` sva r'a da: dbyangs las aa'o //
T12TD4298E:121a-38: byings dbyangs kyi mtha' can las byed po'i don ma yin pa'i dngos po sogs kyi don la rkyen aa 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121a-39: sam sngon ma'i tsinya\ la aa yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:121a-40: sanytsa ya:....(sdud pa'am bde ba/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-0: na ya:....(thob pa/) sta ba:....(bstod pa/) na ra:....('dod pas rnam par g-yo ba ste mi/) sogs @121b so /
T12TD4298E:121b-3: byings mad la sogs pa rnams la'ang byed po ma yin pa'i dngos po sogs kyi don la rkyen aa 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-5: ma da:....(yi rang ba/) pra ma da:....(rab tu myos pa/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-6: sha ma:....(zhi ba/) ....dam: de ba:....('di ni sna tshogs pas rtse byed de lha/) bi sha ya:....(khyad par gyi 'ching ba/) ` m'uktoo gha na: ghana\ las sra ba la'o //
T12TD4298E:121b-7: byings ghana\ las sra ba dang /
T12TD4298E:121b-8: yongs su gcog pa'i don dang 'grel ba la rkyen aa 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-9: da dhi sngon ma'i hana\ la aa hana\ ghana\ ru bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:121b-10: da dhi gha na:....(zho sra ba ste zho gar po/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-11: sendha bagha na:....(lan tshva gcog go/) sogs so//
T12TD4298E:121b-13: yi ge bsgyur ba la'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:121b-14: phul du byung ba'i don gyi yi ge phan tshun bsgyur ba la'ang rkyen aa 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-15: hings 'tshe ba la aa ha dang sa\ phan tshun bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:121b-16: sidha:....('tshe ba phul du byung ba ste seng ge/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121b-17: ` /tvi to thu: tu 'gro ba las aa thu'o //
T12TD4298E:121b-18: byings tu yig rjes 'brel 'gro ba la dngos po sogs kyi don la rkyen aa thu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-19: tu be sri g-yo ba dang tu kshe pri lag pas 'phen pa la /
T12TD4298E:121b-20: be pa thu:....('dar ba/) kshe pa thu:....('phen pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121b-22: du 'gro ba las de 'das pa la tri maka\'o//
T12TD4298E:121b-23: byings du rjes 'brel 'gro ba las byings de 'das pa'i don brjod pa la rkyen tri maka\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-25: kri tri mo gha ta:....(bum pa byas/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-27: sam bhri tri mo yuddham/....(dmag tshogs 'khrugs so//) du pa tsasha\ la /
T12TD4298E:121b-28: paktri mam pha lam ....('bras bu smin no//) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:121b-31: byings las dngos po'i don la rkyen nata\ dang ki dag 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-32: ya t'i mchod pa la nata\ yatna:....(sdom brtson/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-33: pratsha\ dang bitsha\ la na ta\: ` pra tstsha bi tstsho: sha ne /
T12TD4298E:121b-34: pra tstsha bitstsha dag gi na la sha'o//
T12TD4298E:121b-35: byings pra tsha\ dang bitsha\ dag gi tsha\ yig ni rkyen na pha rol la sha yig tu 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-36: pra shna:....('dri ba/) bishna:....(khyab par 'gro ba ste g-yog/) ya dza la nata\/
T12TD4298E:121b-37: sa tu sogs kyi na nya /
T12TD4298E:121b-38: yadznya:....(mched pa/) bi sngon ma'i dh'anya\ 'dzin pa la ki /
T12TD4298E:121b-39: aapa\ med pa sogs kyi a'a phyis /
T12TD4298E:121b-41: bi dhi:....(cho ga'am sems la 'dzin pa/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:121b-42: (mtshams bzung ba) ....a'adhi: sandri:....(mtshams sbyor ram nyis sprel/) nadhi:....(nges par 'dzin pa ste gtar/) ` yuta /
T12TD4298E:121b-44: byings las dngos po'i don la rkyen yuta\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:121b-46: ka ra nam/....(byed pa/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:122a-0: @122a * // ha ra nam/....('phrog pa/) ha ba nam/....(sbyin sreg/) bh'u sha nam/....(rgyan/) ba ha nam/....(thob ba/) auta\ sngon ma'i sth'a la yuta\/
T12TD4298E:122a-1: ` au dasth'a de sa lo ba: auta\ las sth'a sogs kyis dbyi'o //
T12TD4298E:122a-2: nyer bsgyur auta\ sngon ma las byings sth'a la sogs pa'i sa yig ni rkyen yuta\ pha rol la dbyi bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:122a-3: autth'a nam/....(steng gi gnas/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:122a-4: au ta\ sngon ma'i stam bha la /
T12TD4298E:122a-5: auttambha nam ....(steng gi ka ba/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122a-6: ` / s'a dha n'am dh'a ra yoshtsa /
T12TD4298E:122a-7: sgrub thabs dang rten dag la'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:122a-8: byings las sgrub thabs dang rten gyi don la'ang rkyen yutra 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:122a-10: (mes mchod) ....pa tsa no nyagni: pa tsa na:th'a l'i ....(gzhong par bcos/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122a-12: a'i sha\ du:su rnams la khala\ yu ta\'o //
T12TD4298E:122a-13: a'i sha ta\ dang du:dang su rnams dang sbyor ba'i byings la rkyan khal dang yuta\ dag 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:122a-14: a'i sha dbha ba:...(khal\ cung zad yod/) durbha ba:....(khal\ sdug bsngal yod/) su bha ba:...(khal\ bde ba yod/) a'ishatka ra:...(khal\ cung zad byed/) du:ka ra:....(khal\ sdug bsngal byed/) su ka ra:....(bde ba byed/) (y'uta\) ...a'i sha dyo dha na:....(cung zad 'thabs/) (y'uta\) ...dur++yo dha na:....('thab dka' ba/) su yod dha na:...(y'uta\ bde bar 'thab/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122a-16: ta bya a'a n'i ya dag go //
T12TD4298E:122a-17: byings bh'u la sogs pa rnams la ma 'ongs pa'i dus brjod pa'i don la rkyen ta bya dang a'a n'i ya dag 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:122a-18: bha bi ta byam/....('byung bar 'gyur ro//) ....bha b'a n'i ya: a'a si ta byam/....(gnas 'cha' bar 'gyur ro//) ....a'a s'a n'i yam /
T12TD4298E:122a-19: karta byam/....(byed par 'gyur/) ....ka r'a n'i yam /
T12TD4298E:122a-20: gra hi ta byam/....('dzin par 'gyur/) ....gra h'a n'i yam sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122a-21: ` / sva r'a dya: dbyangs las ya'o //
T12TD4298E:122a-22: byings dbyangs mtha' can la rkyen ma 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:122a-23: kshe yam/....(zad bya/) dze yam/....(rgyal bya/) ne yam ....(thob bya/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:122a-24: yang byings kshi dang dzi la ya sbyar ba'i ksha yya:....(zad nus/) dang (rgyal nus/) ....dzayya: zhes pa'ang nus pa'i don tshig phrad du bshad do /
T12TD4298E:122a-27: byings pa sde'i yi ge'i mtha' can dang sha ka sogs la'ang rkyen ya 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:122a-28: la bhyam/....(thob ba/) ya bhyam/....('khrig ba/) dza pyam/....(bzlas pa/) sha kya/....(nus pa/) sa hyam/....(dga' ba/) (dad pa dang 'dod ba dang mdzes ba/) ....ru tsyam sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122a-29: ` / a'i ts'a ta: a'ata\ las a'i'ang ngo //
T12TD4298E:122b-0: byings a'ata\ mtha' can la'ang rkyen ya 'gyur zhing ya pha rol la a'ata\ de a'i @122b yig tu'ang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:122b-1: d'a la ya a'a a'i yon tan byas pas /
T12TD4298E:122b-2: de yam/....(sbyin bya/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:122b-3: dznye yam/....(shes bya/) pe yam ....('thung bya/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122b-4: ` / ri ha s'a nt'a dghya na /
T12TD4298E:122b-5: ri ha sa'i mtha' las ghya na\'o //
T12TD4298E:122b-6: byings ri yig dang ha sa'i mtha' can las dngos po sogs dang 'byung 'gyur gyi don la rkyen ghyana\ 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:122b-7: k'a r++yam ....(las/) p'a r++yam ....(sgrib ba'am 'gangs pa/) b'a dhyam/....(gsong por smra ba/) h'a syam/....(gang mo/) ba tsa dang pa tsa la gha\ 'gro ba sogs kyi yang na tsa kar bsgyur bas /
T12TD4298E:122b-8: b'a kyam/....(smra ba'am ngag sbyor/) ....b'a tsyam /
T12TD4298E:122b-9: p'a kyam/....(mchod pa/) ....p'a tsyam sogs so //
T12TD4298E:122b-10: mchod pa'i don dang 'brel ba'i dngos po'i don la ta bya /
T12TD4298E:122b-12: kyap\ ghyana\ ya rnams 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:122b-13: dri shal ta bya dri sha sogs kyi ri ra sha sha /
T12TD4298E:122b-15: drashta byam/....(bltas nas mchod/) de bzhin du /
T12TD4298E:122b-17: darsh'a n'i aa:....(bltas nas mchod/) ya la /
T12TD4298E:122b-18: dri shya:....(bltas nas mchod/) shr'u thos pa la /
T12TD4298E:122b-19: shro ta byam/....(thos pa/) ....shra ba n'i yam /
T12TD4298E:122b-21: mam ta byam/....(shes pa/) ....ma na n'i ya: sogs so//
T12TD4298E:122b-22: yang byings 'dod pa'i don gyi rkyen si'i mtha' can la'ang ta bya la sogs pa 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:122b-23: ni di dhy'a si ta byam/....(bar ma chad par bsam gtan 'dod pa/) bi dzi dzny'a si ta byam ....(bye brag tu shes par 'dod/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:122b-26: byings au yig mtha' can las lhag par dang nges par sogs kyi don la rkyen ghyana\ 'gyur zhing /
T12TD4298E:122b-27: ao ta mtha' las rkyen ya la dbyangs kyi bya ba 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:122b-29: bh'a byam/....(los yod dam nges par yod/) l'u nya\ la /
T12TD4298E:122b-30: l'a byam ....(nges par gcod/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:122b-31: yang krita\ sogs kyi rkyen ta bya sogs kyi mtha' can dang sbyor ba'i aa ba shyama\ gyi ma\ dang /
T12TD4298E:122b-32: k'a ma dang na masa\ dang sbyor ba'i tuma\ gyi ma\ dag dbyi ba dang /
T12TD4298E:122b-33: hi ta dang tata\ gnyis dang sbyor ba'i nyer bsgyur sama\ gyi ma\ yig dang pa tsa rkyen yuta dang gha nya\'i mtha' can dang sbyor ba'i mam sa'i aa dbyi ba dang mi dbyi ba 'dam ka can du bshad de /
T12TD4298E:122b-35: lumpa de ba bya ma:kri tye tum k'a ma ma\ na so ra pi /
T12TD4298E:122b-36: sa mo b'a hi ta ta ta yorm'am sa sya pa tsi yutgha nyo:/
T12TD4298E:122b-37: kri ta\ la aa ba shyama\ gyi ma\ dbyi zhing //
T12TD4298E:122b-38: tuma\ gyi yang ni k'a ma ma na sa\ la //
T12TD4298E:122b-39: hi ta ta ta\ la sama\ gyi yang na ste //
T12TD4298E:122b-40: m'am sa'i pa tsa yuta\ ghanya\ la'o //
T12TD4298E:123a-2: aa ba shya bh'a bya:....(nges par bden nam yod/) bho ktu k'a ma:....(longs spyod 'dod/) shro tu ma n'a:....(thos pa yid la byed/) sam hi ta:....grogs bzang po'am lhan cig pa/) ....sa hi ta: sam ta tam/....(de legs pa/) ....sa ta tam /
T12TD4298E:123a-3: m'am sa pa tsa nam/....(sha 'tshod par byed/) ....m'am spa tsa nam /
T12TD4298E:123a-4: m'am sa p'a ka:....(sha tshos/) ....m'am sp'a ka: sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123a-5: ` / ri du pa dh'a tkya pa /
T12TD4298E:123a-6: ri au pa dh'a las kya pa\'o //
T12TD4298E:123a-7: byings ri yig au pa dh'a can las dngos po dang las kyi don la rkyen kyapa\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123a-8: kri t'i gcod pa la kyapa\ sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:123a-9: kri tyam/....(gcod pa/) yang shtunya\ sogs la'ang rkyen kyapa\ 'jug par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:123a-10: shtunya\ dang kri la kyapa\ thung du sogs kyi pa\ 'gro ba tuka\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:123a-11: stu tyam/....(bstod pa bya'o//) ....kri tyam sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123a-12: ` / stri y'am ya dzam bh'a be /
T12TD4298E:123a-13: ya dza rnams kyi dngos po la bud med la'o //
T12TD4298E:123a-14: byings yadza\ la sogs pa rnams las dngos po'i don la rkyen kyapa\ 'gyur zhing rtags de yang bud med kyi rtags su 'gyur ba nyid de /
T12TD4298E:123a-15: pra sngon ma'i ya dza la kyapa\/
T12TD4298E:123a-16: yadza\ sogs kyi slar yang dag par bsgyur /
T12TD4298E:123a-17: bud med la a'apa\ sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:123a-18: pre dzy'a/....(rab tu mchod/) de bzhin du sama\ sngon ma'i aadza\ 'gro ba la /
T12TD4298E:123a-19: (a'apa\) ...sa ma dzny'a/....(yang dag par 'gro ma/) brahma sngon ma'i hana\ la kyapa\ ha gha ka 'gro ba la aa nu d'atta phyis /
T12TD4298E:123a-20: thung ngu sogs kyis tuka\ byin pas /
T12TD4298E:123a-24: byings las dngos po sogs kyi don la'ang kti 'gyur zhing de yang rang bzhin gyi mo rtags te //
T12TD4298E:123a-25: bhu ti:....('byor pa/) shuddhi: ....(dag pa/) (bhra) ...a'u dhi:...(ki thob pa/) pamkti:...(pi tsa 'phreng ba/) pitti:....(rig pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123a-28: byings las byed pa po'i don la'ang rkyen kti 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123a-29: pra kri ti:....(rang bzhin/) bi dhri ti:....(khyab par 'dzin pa/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123a-30: ` / aika\ shti boo dh'a tu ni rde sha: aika\ shtipa\ dag las byings la rnam 'gyur med do //
T12TD4298E:123a-31: byings las dngos po sogs kyi don la rkyen aika\ dang stipa\ dag 'gyur la rkyen de gnyis pha rol las byings la rnam 'gyur yang med de /
T12TD4298E:123a-34: sha\ yig aapa\ bi k'a ra na'i don te /
T12TD4298E:123a-35: pa tsi:....('tshed do//) pa tsa ti:....('tshed par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123a-37: sha 'gro ba dang bhida\ rnams kyi aada\ ngo //
T12TD4298E:123b-0: byings sha\ yig rjes 'brel 'gro ba rnams dang bhida\ la sogs pa rnams las kyang rkyen aada\ @123b 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123b-1: (a'apa\) ...pa ts'a/....('chad ma/) (a'apa\) ...gri dz'a/....(dag ma/) bhi d'a/...(a'apa\/
T12TD4298E:123b-3: dum bur byed ma/) sogs so //
T12TD4298E:123b-4: yang dza ra sogs la rkyen aada\ gi da\ yig med par aa nyid sbyor bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:123b-7: lci ba'i ha sa las so //
T12TD4298E:123b-8: byings au pa dh'a yi ge lci ba dang ldan pa'i ha sa'i mtha' can la'ang rkyen aang 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123b-9: a'i h'a/....(rtsed mo byed/) a'u h'a/....(rtog par byed/) a'eeksha ....('dod par byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123b-12: byings rkyen mtha' can las kyang rkyen aa 'gyur zhing rtags de'ang mo rtags su bya ste /
T12TD4298E:123b-13: tsi k'irsh'a/....(byed par 'dod/) pu tr'i y'a ....(bu 'dod ma/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123b-16: sngon byung ba'i 'das pa yun ring song ba dang 'das nas yun ring ma song ba'i don la'ang rkyen ktv'a 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123b-17: sn'a tv'a bhum kte/. ...(khrus byas nas zas bza'/) bhu ktv'a pra dza ti ....(bzos nas 'gro/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123b-18: ` / aa lam kha lvo: pra ti she dhe ktv'a /
T12TD4298E:123b-19: aa la kha lu dag las dgag pa la ktv'a'o //
T12TD4298E:123b-20: mi zad pa'i nang tshan aa lam dang kha lu dgag pa'i don can sngon ma'i byings las kyang rkyen ktv'a 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123b-21: aa lambh'u ktv'a/....(mi za'o/) kha l'u ktv'a ...(bdza //
T12TD4298E:123b-24: aita\ dang bcas pa'i ktv'a ka 'gro ba yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:123b-25: spyir rkyen ktv'a ka 'gro ba yin kyang aita\ dang bcas pa'i ktv'a ni ka\ 'gro ba'i ming can du yang na par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:123b-26: bi di tv'a/....(rig go'am shes so//) ....be di tv'a sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123b-28: auta\ 'gro ba las ktv'a ste aita yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:123b-29: byings auta\ rjes 'brel 'gro ba las kyang rkyen ktv'a 'gyur zhing aita\ a'a ga ma ster ba 'dam ka can du bya ste /
T12TD4298E:123b-32: aisht'a/....('dod pa nyid/) ba su nges par gnas pa la /
T12TD4298E:123b-38: byings las tshig sdud dang 'brel ba'i byed pa'i don la'ang rkyen kyapa\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:123b-39: sam bhri tye ka ro ti/....(kun nas 'phel bar byed/) pra na mya gatstsha ti ....(/ phyag btsal nas 'gro bar byed/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:123b-40: ` / yang kha cig tu na nya\ sbyor ba la'ang rkyen ktv'a sbyor bar bshad de /
T12TD4298E:123b-45: aa dzi tv'a sh'a tra b'a rsa rb'an kri tv'a bi ma lam ya sha:/
T12TD4298E:123b-46: aa dattv'a mitta marthi bhya:ka tham dz'i banti bh'u bhri ta:/
T12TD4298E:123b-47: dgra rnams kun las rgyal bar ma 'gyur bas /
T12TD4298E:123b-48: dri ma med pa'i grags ldan mi byed cing //
T12TD4298E:124a-2: sa 'dzin 'tsho ba'i gtam yang med par 'gyur //
T12TD4298E:124a-4: yang rkyen kyapa\ pha rol las byings sngon ma de thung du yin pa'i bar rkyen nyi la yon tan byed par bshad de /
T12TD4298E:124a-5: pa ri na ...(nyi kyap\) me yyo bhu kte ....(yongs su 'dud nas zas za/) sogs se //
T12TD4298E:124a-6: yang dus dang 'brel pa la yang rkyen kyapa\ 'jug pa mthong ste /
T12TD4298E:124a-7: (mig rab tu btsums nas dgod/) ....ne tre sam m'i lya ha sa ti/...(mi la\ kyapa\) mu kham by'a d'a ...(d'a) ya ...(kyapa\) sve pi ti ....(kha gdangs nas nyal/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:124a-8: ` / poo na: pu n+ye na ma pa dam dvi shtsa /
T12TD4298E:124a-9: yang yang la nama\ ste tshig gnyis kyang ngo //
T12TD4298E:124a-10: byings las bzang ngan sogs dbye ba ma yin pa'i mnyam pa'i don dang yang yang bskyar ba'i don la rkyen nama\ 'gyur zhing byings rkyen dang bcas pa de'ang gnyis su brjod par bya ste /
T12TD4298E:124a-11: p'a yam b'a yam gatstsha ti/....(btungs shing btungs nas 'gro/) bho dzam bho dzam bra dza ti ....(zos shing zos nas 'gro/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:124a-12: ` / ka tha m'a di shu sva rthe na ma\ kri nya: ka tham la sogs pa rnams la kri nya las rang don la nama\'o//
T12TD4298E:124a-13: ka thi la sogs pa nye ba'i tshig tu yod pa la byings kri nya las rang gi don la rkyen nama\ 'jug ste /
T12TD4298E:124a-14: ka tham k'a ram/....(gang ltar byed/) ai rtham k'a ram ....('di ltar byed/) sogs so//
T12TD4298E:124a-16: bh'u las dngos po la kyapa\'o //
T12TD4298E:124a-17: byings bh'u las dngos po'i don kho na brjod pa la'ang rkyen kyapa\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:124a-18: brahma bh'u yam ga ta:....(srog can du gyur pa'i 'gro ba/) ` lakshe r'i muta\ tsa /
T12TD4298E:124a-19: laksha\ la a'i ste muta\ yang ngo //
T12TD4298E:124a-20: byings laksha mtshan nyid la rkyen a'i 'gyur zhing rkyen de la muta\ a'a ga ma ster bar bya ste /
T12TD4298E:124a-21: lakshm'i:....(dpal lam phun sum tshogs pa'am bkra shis/) ` sty'a ya te: str'i tve da\ ta\/
T12TD4298E:124a-22: stye las bud med nyid la da\ ta\'o //
T12TD4298E:124a-23: byings styee nya sgra dang mnyam par 'dres pa las bud med nyid brjod pa'i don la rkyen da\ ta\ 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:124a-27: ta\ 'gro ba sogs kyi mo rkyen a'ipa\ sbyar bas /
T12TD4298E:124a-28: str'i/....(/ sgra ldan nam bde bar 'tsho ba ste bud med//) ` / barn'atk'a ra: yi ge las k'a ra'o //
T12TD4298E:124a-29: yi ge so so'i mtha' las de dang de'i yi ge zhes rang bzhin brjod pa'i don la rkyen k'a ra 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:124a-30: aa k'a ra:....(aa yig/) ka k'a ra:....(ka yig/) tsa k'a ra:....(tsa yig/) ta k'a ra:....(ta yig/) ta k'a ra:....(ta yig/) pa k'a ra:....(pa yig/) sogs so /
T12TD4298E:124b-0: ` @124b r'a di le b'a/[?] ra las ai pha yang na'o //
T12TD4298E:124b-1: ra yig las de'i rang bzhin brjod ba'i don la ai pha yang na 'gyur te /
T12TD4298E:124b-2: re pha:....(ra yig/) ....ra k'a ra: ` lo k'atstshe sha sya siddha: lhag ma 'jig rten las grub pa'o //
T12TD4298E:124b-3: sngon du bshad pa ltar brda sbrod ba'i tshul gyi cho ga sogs nye bar mkho ba rnams bshad zin gyi /
T12TD4298E:124b-4: 'dir ma bshad pa'i lhag ma 'jig rten dang bstan bcos la grags shing grub ba rnams kyang de dag tu shes par bya'o//
T12TD4298E:124b-5: ` ai ti sva ra sva sti by'a ka ra na sya s'u tr'a tkri d'a da ya: bra kri ya sa m'a bt'a:/
T12TD4298E:124b-6: zhes pa brda sprod pa dbyangs can gyi mdo las kri ta\ la sogs pa'i rab tu bya ba rnams rdzogs so//
T12TD4298E:124b-7: ` // sva r'u p'anto& nu bh'u ty'a di: shabdo& bh'a dya tra s'artha ka: / sa maska r'i shu bh'am tsa kre pra kri y'am tsa tu ro tsi t'am //
T12TD4298E:124b-8: thog mtha' rjes 'byor rang bzhin bzang po yis //
T12TD4298E:124b-9: 'dir ni don bcas sgra la zhugs byas te //
T12TD4298E:124b-10: mtshungs par sbyod ldan dge bar byed pa yis //
T12TD4298E:124b-11: rab tu bya ba gsal ldan bshad zin to //
T12TD4298E:124b-12: aa ba t'a dvo ha ya gr'i ba: ka ma l'a ka ra a'i shva ra: //
T12TD4298E:124b-13: su r'a su ra na r'a k'a ra ma dhu b'a p'i ta pam ga dza: //
T12TD4298E:124b-14: khyod la srung bar mdzod cig rta mgrin kye //
T12TD4298E:124b-15: dbang gi mnga' sgyur phyag na padma yis //
T12TD4298E:124b-16: lha dang lha min mi la phan par ni //
T12TD4298E:124b-17: sbrang rtsi 'thung bas chu skyes bzhin du skyongs //
T12TD4298E:124b-18: de ltar ngag gi dbang phyug 'phags ma dbyangs can mas gnas lnga rig pa'i slob dpon chen bo aa nu bh'u ti sva ru b'a tsar++ya ste rjes su 'byor ba rang bzhin bzang po la dngos su stsal ba'i brda sprod pa'i bstan bcos chen bo dbyangs can by'a ka ra na zhes grags pa'i gzhung /
T12TD4298E:124b-19: slob dpon chen po de nyid kyis mdzad pa'i 'grel pa rab tu bya ba gsal ldan zhes pa dang bcas pa 'di yang /
T12TD4298E:124b-20: lha dang bcas ba'i 'gro pa yongs kyi ma 'dris pa'i mdza' bshes chen po 'phags pa phyag na padma nyid gdul bya'i snang ngor gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i skur bzhengs pa don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
T12TD4298E:125a-0: rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen pa chen po ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho 'jigs med go cha thub bstan lang tsho'i sdes gzhung 'di la lha mthong lo ts'a ba'i phyed 'gyur tsam gyi legs po zhig yod tshod du 'dug pa deng sang dpe rgyun dkon zhing phyis su bsgyur @125a * //
T12TD4298E:125a-2: yig sna kha shas 'dug kyang gzhung don go dka' ba dang slob dpon aa nus mdzad pa'i 'grel pa'i dgongs don dang ma 'brel ba sogs 'ga' re 'dug pas /
T12TD4298E:125a-3: khyod kyis pandi ta mched kyi gsung rgyun ltar 'di bzhin sgyur cig ces bka'i gnang ba thob par brten /
T12TD4298E:125a-4: rnam 'dren dam pa 'di nyid kyi gzhal du med pa'i bka' drin las 'phags yul nub phyogs ku ru kshe tra bram ze'i rigs su 'khrungs pa gnas lnga rig pa'i ma h'a pandi ta ba la bha dra dang /
T12TD4298E:125a-5: pandi ta go k'u la n'a tha mi shra mched kyi drung du gzhung 'grel 'di sogs brda sprod pa'i rang lugs la sbyangs pas cung zad tsam shes pa bka' 'bangs kyi tha chung gtsang stod 'dar gyi nor 'dzin yangs par se'i rigs las skyes pa ngag dbang phun tshogs lhun grub bam /
T12TD4298E:125a-6: tshe dbang rab brtan rdo rjer 'bod pa'i rmongs brtul snyom las pas /
T12TD4298E:125a-7: me mkha' rgya mtsho la 'das lo drug cu skor bcu dang nyag sum cu rtsa brgyad bsre ba sna tshogs dbyig ces shing sbrul hor zla gsum pa'i dmar phyogs kyi dga' ba dang po'i gza' tshes dge bar mgo btsugs lo de'i hor zla dgu pa'i tshes bco lnga dkar po nam gru'i 'grub sbyor gyi dus dge bar /
T12TD4298E:125a-8: sde bzhi'i sgo 'phar cig car du phye ba'i phun tshogs lugs brgya'i 'dun sa chen po pho brang po ta lar bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
T12TD4298E:125a-9: tshul 'dir sgo gsum 'bad sogs rnam dkar 'bras //
T12TD4298E:125a-10: ji snyed mchis kun yongs su smin pa'i mthus //
T12TD4298E:125a-11: rigs kun khyab bdag don gyi thams cad mkhyen //
T12TD4298E:125a-12: srid mtha'i bar du zhabs pad brtan pa dang //
T12TD4298E:125a-13: sna mang brda sprod ring lugs chu gter che //
T12TD4298E:125a-14: bsrubs pa'i snying po legs bshad nyin byed 'dis //
T12TD4298E:125a-15: lnga rig bstan pa'i pad tshal cher rgyas shing //
T12TD4298E:125a-16: rab rmongs blo yi mun pa sel bar shog / bdag sogs deng nas skye dang tshe rabs su ;
T12TD4298E:125a-17: / mchog gsum ngo bo rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
T12TD4298E:125a-18: rjes bzung gsang chen zab mo'i lam zhugs te //
T12TD4298E:125a-19: zung 'jug bde ba chen po'i sa thob shog /
